\id 2KI
\h 2 Ijeǧiden 
\toc1 2 Ijeǧiden 
\toc2 2 Ijeǧiden 
\toc3 2 Ij. 
\mt1 2 Ijeǧiden  
\c 1
\s1 Iliya ak-d Axazya - Řmewt n Axazya  
\m
\v 1 Awarni řmewt n Axab iɣewweɣ Mu’ab x Israil. \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt 2 Ij. 3:5\x*  
\v 2 Iwḍa-dd Axazya s tracca n řkazi n tɣurfet nnes di Samarya uca ihřec. Netta issekk ireqqasen inna asen: “Ruḥem ɣar Baɛal-Zabub, arebbi n Ɛaqrun, maḥend ad tesseqsam ma war d ayi ineqq řehřac-a.”   
\m
\v 3 Maca lmalak n SIDI issiweř-dd ɣar Ilicaɛ, Aticbi: “Kkar, geɛɛed, řqa ireqqasen n ujeǧid n Samarya u siweř akidsen: ‘Ma s tidett war din AREBBI di Israil, ařami kenniw tuyurem, ḥima ad tesseqsam Baɛal-Zabub, arebbi n Ɛaqrun?’  
\v 4 S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘War dd-thekkʷid ca zi tassut i x tgeɛɛded, maca ad temmted řmewt.’” Uca \add xenni\add* iffeɣ Iliya.   
\m
\v 5 \add Řami\add* dd-ɛeqben ireqqasen ɣar \add Axaziya\add*, inna asen i nitni: “Min \add ixs ad yini\add* man aya, \add řami\add* dd-tɛeqbem ɛawed \add deɣya\add*?” \f ◼ \fr 1:5 \ft \+fk \+bdit Řami\+bdit* dd-ɛeqben ireqqasen ɣar \+bdit Axazya\+bdit*\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Řami ɣares dd-ɛeqben ireqqasen’.\f*  
\v 6 Nitni arrin-dd xas: “Ijj n weryaz imsagar akidneɣ, inna aneɣ: ‘Ɛeqbem ɣar ujeǧid wenni kenniw dd-issekken, ad as tinim: Ammu i issiweř SIDI, ma s tidett war ɣarwem zeɛma AREBBI di Israil ařami tessekked, ḥima ad tesseqsid Baɛal-Zabub, arebbi n Ɛaqrun? S uya war dd-thekkʷid ca zi tassut i x tgeɛɛded, maca ad temmted řmewt.’”  
\v 7 Netta issiweř akidsen: “Mammec igga waddud n weryaz nni kidwem imsagaren u issiweř akidwem awařen-a?”  
\v 8 Nitni arrin-dd xas: “Netta d ijj n weryaz ɣares \add ijj n upartessu n\add* ucuwwaf, ɣares ijj n webyas n ccark x tejɛinna nnes.” \add Xenni\add* inna netta: “Wa d Iliya, Aticbi.” \f ◼ \fr 1:8 \ft \+fk Aticbi\ft  - ijj n weryaz zi tendint n Ticbi.\f*   
\m
\v 9 Netta issekk ijj n umeqqran n xemsin ak-d xemsin \add n yeryazen\add* nnes ɣares. Wanita igeɛɛed ɣares, u xzar, Iliya tuɣa ittɣima x tqiccat n wedrar. U netta issiweř ɣares: “\add Cek,\add* aryaz n AREBBI, ajeǧid inna ac: ‘Hwa-dd!’”  
\v 10 Iliya yarra-dd, inna i umeqqran n xemsin: “Mařa necc aqa d aryaz n AREBBI, ejj ad tewḍa tmessi zeg ujenna, ad cek tecc, cek d xemsin \add n yeryazen\add* nnec.” \add Řexdenni\add* tewḍa-dd tmessi zeg ujenna, tecca i-t netta d xemsin \add n yeryazen\add* nnes.   
\m
\v 11 Xas uca issekk ɣares ɛawed ijj n umeqqran nneɣni n xemsin ak-d xemsin \add n yeryazen\add* nnes. Wanita iṭṭef deg wawař, inna as: “Cek, \add a\add* aryaz n AREBBI, ammu i iqqar ujeǧid: ‘Hwa-dd deɣya!’”  
\v 12 Iliya yarra-dd uca inna asen: “Mařa necc d aryaz n AREBBI, ammu i dd ɣa tewḍa tmessi zeg ujenna, ad cek tecc d yeryazen nnec,” \add Řexdenni\add* tewḍa-dd tmessi zeg ujenna, tecca i-t netta d xemsin \add n yeryazen\add* nnes.   
\m
\v 13 Issekk ɛawed ijj n umeqqran n xemsin i twařa wiss třata, ak-d xemsin \add n yeryazen\add* nnes. \add Umi\add* igeɛɛed umeqqran n xemsin wiss třata uca yiweḍ \add ɣares\add*, yuḍar netta x ifadden nnes zzat i Iliya uca iḥeccem i-t, inna as: “\add A\add* aryaz n AREBBI, ejj ad teswa tudart inu d tudart n imsexxaren nnec, n xemsin \add n yeryazen-a\add*, di tiṭṭawin nnec.  
\v 14 Xzar, timessi tewḍa-dd zeg ujenna, tecca tnayen n imeqqranen n xemsin ak-d xemsin \add n yeryazen\add* nsen. Ejj ad teswa řexxu tudart inu di tiṭṭawin nnec!”   
\m
\v 15 Uca inna lmalak n SIDI i Iliya: “Hwa akides, war tteggʷed ca zzat i wudem nnes!” Ikkar netta, ihwa akides ɣar ujeǧid.  
\v 16 \add Xas uca\add* issiweř ak-d ujeǧid: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Maɣar cek tessekked ireqqasen nnec, ḥima ad sseqsan Baɛal-Zabul, arebbi n Ɛaqrun, axmi war din iǧi s tidett AREBBI di Israil, ḥima ad \add t\add* tesseqsid x wawař nnes, s uya war dd-thekkwid ca zi tassut i x tgeɛɛded, maca ad temmted řmewt.’”  
\v 17 \add Ammu\add* i immut ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI i tuɣa issiweř Iliya. Maɣar netta tuɣa war ɣares bu mmis, idweř Yuram d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes deg useggʷas wiss tnayen n Yahuram, mmis n Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Yahuda.   
\m
\v 18 Imezruyen iqqimen n Axazya, d min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil?   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Iliya ittwammeksi ɣar ujenna  
\m
\v 1 Imsar ɣar tmeksit n Iliya s \add ufus n\add* SIDI deg ict n tḥaryaḍt ɣar ujenna, aqa iffeɣ Iliya ak-d Ilicaɛ zi Jiljal.  
\v 2 Inna Iliya i Ilicaɛ: “Qqim da, maɣar SIDI issekk ayi ɣar Bayt-Il.” \add Maca\add* Ilicaɛ inna:“S tidett am iddar SIDI u iddar řeɛmar nnec, necc war cek ttejjiɣ.” \add Ammu i\add* hwan nitni \add s tnayen\add* ɣar Bayt-Il.  
\v 3 Ffɣen-dd ayt n inabiyyen, inni \add tuɣa iǧan\add* di Bayt-Il, ɣar Ilicaɛ, nnan as: “Ma tessned, aqa SIDI ass-a ad ikkes bab nnec tiwa i uzeǧif nnec?” Netta yarra-dd: “Uřa d necc aqa ssneɣ t. Sqarem!”   
\m
\v 4 Iliya inna as: “Qqim da, Ilicaɛ, maɣar SIDI issekk ayi ɣar Ariḥa.” Maca netta inna: “S tidett am iddar SIDI u iddar řeɛmar nnec, necc war cek ttejjiɣ ca!” \add Ammu\add* dd-usin nitni ɣar Ariḥa.  
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* usin-dd ayt n inabiyyen nni \add iǧan\add* di Ariḥa ɣar Ilicaɛ, nnan as: “Ma tessned, aqa SIDI ass-a ad ikkes bab nnec tiwa i uzeǧif nnec?” Netta yarra-dd: “Uřa d necc aqa ssneɣ t. Sqarem!”   
\m
\v 6 Iliya maca inna as: “Qqim da, maɣar SIDI issekk ayi ɣar L’Urdun.” \add Maca\add* netta inna: “S tidett am iddar SIDI u am iddar řeɛmar inu, necc war cek ttejjiɣ ca!” Uca nitni uyuren s tnayen idsen.  
\v 7 Uřa d xemsin n yeryazen zeg ayt n inabiyyen uyuren, qqimen bedden arendad nsen ɣar řaggʷaj, am bedden nitni s tnayen idsen ɣar L’Urdun.  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* iksi Iliya aseřham nnes, issunneḍ i-t uca iwta zzayes x waman nni ttwabḍan x tnayen n iɣezdisen u nitni ẓwan s tnayen idsen x řaẓaɣ.  
\v 9 Řami ẓwan nitni, imsar, aqa Iliya inna i Ilicaɛ: “Ttar ict n řḥajjet i d ac ɣa ggeɣ, qbeř mma xak i ɣa mmeksiɣ!” Ilicaɛ yarra-dd: “Iři ad xafi dd-hwant tnayen n tseqqar n buḥbeř nnec!”  
\v 10 Iliya inna: “Cek tᵉttared ict n tmesřact tewɛar. Mařa cek teẓrid ayi řami xak i ɣa mmeksiɣ, ad ac imsar ammu, maca mařa war iǧi amenni, war ittemsar ca.”   
\m
\v 11 Uca imsar am nitni gguren u ssawařen ak-d wayawya, xzar, aqa din ict n tkarrut n tmessi ak-d iysan n tmessi tenni tebḍa i-ten ijj x wenneɣni. \add Ammu\add* igeɛɛed Iliya di tḥaryaḍt ɣar ujenna.  
\v 12 Ilicaɛ iẓra uca iřaɣa xas: “\add A\add* baba, \add a\add* baba! Akarru \add n umenɣi\add* n Israil d imnayen nnes!” \add Xenni\add* netta war t itwiři ɛad uca iksi arruḍ nnes, icarreg i-t x tnayen. \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt 2 Ij. 13:14\x*  
\v 13 Xenni issmun-dd aseřham i dd-yewḍan zzayes netta uca iɛqeb, ibedd ɣar tma n L’Urdun.  
\v 14 Netta iksi aseřham n Iliya i dd-yewḍan zzayes netta, iwta zzayes x waman, inna: “Mani iǧa SIDI AREBBI n Iliya? Wah, Netta!” Uca netta iwta x waman uca mmsebḍan nitni x tnayen n iɣezdisen uca iẓwa Ilicaɛ.   
\m
\v 15 \add Umi\add* ayt n inabiyyen nni \add din\add* ibedden arendad n Ariḥa, ẓrin t, nnan: “Buḥbeř n Iliya yarsa x Ilicaɛ.” Nitni usin-dd ɣares uca uḍaren zzates \add s uɣembub nsen\add* ɣar temmurt.  
\v 16 Nitni nnan as: “Xzar xenni, jar imsexxaren nnec \add aqa din\add* xemsin n yeryazen, ayt n umenɣi. Ejj i-ten ad uyuren, ad arzun x sidi nnec, ad taɣ SIDI iksi t uca inḍar i-t x ijj n wedrar niɣ deg ict zi teɣzurin.” \add Maca\add* netta inna: “War sekkim uřa d ijj!”  
\v 17 Umi xas ɛemmden nitni ařami d as iweddar min ɣa yegg, inna: “\add Iwa\add* sekkem \add ten din\add*!” Nitni ssekken xemsin n yeryazen d ina arzun třata n wussan, maca nitni war t ufin.  
\v 18 Uca ɛeqben-dd nitni ɣares, minzi tuɣa iqqim di Ariḥa. Netta inna asen: “Ma war d awem nniɣ: ‘War ttriḥem ca’?”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ilicaɛ issgenfa aman n Ariḥa  
\m
\v 19 Iryazen n tendint nnan i Ilicaɛ: “Xzar xenni, addud n tendint mliḥ, am mammec ittwařa sidi inu simant nnes, maca aman war iḥřin u tammurt tiwi-dd agray.”  
\v 20 Netta inna: “Awyem ayi-dd ijj n ṭṭebsi d amaynu u ggem dayes tameǧaḥt!” Uca nitni iwyen as t-i-dd.  
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ \add zi tendint\add* ɣar tařa n waman uca inḍar dayes tameǧaḥt nni, inna: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Necc arriɣ aman-a ṣebḥen. War dd-ttiwyen řmewt niɣ d agray ɛad.’”  
\v 22 Aman dewřen ṣebḥen ɛawed ař ass-a ɛlaḥsab awař n Ilicaɛ i issiweř.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Iḥudriyyen sseḥqaren Ilicaɛ di Bayt-Il  
\m
\v 23 Ssenni igeɛɛed ɣar Bayt-Il. \add Am\add* ittgeɛɛed abrid, ffɣen-dd iḥudriyyen zi tendint, inni t ikkʷaren, nnan as: “Aqeccar, geɛɛed! Aqeccar, geɛɛed!”  
\v 24 Netta inneqřeb-dd awarni as, ixzar daysen uca ixza i-ten deg Yisem n SIDI. Řexdenni usin-dd tnayen n ddubat zeg wezɣar u mezzqen tnayen-u-rebɛin n iḥudriyyen. \f ◼ \fr 2:24 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  
\v 25 Ssenni yuyur netta ɣar wedrar n Karmil uca ssenni iɛqeb ɣar Samarya.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Amenɣi n Yuram, ajeǧid n Israil ak-d Mu’ab  
\m
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss tmenṭac n Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Yahuda, idweř Yuram, mmis n Axab, d ajeǧid x Israil di Samarya. Netta iḥkem tenɛac n iseggʷusa.  
\v 2 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, maca war \add t iggi\add* ammu \add d taɛeffant\add* am babas d yemmas, maɣar ikkes amayḍu \add iqeddsen\add* n Baɛal wenni igga babas. \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt 1 Ij. 16:32\x*  
\v 3 Maca netta iqqim imenneɛ di ddnub n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, wenni yarrin Israil ad ixḍa. Netta war iḥeyyed x ddnub n Yarubɛam.  
\v 4 Micaɛ, ajeǧid n Mu’ab, tuɣa d ameksaw u tuɣa ittic i ujeǧid n Israil myat-ařef n izmaren d taḍuft n myat-ařef n icarriyyen. \f ◼ \fr 3:4 \ft \+fk ameksaw\ft  - niɣ ‘aniči’.\f*  
\v 5 Řami immut Axab, imsar, aqa iɣewweɣ ujeǧid n Mu’ab x ujeǧid n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt 2 Ij. 1:1\x*   
\m
\v 6 Deg wass nni iffeɣ-dd ujeǧid Yuram zi Samarya uca isedd marra Israil.  
\v 7 Iṭṭef abrid uca issekk \add ijj n ureqqas\add* ɣar Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Yahuda, inna: “Ajeǧid n Mu’ab iɣewweɣ xafi. Ma cek ad kidi teffɣed deg umenɣi ak-d Mu’ab?” Netta inna: “Necc ad ffɣeɣ akidek. Necc ad iřiɣ am cek, řgens inu am řgens nnec d iysan inu am yiysan nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 3:7 \xt 1 Ij. 22:4\x*  
\v 8 Inna: “X man abrid i ɣa ngeɛɛed?” Netta inna: “X webrid n řexřa n Idum.”   
\m
\v 9 \add Řexdenni\add* yuyur ujeǧid n Israil d ujeǧid n Yahuda d ujeǧid n Idum. Nitni nnḍen ijj n webrid n sebɛa n wussan uca war tuɣi din aman i řɛeskar u i řebhayem nni ten iḍfaren.  
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid n Israil: “Axeyyeb i neccin umi dd-iřaɣa SIDI třata n ijeǧiden-a, ḥima ad ten iwc deg ufus n Mu’ab!”  
\v 11 Uca Yahucafaṭ inna: “Ma war da iǧi ijj n unabi n SIDI, wenni i zi ɣa nesseqsa SIDI?” \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd ijjen zeg imsexxaren n ujeǧid n Israil, inna: “Ilicaɛ, mmis n Cafat, wenni izeǧɛen aman x ifassen n Iliya, aqa-t danita!” \x ◘ \xo 3:11 \xt 1 Ij. 22:7\x*   
\m
\v 12 Uca inna Yahucafaṭ: “Ɣares netta awař n SIDI.” Uca ajeǧid n Israil d Yahucafaṭ d ujeǧid n Idum hwan-dd ɣares.  
\v 13 Ilicaɛ inna i ujeǧid n Israil: “Min dinni jar ayi-dd d cek? Uyur ɣar inabiyyen n babac u ɣar inabiyyen n yemmac!” Maca ajeǧid n Israil yarra-dd xas: “Lla, maɣar SIDI iřaɣa-dd i třata-ya n ijeǧiden \add ɣar da\add*, ḥima ad ten iwc deg ufus n Mu’ab.” \x ◘ \xo 3:13 \xt 1 Ij. 18:19\x*  
\v 14 Ilicaɛ yarra-dd xas: “\add S tidett am\add* iddar SIDI n řɛeskarat nni umi beddeɣ zzat i wudem nnes, mři necc war ɣari bu uweqqar i Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ad yiři necc war cek ḥessbeɣ u war dayek xezzareɣ! \x ◘ \xo 3:14 \xt 1 Ij. 17:1\x*  
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, awi ayi-dd ijj iccat x ifiřan. Řami tuɣa ittirar wenni iccaten x ifiřan, imsar aqa afus n SIDI yarsa xas.  
\v 16 Inna netta: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ggem di teɣzurt-a tařyiwin d teřyiwin \add ktar\add*!’  
\v 17 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Kenniw war tẓarrem asemmiḍ uřa d anẓar, \add maca waxxa amenni\add* taɣzurt-a ad teccur s waman uca kenniw ad tessʷem, kenniw uřa d řebhayem nwem d zzwayeř nwem.’  
\v 18 \add Maca\add* man aya \add ɛad\add* drus di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, \add maɣar\add* Netta ad awem iwc uřa d Mu’ab deg ifassen nwem.  
\v 19 Kenniw ad tewtem kuř tandint ifaryen u kuř tandint icennɛen, u ad tqeḍɛem kuř tacejjart iṣebḥen u ad tbellɛem marra řɛunṣarat n waman u ad tḍeyyɛem kuř iyyar iṣebḥen n temmurt s yeẓra.”   
\m
\v 20 Uca di tiwecca ɣar \add tsaɛɛet i ɣar\add* dd-ttawyen tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*, imsar, aqa usin-dd waman zi Idum uca tɣebba temmurt s waman.  
\v 21 Mu’ab am ikmeř isřa belli ijeǧiden ffɣen-dd i umenɣi akidsen. \add Xenni\add* řaɣan-dd x marra \add iryazen\add*, ixs ad yini, zeg inni \add izemmaren\add* ad sennḥen s webyas \add n řesnaḥ\add* ař \add kuř ijj\add* sennej i uya, uca nitni settfen ixef nsen ɣar weymir.  
\v 22 Nitni kkaren ɣar tuffut n ṣṣbeḥ, u umi dd-tenqar tfuct x waman, ẓrin ayt n Mu’ab nni x ujemmaḍin, aqa aman d izeggʷaɣen am yidammen.  
\v 23 Nitni nnan: “Ina d idammen. Ijeǧiden nɣin ixef nsen am mmenɣen \add jar asen\add* s ssif uca ijj iwta wenneɣni. Iwa \add ayt n\add* Mu’ab, ṭṭfem takeccaḍt!” \f ◼ \fr 3:23 \ft \+fk ijj\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘aryaz’.\f*  
\v 24 \add Maca umi\add* iwḍen nitni ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Israil, kkaren \add ayt n\add* Israil uca wtin \add ayt n\add* Mu’ab. Arewřen \add ayt n\add* Mu’ab zzat i wudem nsen uca xenni udfen nitni \add ɣar temmurt\add*, wtin Mu’ab.  
\v 25 Nitni hedmen tineddam uca \add kuř\add* aryaz inḍar aẓru nnes x kuř iyyar iṣebḥen uca dřin t. \add Ɛawed\add* netyen nitni marra řɛunṣarat n waman uca qeḍɛen kuř tacejjart iṣebḥen ařami ceṭṭen mɣir iẓra \add n řḥiḍ\add* n Qir-Ḥarisat. Ayt bu-iǧayen nnḍen as uca ɣeḍřen tt.  
\v 26 \add Umi\add* iẓra ujeǧid n Mu’ab belli amenɣi iwɛar xas aṭṭas, issmun-dd ɣares sebɛa mya n yeryazen nni \add izemmaren\add* ad jebden ssif, ḥima ad icuq \add iseddiyyen n řɛeskar\add* ɣar ujeǧid n Idum, \add maca\add* nitni war zemmaren.  
\v 27 \add Xenni\add* iksi netta mmis amenzu wenni i ɣa idewřen d ajeǧid awarni as, uca yiwyi t x řḥiḍ d taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ. Uca yusa-dd uduqqez d ameqqran n weɣḍab x Israil. Nitni ffɣen zzayes uca ɛeqben ɣar temmurt nsen.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Zzect n tajjač  
\m
\v 1 Ict zi temɣarin n ayt n inabiyyen třaɣa i Ilicaɛ, tenna: “Amsexxar nnec, aryaz inu, immut, uca cek tessned belli amsexxar nnec tuɣa itteggʷed SIDI. \add Řexxu maca\add* yusa-dd bab n wareṭṭař, ḥima ad iksi akides tnayen n iḥenjiren inu d isemɣan.” \x ◘ \xo 4:1 \xt Lawi 25:39\x*  
\v 2 Inna as Ilicaɛ: “Min zemmareɣ ad am ggeɣ? Ini ayi min ɣarem di taddart.” Nettat tarra-dd xas: “Tayya nnec war ɣares walu mɣir ict n tɣarraft dayes zzect.”  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* inna: “Ttar i yixef nnem tiqduḥin barra i taddart, tiqduḥin n jjiran nnem xwant, ḥḍa war iřint drus.  
\v 4 Xenni adef ɣar daxeř uca belleɛ tawwart awarni am u awarni i iḥenjiren nnem. Farreɣ \add xenni zzect\add* di marra tiqduḥin nni, u min iǧan iccur, sars i-t ɣar uɣezdis!”  
\v 5 \add Xas uca\add* tuyur xas uca tbelleɛ tawwart awarni as u awarni i iḥenjiren nnes. Nitni iwyen ɣares \add tiqduḥin\add* u nettat tfarreɣ \add daysent zzect\add*.  
\v 6 \add Umi\add* ccurent marra tiqduḥin, tenna i mmis: “Awi ayi-dd ɛad ict n teqduḥt!”, \add maca\add* netta yarra-dd xas: “War da teqqim ca teqduḥt \add ɛad\add*!” U zzect tuɣa teqḍa.  
\v 7 Nettat tuyur ad tt txebbar i weryaz n AREBBI u wanita inna: “Uyur, zenz zzect u xeǧeṣ bab n wareṭṭař nnem u zi min ɣa iqqimen ad zzayes teddared, cem ak-d iḥenjiren nnem.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ilicaɛ d mmis n temɣart zi Cunam  
\m
\v 8 Deg ijj n wass umi dd-ikka Ilicaɛ x Cunam, imsar, aqa ict n temɣart icennɛen issbedd i-t din, ḥima ad \add ɣares\add* icc. Řebda umi tuɣa dd-ittekk \add x tendint nni\add*, imsar, aqa iḥeyyed x webrid nnes ɣar din, ḥima ad icc ca n macca.  
\v 9 Nettat maca tenna i weryaz nnes: “Xzar, necc uciɣ aqa aryaz-a i ɣarneɣ dd-yusin řebda, aqa-t d aryaz amqeddas.  
\v 10 Ejj aneɣ ad nebna sennej ijj n wexxam d tameẓyant s řeḥyuḍ, uca ad negg din ijj n qama, ict n ṭṭabřa, ijj n řkursi d ijj n řefnar i netta. Mařa netta xenni yusa-dd ɣarneɣ, izemmar ad dinni iɛzeř ixef nnes.”  
\v 11 Deg ijj n wass imsar aqa Ilicaɛ yusa-dd din uca iɛzeř ixef nnes deg wexxam n nnej uca iruḥ izzeř dinni.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* inna netta i umsexxar nnes Jiḥazi: “Řaɣa-dd i Tcunamect tanita!” Netta iřaɣa as u nettat tbedd zzat i wudem nnes.  
\v 13 Netta tuɣa i d as innan \add i umsexxar nnes\add*: “Ini as: ‘Cem tᵉthillid dayneɣ aṭṭas. Min izemmar ad am ittwagg? Ma ad taɣ din ict n řḥajjet min xef nzemmar ad nessiweř ak-d ujeǧid niɣ ak-d ukumandar ameqqran n řɛeskar di ṭṭweɛ nnem?’” \add Maca\add* nettat tenna: “Necc zeddɣeɣ di řwesṭ n řgens inu.”  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* tuɣa inna: “Min izemmaren ad as ittwagg?” Uca inna Jiḥazi: “Nettat war ɣares aḥenjir u aryaz nnes iwsar.”  
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* tuɣa inna netta “Řaɣa-dd xas!” U netta iřaɣa-dd xas uca teqqim nettat tbedd di tewwart,  
\v 16 uca netta inna: “Di řweqt-a ittwaggen, ɣar tsaɛɛet n tudart, ad teksid aḥenjir deg iɣaǧen nnem.” Uca nettat tenna: “Lla, a sidi inu, \add a\add* aryaz n AREBBI, war sxarriq \add zeɛma\add* x tayya nnec!” \x ◘ \xo 4:16 \xt Amz. 18:10, 14\x*  
\v 17 Tamɣart tedweř teksi s ddeyset uca turuw-dd ijj n uḥenjir di řweqt ittwaggen, ɣar řweqt n tudart nni x tuɣa issiweř Ilicaɛ akides.   
\m
\v 18 \add Umi\add* imɣar uḥenjir, imsar deg ijj n wass, iffeɣ-dd barra ɣar babas, ɣar yinni imejjaren.  
\v 19 Inna i babas: “\add A\add* azeǧif inu, \add a\add* azeǧif inu!” Uca babas inna i yijj n umsexxar: “Arbu t ɣar yemmas!” \f ◼ \fr 4:19 \ft \+fk Uca babas inna ...\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Uca netta inna ...’\f*  
\v 20 Netta yarbu t uca yiwyi t ɣar yemmas. Netta tuɣa ittɣima x ifadden nnes ař azal, \add xenni\add* immut.  
\v 21 Nettat tgeɛɛed sennej, tessars i-t x qama n weryaz n AREBBI. Tbelleɛ tawwart xas uca teffeɣ.  
\v 22 Třaɣa-dd x weryaz nnes, tenna as: “Sekk ayi-dd ijjen zeg imsexxaren d ijj zi teɣyař, ḥima ad uyureɣ deɣya ɣar weryaz n AREBBI u \add xenni\add* ad ɛeqbeɣ \add ɛawed\add*.”  
\v 23 Netta inna: “Mayemmi ɣa tuyured ɣares ass-a? Aqa war iǧi d abeddi n uyur u war iǧi d ssebt.” Nettat tenna: “Kuřci ad yiři mliḥ!”  
\v 24 Nettat tbardeɛ i teɣyuč u tenna i umsexxar nnes: “Ndeh i-tt, qqim ggur. Am tnedhed war tbeddi di ṭṭweɛ inu mɣir xmi d ac t i ɣa iniɣ.”   
\m
\v 25 Nettat teffeɣ uca tiweḍ-dd ɣar weryaz n AREBBI, ɣar wedrar n Karmil. Umi tt iẓra netta zi řaggʷaj, inna i Jiḥazi, amsexxar nnes: “Xzar, aqa din d Tacunamect.”  
\v 26 Řexxu, uyur deɣya, řqa tt uca ini as: ‘Ma aqa cem mliḥ? Ma aryaz nnem aqa-t mliḥ? Ma aḥenjir nnem aqa-t mliḥ?’” Uca nettat tenna: “Aqa-ten mliḥ!”  
\v 27 \add Umi maca\add* dd-tusa ɣar weryaz n AREBBI x wedrar, tqebbeḍ nettat x iḍaren nnes. Jiḥazi yudef-dd din ḥima ad tt iɛarn ɣar uɣezdis, maca aryaz n AREBBI inna: “Aḥta as, maɣar řeɛmar nnes icḍen dayes u SIDI issnuffar xafi min xef u war d ayi issargeb ca.”  
\v 28 Tenna nettat: “Ma necc ttareɣ i sidi inu ijj n mmi? Ma war nniɣ necc: ‘War d ayi cemmet’?” \x ◘ \xo 4:28 \xt 2 Ij. 4:16\x*  
\v 29 Inna netta i Jiḥazi: “Byes tajɛinna nnec, ksi taɣɣarct inu deg ufus nnec uca ṭṭef abrid! Mařa cek temmeřqid ca n yijj, war xas ttseǧam, u mařa iseǧem xak ḥed, war xas dd-ttarri ca! Sars taɣɣarct inu x uɣembub n uḥenjir!” \x ◘ \xo 4:29 \xt Lk. 10:4\x*  
\v 30 \add Maca\add* yemmas n uḥenjir tenna: “\add S tidett am\add* iddar SIDI u iddar řeɛmar inu, necc war xak ttḥeyyideɣ ca!” Netta ikkar, iḍfar i-tt.   
\m
\v 31 Tuɣa Jiḥazi izwar deɣya zzatsen u issars taɣɣarct x uɣembub n uḥenjir, maca netta war iggi ca řḥess uřa d twarrit. \add Xenni\add* iɛqeb ḥima ad xas iřqa, uca iḥaja as t, inna: “Aḥenjir war dd-ifiq.”  
\v 32 \add Umi\add* dd-yusa Ilicaɛ ɣar taddart, tuɣa immut uḥenjir, immars x qama nnes.  
\v 33 Yudef netta ɣar wexxam, ibelleɛ tawwart awarni asen s tnayen idsen uca iẓẓuǧ i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 4:33 \xt Mt. 6:6\x*  
\v 34 Xenni ibedd zzat i qama, iwḍa tiwa n uḥenjir uca issars netta aqemmum nnes x uqemmum nnes, tiṭṭawin nnes x tiṭṭawin nnes, ifassen nnes x ifassen nnes. Netta issbuzzeř \add ammu\add* tiwa nnes uca teḥma arrimet n uḥenjir.  
\v 35 \add Xenni\add* iɛqeb-dd, yuyur di taddart da d diha, igeɛɛed twařa nneɣnit uca issbuzzeř ixef nnes tiwa nnes. \add Řexdenni\add* iɛḍes uḥenjir sebɛa n twařawin uca \add xenni\add* yarzem uḥenjir tiṭṭawin nnes. \x ◘ \xo 4:35 \xt 1 Ij. 17:21; 2 Ij. 8:1; Řex. 20:10\x*  
\v 36 Iřaɣa-dd netta i Jiḥazi, inna: “Řaɣa-dd x Tcunamect!” Uca netta iřaɣa-dd xas uca tusa-dd nettat ɣares, uca inna \add Ilicaɛ\add*: “Arbu mmim!”  
\v 37 Tudef nettat din, tewḍa ɣar iḍaren nnes uca yuḍar \add as\add* \add s uɣembub nnes\add* ɣar tammurt. \add Xenni\add* teksi mmis uca teffeɣ ɣar barra.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řmewt di marmita d lmuɛjiza n usecci  
\m
\v 38 \add Umi\add* dd-iɛqeb Ilicaɛ ɣar Jiljal, tuɣa din řaẓ di temmurt u ayt n inabiyyen qqimen zzates. Inna netta i umsexxar nnes: “Egg marmita d tameqqrant u egg taḥrirt i ayt n inabiyyen.” \f ◼ \fr 4:38 \ft \+fk ayt n inabiyyen\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘inni ixsen ad řemden ad dewřen d inabiyyen. Aqa-ten d imeḥḍaren n Ilicaɛ.\f*  
\v 39 \add Xenni\add* dd-iffeɣ ijjen \add zzaysen\add* yuyur ɣar weḥwic barra, ḥima ad dd-yawi tibbi. Netta yufa ijj n wezbir n řexřa uca iřqeḍ-dd zzayes ařami iccur \add ubeḥrur n\add* warruḍ nnes s texsact n řexřa. \add Xenni\add* iɛqeb-dd uca iqess i-ten di marmita. Aqa nitni war tt ssinen.  
\v 40 \add Xenni\add* farɣen aya i iryazen, ḥima ad ccen. Umi qqasen nitni zi teḥrirt-a, imsar, aqa nitni sɣuyen deg ujenna, řaɣan: “\add A,\add* yeryaz n AREBBI, \bd řmewt aqa-tt di marmita!\bd*” Uca nitni war zemmaren ad \add zzayes\add* ccen.  
\v 41 Netta inna: “Awi ayi-dd \add drus n\add* waren!” Netta issuyes i-t di marmita, inna: “Farɣem \add aya\add* i řgens, ḥima ad ccen!” \add Xenni\add* idweř war dinni ca war iḥři di marmita. \x ◘ \xo 4:41 \xt Uf. 15:25\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 42 Yusa-dd ijj n weryaz zi Baɛl-Calica, yiwi-dd i weryaz n AREBBI aɣrum zi \add ṣṣabet\add* tamenzut, ɛicrin n iɣrumen n imendi d řḥebb ibaryen \add n imendi\add* deg ict n tecyart, uca netta inna: “Ewc \add man aya\add* i řgens.”  
\v 43 Maca wanita inna: “Mammec t i ɣa ssarseɣ i mya n yeryazen?” Netta \add maca\add* inna: “Ewc i-t i řgens ad t yecc, maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: \bd ‘Ad ccen u ɛad ad iceṭṭ’\bd*.” \x ◘ \xo 4:43 \xt Yḥ. 6:9, 11\x*  
\v 44 Netta issars asen \add t\add* uca ccin nitni, u iceṭṭ xasen am mammec \add tuɣa inna\add* wawař n SIDI.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 Asgenfi n Nuɛman  
\m
\v 1 Nuɛman, akumandar n řɛeskar n ujeǧid n Aram, tuɣa-t d ijj n weryaz ɣares ssumɛet zzat i wudem n sidis nnes u tuɣa ɣares ccan aṭṭas, maɣar zzayes i yiwi SIDI asenjem i Aram. Aryaz \add nni\add* tuɣa d ijj n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen, \add maca\add* tuɣa dayes řbarṣ.  
\v 2 Tuɣa din bandiyyat zi Aram, iwyent-dd ict n tebřiɣt zi temmurt n Israil d tameḥbust. Tuɣa-tt \add txeddem\add* i temɣart n Nuɛman.  
\v 3 Tenna i lallas: “Mři \add tuɣa\add* sidi inu ɣar unabi di Samarya, \add xenni\add* iři netta ad t issgenfa zi řbars nnes.”   
\m
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* yuyur wanita, ḥima ad t iḥaja i sidis nnes, inna: “Ammu d wammu i tessiweř tebřiɣt zi temmurt n Israil.” \f ◼ \fr 5:4 \ft \+fk wanita\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘Nuɛman’.\f*  
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid n Aram: “Uyur din u necc ad ssekkeɣ ict n tebrat i ujeǧid n Israil.” Netta yuyur deg webrid uca iksi ɛecra talintat n nnuqart d setta-ařaf \add ciqlu\add* n wureɣ d ɛecra n warruḍ icnan.  
\v 6 Netta issiweḍ tabrat i ujeǧid n Israil, \add ammu i\add* yura: “Řexxu \add xenni\add*, xzar, mařa tiweḍ-dd tebrat-a ɣarek, aqa necc ssekkeɣ-dd ɣarek \add ɛawed\add* amsexxar inu Nuɛman, maḥend ad t tessgenfid zi řbarṣ nnes.”  
\v 7 \add Umi\add* iɣra ujeǧid n Israil tabrat, icarreg arruḍ nnes, iřaɣa: “Necc maɣar ma d AREBBI ařami zemmareɣ ad sseddareɣ ijj n umettin ařami netta dd-issekk weryaz-a ɣari, maḥend ad t ssgenfiɣ zi řbarṣ nnes? Iwa, ssnem, u xzarem, aqa netta yarezzu ayi řesbab waha!” \x ◘ \xo 5:7 \xt Aɛwd. 32:39; 1 Ṣm. 2:6\x*   
\m
\v 8 Umi isřa Ilicaɛ, aryaz n AREBBI, belli ajeǧid n Israil icarreg arruḍ nnes, imsar aqa netta issekk \add ijj\add* ɣar ujeǧid, ḥima ad as yini: “Mayemmi tcarrged arruḍ nnec? Ejj i-t ad ɣari dd-yas, \add ḥima\add* xenni netta ad issen, aqa din ijj n unabi di Israil.”  
\v 9 Ammu dd-yusa Nuɛman ak-d iysan d ukarru nnes uca ibedd ɣar tewwart n taddart n Ilicaɛ.  
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* issekk Ilicaɛ ijj n ureqqas ɣares, iqqar: “Uyur u ssird ixef nnec sebɛa n twařawin di L’Urdun, \add xenni\add* ad tedweř arrimet nnec teggenfa uca cek ad tiřid d amezdag.”  
\v 11 Iffugem Nuɛman, uca yuyur, iqqar: “Xzar, necc nniɣ deg ixef inu: ‘Netta ad iffeɣ ɣar barra, ad ibedd \add din\add*, maḥend ad iřaɣa Isem n SIDI, AREBBI nnes, uca ad issekk s ufus nnes amcan \add i dayes iǧan řbarṣ\add* u ammu i ɣa iggenfa řbarṣ.’  
\v 12 Ma war iǧi Abana d Farfar, iɣezran n Dimacq, ḥsen x marra iɣezran n Israil? Ma war zemmareɣ ad dinni ssirdeɣ, ḥima ad zedgeɣ?” Netta inneqřeb uca yuyur, isɛar aṭṭas.   
\m
\v 13 Imsexxaren nnes usin-dd ɣares, ssiwřen akides, nnan: “Baba, \add mři\add* anabi nni ittar zzayek ca min iwɛaren, iři teggid t? I mařa inna xak ɛad: ‘Sird ixef nnec uca ad tdewřed cek tizdiged?’”  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* ihwa-dd ɣar L’Urdun uca isseɣḍeṣ ixef nnes sebɛa n twařawin di L’Urdun am mammec inna wawař n unabi n AREBBI uca \add tedweř\add* arrimet nnes teggenfa am arrimet n ijj n uḥenjir u netta idweř izdig. \x ◘ \xo 5:14 \xt Lk. 4:27\x*   
\m
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* iɛqeb ɣar weryaz n AREBBI ak-d marra řɛeskar nnes uca yiweḍ \add din\add*, ibedd zzat i wudem nnes, inna: “Xzar, řexxu ssneɣ, aqa war iǧi AREBBI mani ma x marra tammurt mɣir di Israil waha. Xenni řexxu, ɛafek, ksi ict n tarzeft zeg umsexxar nnec!”  
\v 16 \add Maca\add* netta inna: “\add S tidett am\add* iddar SIDI wenni umi beddeɣ zzat i wudem nnes, necc war kessiɣ walu!” U netta issḥeccem i-t, ḥima ad iksi \add ca\add*, maca netta yugi.  
\v 17 Inna Nuɛman: “Mařa lla, iři xenni ad immewc i umsexxar nnec aṭṭas n ucař, anect \add zemmaren\add* tnayen n iserdan ad arbun, maɣar amsexxar nnec war ittiwi ɛad taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ niɣ taɣarṣt i irebbiten inneɣni mɣir i SIDI waha.  
\v 18 \add Maca\add* iři ad iɣfar SIDI i umsexxar nnec ta \add waha\add*, mařa sidi inu ad yadef ɣar zzawect n Rimmun ḥima ad ibendeq am ittɛemmed dinni x uɣiř inu, aqa necc xenni ad bendqeɣ \add ammu\add* di zzawect n Rimmun. \add Mařa\add* ad bendqeɣ \add ammu\add* di zzawect n Rimmun, iři ad iɣfar SIDI tamesřact nni i umsexxar nnec.”  
\v 19 Inna as: “Uyur di řehna!” U netta isafar tammurt, iggʷej xas \add ijj n webrid\add*.   
\m
\v 20 Inna Jiḥazi, amsexxar n Ilicaɛ, aryaz n AREBBI: “Xzar, sidi inu issɛizz x Naɛman, Aramiyu, maḥend ad iksi \add ca\add* zeg ufus nnes zi min tuɣa i dd-yiwi netta. \add S tidett am\add* iddar SIDI, necc ad t areddfeɣ deɣya uca ad zzayes ksiɣ ca!”  
\v 21 Jiḥazi yuyur, yardef Nuɛman. \add Umi\add* Nuɛman iẓra, aqa netta yuzzeř awarni as, iḍra-dd zeg ukarru, maḥend akides imsagar, inna: “Mliḥ?”  
\v 22 Netta yarra-dd xas: “Mliḥ. Sidi inu issekk ayi-dd maḥend ad yini: ‘Aqa, ɣar řexxu ɛad usin-dd tnayen n iḥudriyyen zeg ayt n inabiyyen zeg idurar n Ifrayim. Ewc asen \add xenni\add* ict n talint n nnuqart d tyuya n warruḍ icnan.’”  
\v 23 Inna Nuɛman: “Ɛafak, ksi zzayi tnayen talint n nnuqart.” Netta iḥeccem i-t u igga tnayen talint n nnuqart di tnayen n tecyarin uca iwca tnayen n warruḍ icnan i tnayen n imsexxaren nnes, inni ten yarbun ɣar zzat nnes.  
\v 24 \add Umi\add* yiweḍ ɣar řgeɛɛdet, iksi ten zeg ifassen nsen uca innuffar i-ten di taddart. Ijja iryazen ad uyuren uca ffɣen nitni.   
\m
\v 25 \add Awarni man aya\add* yudef uca ibedd zzat i bab nnes. Ilicaɛ isseqsa t: “Manis dd-tusid, \add a\add* Jiḥazi?” Uca netta yarra-dd: “Amsexxar nnec war dd-iffiɣ ca mani.”  
\v 26 \add Maca\add* Ilicaɛ inna as: “Ma war tuɣi uř inu din iḥḍar umi dd-iḍra weryaz zeg ukarru nnes i umsagar akidek? Maɣar ma d řḥař ad tmenɛed nnuqart d warruḍ d tcejjura n zzitun d imarjaɛen n uḍiř d wuǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin d isemɣan d tiyya?  
\v 27 Řbarṣ n Nuɛman ad iřseq i řebda dayek u di zzariɛet nnec!” \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ zi zzat i wudem nnes s řbarṣ, d acemřař am wedfeř. \x ◘ \xo 5:27 \xt Řxř. 12:10; 2 Im. 26:19, 20\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\s1 Taceqqurt ifettaḥen  
\m
\v 1 Ayt n inabiyyen nnan i Ilicaɛ: “Xzar, amcan mani nzeddeɣ zzat i wudem nnec, iḥṣar i neccin.”  
\v 2 Ejj aneɣ ad nuyur ɣar L’Urdun u dinni qaɛ ijj zzayneɣ ad dd-yawi ijj n ukeccuḍ, maḥend ad negg ict n tzeddiɣt i neccin.” Netta inna: “Uyurem!”  
\v 3 Ijjen \add zzaysen\add* maca inna: “Ɛafak, uyur ak-d imsexxaren nnec.” Netta inna: “Necc akidwem uyureɣ.”  
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* yuyur akidsen. \add Umi\add* dd-usin ɣar L’Urdun, zedmen ticejjura.  
\v 5 Řami izdem ijj ict n tcejjart, imsar, aqa \add řeqḍeɛ n\add* wuzzař \add n ccaqur\add* iwḍa deg waman uca netta iřaɣa, inna: “A sidi inu, \add ccaqur\add* tuɣa ittwarḍeř!”  
\v 6 Aryaz n AREBBI inna: “Mani iwḍa?” \add Umi\add* d as isscen amcan, iqess ijj n ukeccuḍ, inḍar i-t din u \add ammu\add* yiwi-dd uzzař iggur sennej.  
\v 7 Inna netta: “Sgeɛɛed i-t-i-dd ɣarek!” \add Xenni\add* isswiẓẓeḍ s ufus nnes uca iṭṭef i-t.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Timegga n Ilicaɛ deg umenɣi ak-d Aram  
\m
\v 8 Ajeǧid n Aram immneɣ ak-d Israil uca imcawar ak-d imsexxaren nnes, inna: “Deg wemcan-in d win ad wteɣ iqiḍan i řɛeskar inu.”  
\v 9 \add Maca\add* aryaz n AREBBI issekk \add ijj\add* ɣar ujeǧid n Israil, inna: “Ḥḍa ixef nnec ad tekked x wemcan nni, maɣar din hwan ayt n Aram.”  
\v 10 Ajeǧid n Israil issekk \add ireqqasen\add* ɣar wemcan i x tuɣa akides issiweř weryaz n AREBBI u i zi tuɣa i d as iɛřem wanita, uca igga ad ḥḍan din. \add U man aya\add* war \add imsar ca\add* ict n twařa niɣ tnayen n twařawin \add waha\add*.  
\v 11 Uř n ujeǧid n Aram ihaj x man aya u netta iřaɣa i imsexxaren nnes, inna asen: “Ma war tzemmarem kenniw ad ayi tinim man wen jar aneɣ ittraḥ ak-d ujeǧid n Israil?”  
\v 12 Ijjen zeg imsexxaren nnes inna: “Lla, sidi inu, ajeǧid! Maca Ilicaɛ, anabi wenni \add iǧan\add* di Israil, issargeb ujeǧid n Israil awařen i tessawařed deg wexxam nnec n yiḍeṣ.”  
\v 13 Inna netta: “Uyurem uca xzarem mani ittiři netta. \add Xenni\add* ad ssekkeɣ \add iryazen inu\add*, ad t ṭṭfen.” Xebbaren t, nnan: “Netta aqa-t di Dutan.”  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* issekk netta iysan d ikarruten d ijj n řɛeskar ameqqran. Nitni iwḍen din di ǧiřet uca nnḍen-dd i tendint.   
\m
\v 15 Amsexxar n AREBBI ikkar ɣar tuffut uca iffeɣ ɣar barra, u xzar, ijj n řɛeskar tuɣa inneḍ i tendint s yeysan d ikarruten. \add Xenni\add* inna as aḥudri: “A sidi inu, min ɣa negg?”  
\v 16 Netta inna: “War tteggʷed ca, maɣar inni ɣarneɣ aṭṭas x yinni ɣarsen.” \x ◘ \xo 6:16 \xt 2 Im. 32:7; Yḥ. 16:33; 1 Yḥ. 4:4\x*  
\v 17 Ilicaɛ iẓẓuǧ, inna: “\add A\add* SIDI, arzem as tiṭṭawin, \add maḥend\add* ad iẓar!” U SIDI yarzem i umsexxar tiṭṭawin \add ařami\add* itwařa. U xzar, adrar iccur s yeysan d ikarruten n tmessi i dd-innḍen i Ilicaɛ.  
\v 18 \add Umi\add* ɣares dd-usin nitni, iẓẓuǧ Ilicaɛ i SIDI, inna: “Wwet maca řgens-a s tuddarɣeč!” Uca netta iwta ten s tuddarɣeč ɛlaḥsab awař n Ilicaɛ.   
\m
\v 19 \add Xas uca\add* inna asen Ilicaɛ: “Wa war iǧi d abrid nican u war teǧi d tandint nican. Ḍfarem ayi-dd! Necc ad kenniw nedheɣ ɣar weryaz nni x tarezzum!” U netta indeh i-ten ɣar Samarya.  
\v 20 Umi iwḍen nitni ɣar Samarya, imsar, aqa Ilicaɛ inna: “\add A\add* SIDI arzem tiṭṭawin n iryazen-a, \add maḥend\add* ad ẓaren!”. Uca yarzem asen SIDI tiṭṭawin ařami ẓrin. U xzar, aqa nitni \add tuɣa aten\add* di řwesṭ n Samarya.  
\v 21 \add Umi\add* ten iẓra, inna ujeǧid n Israil i Ilicaɛ: “Ma ad ten nɣeɣ, \add a\add* baba?”  
\v 22 \add Maca\add* wanita inna: “War ten neqq ca! Cek s yixef nnec, ma ad tenɣed inni tḥebbsed s ssif nnec d řqews nnec? Sars asen-dd aɣrum d waman maḥend ad ccen ad swen, uca xenni ad ɛeqben ɣar sidi nsen.”  
\v 23 Issewjed asen ijj n umensi d ameqqran uca nitni ccin, swin. \add Awarni aya\add* yarxu asen uca ffɣen ɣar sidi nsen. \add Xenni\add* war dd-usint bandiyyat n Aram ɛad di temmurt n Israil.   
\b  
\m
\v 24 Awarni uya imsar, aqa Binhadad, ajeǧid n Aram, issmun marra řɛeskar nnes, iffeɣ, ḥima ad inneḍ i Samarya.  
\v 25 Imsar ijj n řaẓ d ameqqran di Samarya, maɣar xzar, nitni nnḍen as-dd ařami idweř ijj n uzeǧif n ijj weɣyuř isekkwa tmenyin n \add uqiyyat n\add* nnuqart d yijj n arrbeɛ n ijj n řeqyas s řeɣbar n wedbir \add idweř isekkwa\add* xemsa n \add uqiyyat n\add* nnuqart.  
\v 26 Umi iɛdu ujeǧid n Israil x řḥiḍ, imsar, belli třaɣa as-dd ict n temɣart, tenna: “Ewc ayi-dd afus, a sidi inu ajeǧid!”  
\v 27 Netta inna: “\add Mařa\add* SIDI war d am iwci afus, mammec necc d am ɣa wceɣ afus? Ma ad yiři \add s ca\add* zeg unedrar niɣ zi tsirt n uḍiř?”  
\v 28 Inna as ujeǧid: “Min cek yuɣin?” Nettat tenna: “Tamɣart-a tenna ayi: ‘Awi-dd mmim, ḥima ass-a ad t necc u mmi ad t necc xenni tiwecca.’”  
\v 29 \add Ammu\add* neccin nᵉssnenna mmi uca necca i-t. \add Maca\add* řami d as nniɣ tiwecca nnes: ‘Ewc \add řexxu\add* mmim, ḥima ad t necc!’, řexdenni tessnuffar nettat mmis.” \x ◘ \xo 6:29 \xt Aɛwd. 28:53\x*   
\m
\v 30 Umi isřa ujeǧid awařen n temɣart-a, icarreg arruḍ nnes uca \add ammu i\add* yuyur x řḥiḍ uca iẓra řgens illa aqa yarḍ ict n txancet \add n wecḍan\add* x arrimet nnes.  
\v 31 Netta inna: “Ejj ad ayi igg AREBBI ta d ta uca ad dayes yarni ɛad, mařa iqqim uzeǧif n Ilicaɛ, mmis n Cafat, xas ař ass-a!” \x ◘ \xo 6:31 \xt 1 Ij. 19:2\x*   
\m
\v 32 Ilicaɛ iqqim di taddart nnes d imeqqranen qqimen ɣares. Tuɣa \add ujeǧid\add* issekk ijj n weryaz ɣar zzat nnes, maca qbeř ma yiweḍ ureqqas ɣares, inna \add Ilicaɛ\add* i imeqqranen: “Ma teẓrim aqa wanita, mmis n ijj n uqettař, issekk-dd wenni d ayi ɣa iqessen azeǧif? Ḥḍam řexxu, xmi dd ɣa yas ureqqas, bellɛem tawwart u sbeddem t ɣar tewwart! Ma war \add ittwaseř\add* řḥess n iṣuraf n sidis awarni as?”  
\v 33 Řami tuɣa akidsen issawař ɛad, xzar, ihwa-dd ureqqas ɣares. Uca ajeǧid inna: “Xzar, tuɛeffna-ya zi SIDI. Min ɣa rajiɣ ɛad \add xenni\add* zi SIDI?”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\s1 Ilicaɛ izwar ibarreḥ s usenjem n Samarya  
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* inna Ilicaɛ: “Sřem i wawař n SIDI! Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Tiwecca ɣar řweqt-a ad teswa ijj n řeqyas n waren azdad ɣar tewwart n Samarya mɣir ijj n ciqlu u ad mmenzen uřa d tnayen n řeqyas n imendi i yijj n ciqlu \add waha\add*!” \f ◼ \fr 7:1 \ft \+fk řeqyas\ft  - ɛřayen 7-8 litru.\f*  
\v 2 Ijj n uneɣraf \add n řɛeskar\add*, wenni x uɣiř nnes iɛemmed ujeǧid, yarra-dd x weryaz n AREBBI: “Xzar, waxxa mařa SIDI igga řekwaza deg ujenna, ma izemmar aya ad imsar?” \add Maca\add* netta inna: “Xzar, ad t tẓared s tiṭṭawin nnec, maca war zzayes tᵉttetted.”   
\b  
\m
\v 3 Tuɣa din arebɛa n yeryazen zzat i wadaf n tewwart. Nnan ijj i wenneɣni: “Mayemmi ɣa neqqim da ař ɣa nemmet? \x ◘ \xo 7:3 \xt Lawi 13:46\x*  
\v 4 Mařa ad nini: ‘Ejj aneɣ ad nadef ɣar tendint!’, xenni iǧa řaẓ di tendint u neccin ad dayes nemmet. U mařa neqqim neccin da, ad nemmet \add ɛawed\add*. Xenni řexxu, ejj aneɣ ad neffeɣ ad newḍa deg ifassen n řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Aram. Mařa nitni jjin aneɣ neddar, ad neqqim neddar, u mařa nitni nɣin aneɣ, \add xenni\add* ad nemmet.”  
\v 5 Nitni kkaren di tbambast, ḥima ad uyuren ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Aram. \add Maca umi\add* udfen nitni ɣar ṭṭarf n řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Aram, war din tuɣi uřa d ijjen.  
\v 6 Maɣar Sidi ijja řɛeskar n Aram ad iseř i yijj n ujarri n ikarruten d ijj n ddriz n iysan d ǧɣa n ijj n řɛeskar d ameqqran, \add ařami\add* nitni nnan ijjen i wenneɣni: “Xzar, ajeǧid n Israil icra d iḥarrec-dd xaneɣ ijeǧiden n Iḥittiyyen d ijeǧiden n Imiṣriyyen.” \f ◼ \fr 7:6 \ft \+fk Sidi\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Sidi inu’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 7:6 \xt Ica. 13:4\x*  
\v 7 Kkaren uca arewřen di tbambast uca jjin iqiḍan nsen d yeysan nsen d yeɣyař nsen uřa d řmargeḥ n řɛeskar am mammec ten tuɣa, uca arewřen maḥend ad ssnejmen řeɛmar nsen.   
\m
\v 8 \add Řami\add* dd-iwḍen ayt n bu-řbarṣ ɣar ṭṭarf n řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, udfen ɣar ijj n uqiḍun, ccin, swin u iwyen ssenni nnuqart d wureɣ d warruḍen uca ffɣen, ssnuffaren aya. \add Awarni man aya\add* ɛeqben-dd, udfen ɣar ijj n uqiḍun nneɣni uca iwyen uřa ssenni \add ca\add*, uca ffɣen, ssnuffaren aya \add ɛawed\add*.  
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* nnan i wayawya: “Neccin war nᵉttegg min iǧan nican. Ass-a d ijj n wass n řexbar aṣebḥan u neccin nesseɣd. \add Mařa\add* nraja \add da\add* ař i ɣa iffu řḥař, ad aneɣ teřqef řmuɛṣiyyet. \add Xenni\add* řexxu, asem-dd, ejj aneɣ ad nuyur, ad t nɛawed di taddart n ujeǧid.”   
\m
\v 10 Nitni iwḍen \add din\add*, řaɣan x uɛessas n tewwart n tendint, ḥajan asen, nnan: “Neccin nudef ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Aram, u xzar, war din uřa d ijj, war nesři i ca n řḥess n yewdan, mɣir iysan tuɣa qqnen d yeɣyař tuɣa carfen, d iqiḍan am mammec \add ǧan\add*.”  
\v 11 Iřaɣa x iɛessasen n tewwart uca ssiwḍen nitni \add areqqas\add* ɣar daxeř n taddart n ujeǧid.   
\m
\v 12 Ikkar ujeǧid di ǧiřet, inna i imsexxaren nnes: “Necc ad awem iniɣ min akidneɣ i ɣa yegg Aram. Nitni ssnen, aqa neccin d ayt n bu-ǧuẓ. \add X uyenni\add* ffɣen zi řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, ḥima ad nuffaren deg iyyar, qqaren: ‘Mařa nitni ad ffɣen zi tendint, ad ten neṭṭef ddaren uca ad nadef ɣar tendint.’”  
\v 13 Ijjen zeg imsexxaren yarra-dd, inna: “Ejj \add iryazen\add* ad ksin xemsa n iysan nni ɛad din iǧan, inni iqqimen di tendint, \add u xenni\add* ad nẓar ma ad asen imsar am waṭṭas n ayt n Israil inni da iqqimen, \add niɣ\add* am waṭṭas n ayt n Israil inni ittwahellken. Ejj aneɣ ad ten nessekk uca xenni ad nẓar \add min i ɣa yiři\add*.”   
\m
\v 14 Ksin nitni tnayen n iysan n tazřa. Ajeǧid issekk i-ten awarni i řɛeskar n Aram, inna: “Uyurem, texzarem!”  
\v 15 Nitni ḍfaren ten ař L’Urdun, u xzar, abrid marra inti s warruḍ d řeḥwayej nni immenḍaren ayt n Aram am tuɣa ttqeǧiqen \add di tarewřa\add* nsen. Ireqqasen ɛeqben u ssiwḍen řexbar i ujeǧid.  
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ řgens \add zi tendint\add* uca keccḍen řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Aram uca temmenz ijj n řeqyas n waren azdad s yijj n ciqlu d tnayen n řeqyas n imendi s yijj n ciqlu ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 7:16 \ft \+fk řeqyas\ft  - ɛřayen 7-8 litru.\f*  
\v 17 Igga ujeǧid aneɣraf \add n řɛeskar\add* wenni x ittcař, ḥima ad yiři x tewwart, \add maca\add* iɛfes xas řgens di tewwart ařami immut am mammec tuɣa inna weryaz n AREBBI, wenni issiwřen umi tuɣa ɣares dd-ihwa ujeǧid.  
\v 18 Aqa imsar am mammec tuɣa issiweř weryaz n AREBBI i ujeǧid, i innan: “Tiwecca ɣar řweqt-a \add ad mmenzen\add* ɣar tewwart n Samarya tnayen n řeqyas n imendi s yijj n ciqlu d yijj n řeqyas n waren azdad s yijj n ciqlu.”  
\v 19 Tuɣa yarra-dd uneɣraf \add n řɛeskar\add* x weryaz n AREBBI, inna: “Xzar, waxxa mařa SIDI igga řekwaza deg ujenna, ma izemmar ad imsar uya?” U netta tuɣa inna: “Xzar, ad t tẓared s tiṭṭawin nnec, maca war zzaysen tᵉttetted.”  
\v 20 Ammu i d as temsar, \add maɣar\add* řgens iɛfes xas di tewwart. \add ařami\add* immut.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\s1 Cwar n Ilicaɛ i temɣart zi Cunam  
\m
\v 1 Řami issiweř Ilicaɛ ak-d temɣart tenni umi tuɣa issfaq mmis, inna \add as\add*: “Kkar, ffeɣ, cem ak-d twacunt nnem u zdeɣ am yict n tbarranect mani ma tzemmared ad tzedɣed, maɣar SIDI yura ict n řeḥṣaret n řaẓ tenni i ɣa yekken ɛawed sebɛa n iseggʷusa x temmurt.” \x ◘ \xo 8:1 \xt 2 Ij. 4:34\x*  
\v 2 Uca tekkar temɣart, tegga ɛlaḥsab awař n weryaz n AREBBI. Nettat teffeɣ ak-d twacunt nnes uca tezdeɣ sebɛa n iseggʷusa di temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen.   
\m
\v 3 Awarni sebɛa n iseggʷusa, imsar belli tamɣart teɛqeb-dd zi temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen. Nettat teffeɣ, ḥima ad tᵉttar twiza n ujeǧid x taddart nnes d yeyyar nnes.  
\v 4 Ajeǧid tuɣa ittḥarreḍ ak-d Jiḥazi, amsexxar n weryaz n AREBBI, inna: “Ḥaja ayi marra timesřayin timeqqranin i igga Ilicaɛ.”  
\v 5 Imsar am tuɣa ittɛawad wanita i ujeǧid x mammec dd-issfaq Ilicaɛ ijj n umettin, xzar, tusa-dd temɣart nni umi dd-issfaq mmis, ḥima ad tᵉttar twiza n ujeǧid x taddart nnes d yeyyar nnes. \add Xenni\add* inna Jiḥazi: “\add A\add* sidi inu ajeǧid, ta d tamɣart d wa d mmis i dd-issfaq Ilicaɛ ɣar tudart.”  
\v 6 Ajeǧid isseqsa tamɣart u nettat tḥaja as tt-i-dd. \add Xas uca\add* iwca as ujeǧid ijj n umsexxar amcenneɛ, inna: “Ḥḍat ad ɣares ittwarr marra min iǧan nnes uřa d marra ṣṣabet n iyyar zeg wass nni di tejja nettat tammurt ař ass-a.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ilicaɛ di Dimacq  
\m
\v 7 Ilicaɛ yusa-dd ɣar Dimacq \add umi\add* Binhadad, ajeǧid n Aram, ihřec. Ḥajan as man aya, nnan: “Aqa aryaz n AREBBI yusa-dd danita.”  
\v 8 \add Xas uca\add* inna ujeǧid i Ḥazayil: “Awi-dd akidek ict n terzeft, ruḥ ad teřqid aryaz n AREBBI uca seqsa zzayes SIDI, ad tinid: “Ma necc ad ggenfiɣ zi řehřac-a?” \x ◘ \xo 8:8 \xt 1 Ij. 14:2, 3; 2 Ij. 1:2\x*  
\v 9 Ḥazayil yuyur ad t iřqa uca yiwi akides ict n terzeft, ɛřam kuř n min iǧan d lemliḥ zi Dimacq, ijj n ddqeř n arebɛin n iřeɣman. Netta yiweḍ u ibedd zzates, inna: “Mmic Binhadad, ajeǧid n Aram, issekk ayi-dd ɣarek, maḥend ad sseqsiɣ: ‘Ma ad ggenfiɣ zi řehřac-a?’”  
\v 10 Inna as Ilicaɛ: “Uyur, ad tinid: ‘Cek war teggenfid ca kuřci!’ SIDI isscen ayi, aqa netta ad immet nican.”   
\m
\v 11 Udem nnes ibɛar u isseqseḥ dayes tamuɣři ařami war issin min ɣa yegg. \add Xenni ibda\add* weryaz n AREBBI ittru.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* inna Ḥazayil: “Mayemmi ittru sidi inu?” Netta inna: “Minzi necc ssneɣ řeḥřiq i d ɣa tawyed cek i ayt n Israil. Cek ad teqqded timessi i lqelɛat nsen, ad tenɣed iḥudriyyen nsen s ssif, ad třebzed iḥenjiren nsen u timɣarin nsen i iksin s ddeyset ad asent tcarrged aɛeddis.” \x ◘ \xo 8:12 \xt 2 Ij. 10:32; 12:17; 13:7\x*  
\v 13 Ḥazayil inna: “Maɣar min iɛna umsexxar nnec, aqzin nni, aqa netta izemmar ad igg řḥajjet d tameqqrant am tanita?” Ilicaɛ inna: “SIDI isscen ayi-dd belli ad tiřid d ajeǧid x Aram.”  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* iggʷej netta x Ilicaɛ, uca yusa-dd ɣar sidis. Wanita inna as: “Min d ac inna Ilicaɛ?” U netta yarra-dd: “Netta inna ayi: ‘Aqa cek ad teggenfid!’”  
\v 15 Tiwecca nnes imsar aqa iksi netta ict n malta, isseɣḍeṣ i-tt deg waman uca issars i-tt x uɣembub nnes ařami immut. Uca idweř Ḥazayil d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yuram, ajeǧid n Yahuda  
\m
\v 16 Deg useggʷas wiss xemsa n Yuram, mmis n Axab, ajeǧid n Israil, umi tuɣa Yahucafat d ajeǧid n Yahuda, idweř Yahuram, mmis n Yahucafaṭ, d ajeǧid n Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 8:16 \xt [2 Im. 21:2-20] — 2 Im. 21:4, 5\x*  
\v 17 Netta \add tuɣa\add* ɣares tnayen u-třatin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem tmenya n iseggʷusa di Urcalim.  
\v 18 Netta yuyur deg webrid n ijeǧiden n Israil, am mammec tuɣa tegga taddart n Axab, maɣar yeǧis n Axab tedweř d tamɣart nnes. Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI.  
\v 19 \add Maca\add* SIDI war ixs ad yareddeǧ Yahuda di ṭṭweɛ n umsexxar nnes Dawud, am mammec d as tuɣa inna, ad as iwc řebda ijj n řefnar zzat i tiṭṭawin nnes di ṭṭweɛ n warrawen nnes. \x ◘ \xo 8:19 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:13; 1 Ij. 11:36; 15:4; Izhd. 132:17\x*   
\m
\v 20 Deg wussan nnes izemmar Idum ad ixtutteř zeg ifassen n Yahuda umi ɣewwɣen, u nitni ggin ijj n ujeǧid x yixef nsen. \x ◘ \xo 8:20 \xt Amz. 27:40; 2 Im. 21:8\x*  
\v 21 \add Xas uca\add* iɛdu Yahuram ak-d marra ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add* nnes ɣar Ṣaɛir. Uca imsar aqa ikkar s ǧiřet uca ihjem x ayt n Idum inni tuɣa i d as dd-innḍen i netta u i imeqqranen n ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add*, \add maca\add* řgens yarweř ɣar iqiḍan nnes.  
\v 22 \add S uyenni\add*, xtuttřen ayt n Idum s uɣewweɣ zi jar ifassen n Yahuda ař ass-a. Di řweqt nni beɛda iɣewweɣ uřa d Libna.   
\m
\v 23 Imezruyen i iqqimen n Yahuram, d marra min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda?  
\v 24 Yahuram igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Netta ittwanḍeř jar řejdud nnes di tendint n Dawud. Mmis, Axazya, idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes. \x ◘ \xo 8:24 \xt 2 Im. 21:19\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Axazya, ajeǧid n Yahuda  
\m
\v 25 Deg useggʷas wiss tenɛac n Yuram, mmis n Axab, ajeǧid n Israil, ibda Axazya, mmis n Yahuram, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ad iḥkem. \x ◘ \xo 8:25 \xt [2 Im. 22:1-6] — 2 Im. 22:1\x*  
\v 26 Axazya \add tuɣa\add* ɣares tnayen u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem ijj n useggʷas di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Ɛatalya, yeǧis n Ɛumri, ajeǧid n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 8:26 \xt 2 Im. 22:2\x*  
\v 27 Netta yuyur deg webrid n taddart n Axab u igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, am taddart n Axab, maɣar tuɣa d aḍeggʷař n taddart n Axab.   
\m
\v 28 Iffeɣ \add Axazya\add* ak-d Yuram, mmis n Axab, i umenɣi ak-d Ḥazayil, ajeǧid n Aram, ɣar Ramut di Jilɛad, \add maca\add* ayt n Aram ɣeřben x Yuram.  
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* yareggʷeḥ ujeǧid Yuram, maḥend ad yarzu di Yazraɛil agenfu zeg iyezzimen nni i d as ggin \add ayt n\add* Aram umi immneɣ netta di Ramut ak-d ujeǧid nsen Ḥazayil, ajeǧid n Aram. Axazya, mmis n Yahuram, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ihwa-dd \add din\add*, ḥima ad issijj x Yuram, mmis n Axab, di Yazraɛil, umi tuɣa ihřec netta. \x ◘ \xo 8:29 \xt 2 Ij. 9:15; 22:6, 7\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\s1 Yahu idweř d ajeǧid x Israil  
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* anabi Ilicaɛ iřaɣa-dd i yijjen zeg ayt n inabiyyen, inna as: “Byes, ksi aɣarraf-a n zzect deg ufus nnec uca tuyured ɣar Ramut \add di\add* Jilɛad. \x ◘ \xo 9:1 \xt 1 Ij. 19:16\x*  
\v 2 \add Xmi\add* dinni i ɣa tawḍed, arzu x Yahu, mmis n Yahucafaṭ, mmis n Nimci. Adef \add ɣares\add* uca ejj i-t ad dd-ikkar zi řwesṭ n yaytmas, ndeh i-t ɣar ijj n wexxam iṭṭurfiy mliḥ.  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* ksi aɣarraf n zzect, zeǧeɛ i-t x uzeǧif nnes uca ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Necc dehneɣ cek d ajeǧid x Israil.’ \add Xenni\add* arzem tawwart, arweř, war ttriji ɛad ktar!” \x ◘ \xo 9:3 \xt 2 Im. 22:7\x*   
\m
\v 4 Aḥudri, amsexxar n unabi, yuyur deg webrid ɣar Ramut \add di\add* Jilɛad.  
\v 5 \add Umi\add* \add din\add* dd-yiweḍ, xzar, ikumandaren n řɛeskar tuɣa qqimen dinni. Netta inna: “Necc ɣari ijj n wawař i cek, \add a\add* řqebṭan. Yahu isseqsa: “I man wen zzayneɣ marra?” Netta inna: “I cek, \add a\add* řqebṭan!”  
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Yahu, yudef ɣar taddart. U netta ifarreɣ as zzect x uzeǧif nnes, inna as: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Necc dehneɣ cek d ajeǧid x řgens n SIDI, x Israil.  
\v 7 Cek ad tewted taddart n Axab, sidi nnec, u necc ad ttareɣ zeg ufus n Izabil idammen n imsexxaren inu, inabiyyen, uřa d idammen n marra imsexxaren n SIDI.  
\v 8 Marra taddart n Axab ad tᵉttwakkes, u Necc ad qḍiɣ zi taddart n Axab marra wi t itteggen x řḥiḍ, \add am\add* wenni ittwaṭṭfen, \add am\add* wenni umi jjin di Israil. \x ◘ \xo 9:8 \xt 1 Ij. 21:21\x*  
\v 9 Necc ad arreɣ taddart n Axab amecnaw taddart n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, u am taddart n Baɛca, mmis n Axiya. \x ◘ \xo 9:9 \xt 1 Ij. 14:10; 15:29; 16:3, 11\x*  
\v 10 Iṭan ad ccen Izabil deg iyyar n Yazraɛil uca war ittiři uřa d ijj wenni tt i ɣa ineḍřen.” \add Xenni\add* yarzem netta tawwart uca yarweř.’” \x ◘ \xo 9:10 \xt 1 Ij. 21:23\x*  
\v 11 Umi dd-iffeɣ Yahu ɣar barra ɣar imsexxaren n sidis, nnan as: “Aqa cek mliḥ? Mayemmi i ɣarek dd-yusa ubuhaři-ya?” Netta yarra-dd xasen: “Kenniw tessnem aryaz d řhard nnes!”  
\v 12 \add Maca\add* nitni nnan “D ixarriqen, ini aneɣ \add t\add*!” \add xenni\add* inna: “Ammu d wammu i kidi issiweř, inna: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Necc dehneɣ cek d ajeǧid x Israil.’”  
\v 13 \add Řexdenni\add* qeǧqen u kuř ijj iksi arruḍ nnes uca issars i-t sadu \add iḍaren\add* nnes x tareddifin n ddruj uca suḍen deg uyicc n icarri, nnan: “Yahu d ajeǧid!”   
\m
\v 14 Yahu, mmis n Yahucafaṭ, mmis n Nimci, igga ijj n řɛahd ḍidd Yuram. Yuram, netta \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d marra Israil, tuɣa iḥḍa x Ramut \add di\add* Jilɛad arendad n wudem n Ḥazayil, ajeǧid n Aram.  
\v 15 \add Maca\add* ajeǧid Yuram yareggʷeḥ-dd, maḥend ad yarzu di Yazraɛil agenfu zeg iyezzimen i d as tuɣa ggin \add ayt n\add* Aram, umi immneɣ ak-d Ḥazayil, ajeǧid n Aram. Yahu inna: “Mařa kenniw tᵉttafqem, \add xenni\add* war ttejjim ad yarweř uřa d ijj zi tendint, ad yuyur maḥend ad issiweḍ řexbar-a ɣar Yazraɛil.” \x ◘ \xo 9:15 \xt 2 Ij. 8:29\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řmewt n ujeǧid Yuram d ujeǧid Ahazya d tjeǧidt Izabil  
\m
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* inya \add deg ukarru nnes\add*, indeh ɣar Yazraɛil, maɣar dinni i tuɣa Yuram. Axazya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, tuɣa ihwa-dd, ḥima ad issijj x Yuram.  
\v 17 Aɛessas ibedd x ṣṣumɛet di Yazraɛil uca iẓra Yahu yusa-dd, inna: “Necc ttwařiɣ ijj n uhimur.” \add Xenni\add* inna Yuram: “Awi-dd ijj n bu-uyis uca ssekk i-t-i-dd i umsagar akidsen, ad yini: “Ma d řehna \add min xef dd-tusid\add*?”  
\v 18 Bu-uyis inya, ḥima ad t iřqa, inna: “Ammu i iqqar ujeǧid: ‘Ma d řehna \add min xef dd-tusid\add*?’” \add Maca\add* Yahu yarra-dd \add xas\add*: “Mani cek icqa řehna? As-dd ɣar ḍeffar inu.” Aɛessas iɛřem \add aya\add*, inna: “Amsexxar yiweḍ ɣarsen, \add maca\add* war dd-iɛqib ca.”  
\v 19 Issekk ujeǧid ijj n bu-uyis wiss tnayen. \add Umi\add* dd-yusa wanita ɣarsen, inna: “Ammu i iqqar ujeǧid: ‘Ma d řehna \add min xef dd-tusid\add*?’” \add Maca\add* Yahu yarra-dd \add xas\add*: “Mani cek icqa řehna. As-dd ɣar ḍeffar inu.”  
\v 20 Aɛessas iɛřem \add s man aya\add* ɛawed: “Netta yiweḍ i-ten, \add maca\add* war dd-iɛqib ca u mammec ineddeh ayis, igga am mammec ittegg Yahu, mmis n Nimci, maɣar netta ineddeh am ineddeh ijj n ubuhaři.”   
\m
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* inna Yuram: “Ḥezzem akarru!” Ḥezzmen akarru nnes u Yuram, ajeǧid n Israil, iffeɣ ak-d Axazya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, nedhen kuř ijj akarru nnes. Nitni ffɣen i umsagar ak-d Yahu uca ufin t ɣar yeyyar n Nabut, Ayazraɛili.  
\v 22 Imsar umi iẓra Yuram Yahu, inna: “Ma d řehna \add i xef dd-tusid\add*, \add a\add* Yahu?” \add Maca\add* wanita yarra-dd: “Mana řehna-ya min ɣa yekk farq-ccɣeř n yemmac Izabil d tseḥḥarin nnes \add ammu\add* s waṭṭas?”  
\v 23 Inneqřeb Yuram, ḥima ad yarweř, uca inna i Axazya: “Tamenziwt, Axazya!”  
\v 24 Maca Yahu imneɛ řqews nnes deg ufus uca iřqef Yuram \add s fřitca\add* jar iɣaǧen nnes. Fřitca tesnuqqeb qaɛ uř nnes uca iwḍa netta deg ukarru nnes.  
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* inna Yahu i Bidkar, aneɣraf nnes \add n řɛeskar\add*: “Ksi t uca nḍar i-t di tesɣart n yeyyar n Nabut, Ayazraɛili. Ɛqeř, necc d cek, ijj ɣar uɣezdis n wenneɣni, aqa nedhen \add x ikarruten nneɣ\add* awarni i babas Axab umi xas icetca SIDI ammu, \add inna\add*:  
\v 26 ‘S tidett am ẓriɣ iḍennaḍ idammen n Nabut d iḥenjiren nnes, iqqar SIDI, ammu i zzayek ten ɣa xeřfeɣ x yeyyar-a, issawař SIDI.’ Xenni řexxu, ksi t uca nḍar i-t deg iyyar ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 9:26 \xt 1 Ij. 21:19\x*   
\m
\v 27 \add Umi\add* Axazya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, iẓra \add aya\add*, iṭṭef abrid ɣar Bayt-Hagan. Yahu iḍfar i-t u \add řami yiweḍ\add* ɣar teysart n Jur nni iǧan ɣar Jibliɛam, inna: “Wwet i-t uřa d netta x ukarru!” \add Xenni\add* yarweř netta ɣar Majiddu uca immut din. \x ◘ \xo 9:27 \xt 2 Im. 22:7-9\x*  
\v 28 Imsexxaren nnes iwyen t \add x ukarru\add* ɣar Urcalim uca neḍřen t deg wenḍeř nnes jar řejdud nnes di tendint n Dawud.  
\v 29 Deg useggʷas wiss ḥiṭac n Yuram, mmis n Axab, tuɣa idweř Axazya d ajeǧid x Yahuda.   
\b  
\m
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd Yahu ɣar Yazraɛil. \add Řami\add* tt tesřa Izabil, tkeḥḥeř tiṭṭawin nnes, tzewweq acuwwaf nnes uca texzar zi řkazi ɣar swadday.  
\v 31 \add Umi\add* dd-yudef Yahu zi tawwart, tenna: “Ma d řehna \add i xef dd-tusid\add*, Zimri, \add a cek\add* wenni inɣin sidis?” \f ◼ \fr 9:31 \ft \+fk aneqqam\ft  - aqa-t d aryaz wenni inɣin ijj n bnadem.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 9:31 \xt 1 Ij. 16:18\x*  
\v 32 Netta ixzar ɣar řkazi sennej, inna: “Wi akidi iǧan? Man Wen?” \add Xenni\add* xzaren tnayen niɣ třata n imsexxaren icennɛen ɣares \add din\add* swadday.  
\v 33 Netta inna \add asen\add*: “Nḍarem tt-i-dd swadday!” Nitni nḍaren-tt-i-dd swadday ařami idammen nnes ttwaruccen x řḥiḍ u x yeysan, u netta iřbez i-tt.  
\v 34 Netta yudef uca icca, iswa. \add Awarni uya\add* inna: “Xzarem ɣar tmexziwt nni u neḍřem tt, maɣar nettat d yeǧis n ujeǧid.” \x ◘ \xo 9:34 \xt 1 Ij. 16:31\x*  
\v 35 Nitni uyuren, ḥima ad tt neḍřen, \add maca\add* nitni war tt ufin ca mɣir taceqquft n uzeǧif d iḍaren d ifassen waha.  
\v 36 \add Umi\add* dd-ɛeqben, ɛawden as \add t\add* u netta yarra-dd: “Wa d awař n SIDI nni issiwiř s uqemmum n umsexxar nnes, Ilicaɛ Aticbi. Netta inna: ‘X yeyyar n Yazraɛil iṭan ad ccen aysum \add n řxecbet\add* n Izabil. \x ◘ \xo 9:36 \xt 1 Ij. 21:23\x*  
\v 37 Řxecbet n Izabil ad tiři am řeɣbar x yeyyar deg weḥwic n Yazraɛil, ař ɣa taf war din wi ɣa inin: Ta d Izabil.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\s1 Yahu inɣa řaǧ n Axab  
\m
\v 1 Axab tuɣa ɣares sebɛin n iḥenjiren di Samarya. Yahu yura tibratin, issekk \add i-tent\add* ɣar Samarya i imeqqranen n Yazraɛil, i imɣaren u i yinni yarebban \add iḥenjiren n\add* Axab. \add Daysent\add* inna:  
\v 2 “Mařa řexxu tabrat-a tusa-dd ɣarwem, \add am\add* ɣarwem iḥenjiren n siditwem řa d ikarruten d yeysan, d ict n tendint ifaryen d řesnaḥ,  
\v 3 arzum \add xenni\add* x yinni iṣebḥen d inni imeḥḍen qaɛ jar iḥenjiren n siditwem u sɣimem \add t\add* x řɛarc n babas u wtem di ṭṭweɛ n taddart n siditwem.”  
\v 4 \add Maca\add* nitni dewřen tteggʷeden aṭṭas, nnan: “Xzar, tnayen n ijeǧiden war zemmaren ad qqimen bedden zzates, mammec \add i ɣa nzemmar neccin\add* ad neqqim nbedd?”  
\v 5 Inni iǧan x taddart u x tendint, imɣaren d yinni yarebban \add iḥenjiren n Axab\add*, ssekken \add ijj n ureqqas\add* ɣar Yahu, nnan: “Neccin d imsexxaren nnec, u marra min d aneɣ ɣa tinid, ad \add t\add* negg. Neccin war nᵉttegg uřa d ijj d ajeǧid. Egg min tᵉttwařid nican di tiṭṭawin nnec.”   
\m
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* yura ɣarsen ict n tebrat i twařa wiss tnayen, inna: “Mařa aqa kenniw ɣar uɣezdis inu, ad tesřem ɣar min ɣa iniɣ, ksim \add xenni\add* izeǧifen n iḥenjiren n siditwem, u asem-dd tiwecca ammu ɣar řweqt-a ɣari di Yazraɛil.” Iḥenjiren n ujeǧid, sebɛin n yeryazen, \add tuɣa zeddɣen\add* ɣar imcennɛen n tendint, inni ten yarebban.  
\v 7 Umi ɣarsen dd-tiweḍ tebrat, imsar, belli nitni ṭṭfen iḥenjiren n ujeǧid, nɣin ten \add marra\add*, sebɛin n yeryazen. Nitni ggin izeǧifen nsen di řkurbat uca ssekken tent ɣares ɣar Yazraɛil.  
\v 8 Yusa-dd umsexxar, issiweḍ areqqas, inna: “Aqa iwyen-dd izeǧifen n iḥenjiren n ujeǧid.” Netta yarra-dd: “Sarsem ten ař tiwecca di tnayen n iɛurrac ɣar wadaf n tewwart.”  
\v 9 Ɣar tiwecca, umi iffeɣ ɣar barra, imsar, aqa ibedd \add din\add*, inna i marra řgens: “Kenniw d imseggaden. Xzarem, d necc i iggin ict n tmeɛmuč x sidi inu u nɣiɣ t. \add Maca\add* wi inɣin marra ina?  
\v 10 Snem, aqa war iweṭṭi ɣar temmurt uřa d ijj n wawař n SIDI nni inna SIDI ḍidd i taddart n Axab, maɣar SIDI igga min tuɣa inna s uqemmum n umsexxar nnes Ilicaɛ.” \f ◼ \fr 10:10 \ft \+fk s uqemmum\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘s ufus’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 10:10 \xt 1 Ij. 21:19, 21, 29\x*  
\v 11 Yahu inɣa marra wi iqqimen zi taddart n Axab di Yazraɛil uřa d marra imcennɛen nnes d imeddukkař nnes d ikehhanen nnes, ařami war ijji ad zzayes iqqim uřa d ijj n umarweř.   
\m
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* ikkar uca iṭṭef abrid ɣar Samarya. Umi t tuɣa netta deg webrid, \add imsar di\add* taddart n umeřqi n imeksawen, \f ◼ \fr 10:12 \ft \+fk imeksawen\ft  - niɣ iničan’.\f*  
\v 13 aqa immeřqa Yahu ak-d awmaten n Axazya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, inna: “Min teɛnam kenniw?” Nitni arrin-dd: “Neccin d awmaten n Axazya u nehwa-dd, ḥima ad nseǧem x iḥenjiren n ujeǧid d iḥenjiren n tjeǧidt.” \x ◘ \xo 10:13 \xt 2 Im. 22:8\x*  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* inna: “Ṭṭfem ten ddaren!” Ṭṭfen ten ddaren u nɣin ten ɣar wanu n taddart n imeksawen. \add Tuɣa-ten\add* di tnayen u arebɛin n yeryazen. War ijji uřa d ijj zzaysen iddar.  
\v 15 Netta iffeɣ ssenni uca yufa Yunadab, mmis n Rikab, wenni dd-iffɣen i umsagar akides. Netta iseǧem xas, inna as: “Ma uř nnec iseggem \add akidi\add* am mammec iseggem wuř inu akidek?” Yunadab yarra-dd xas: “Amenni, amenni! Ewc \add ayi-dd\add* afus nnec.” Netta iwca as afus uca ijja i-t ad dd-iniy ɣares deg ukarru.  
\v 16 Netta inna: “As-dd akidi uca ad tẓared asam inu i SIDI.” \add Ammu i\add* jjin t ad dd-iniy akides deg ukarru.  
\v 17 \add Umi\add* yiweḍ ɣar Samarya, inɣa netta marra inni tuɣa iqqimen n Axab di Samarya, ařami t iqḍa qaɛ am mammec inna wawař n SIDI nni tuɣa inna i Ilicaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 10:17 \xt 2 Im. 22:8\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yahu iqḍa x weɛbed n Baɛal  
\m
\v 18 Yahu issmun marra řgens uca inna asen: “Axab tuɣa isexxar i Baɛal cwayt, \add maca\add* Yahu ad as isexxar aṭṭas \add ɛad\add*.  
\v 19 Xenni řexxu, řaɣam-dd x marra inabiyyen n Baɛal d marra imsexxaren nnes d marra ikehhanen nnes, \add maḥend ad\add* ɣari \add dd-asen\add*. Ḥḍam aqa ad iqqim ḥed, minzi ɣari ict n tɣarṣt d tameqqrant i Baɛal. Marra wi ɣa iɣaben, war ittɣimi iddar.” Yahu \add maca\add* igga ta s tḥraymect, maḥend ad iqḍa x imsexxaren n Baɛal.  
\v 20 \add Xas uca\add* inna Yahu: “Sqeddsem ijj n umuni ifarzen i Baɛal!” Uca nitni barrḥen i man aya.  
\v 21 Issekk Yahu \add ireqqasen\add* di marra Israil u marra imsexxaren n Baɛal usin-dd, war iqqim uřa d ijj war dd-yusi. Nitni udfen ɣar zzawect n Baɛal ařami teccur zzawect n Baɛal zi ṭṭarf ař ṭṭarf.  
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* inna i wenni iǧan x wexxam n warruḍ: “Awi-dd arruḍen i marra imsexxaren n Baɛal!” U wanita yiwi asen-dd arruḍen.   
\m
\v 23 Yudef Yahu ak-d Yunadab, mmis n Rikab, ɣar zzawect n Baɛal u netta inna i imsexxaren n Baɛal: “Xzarem mliḥ, aqa war ɣarwem ittiři uřa d ijj zeg imsexxaren n SIDI, mɣir imsexxaren n Baɛal waha.”  
\v 24 \add Umi\add* iwḍen, maḥend ad \add din\add* awyen tiɣarṣa d tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ, tuɣa issbedd Yahu tmenyin n yeryazen i yixef nnes di barra, inna: “Zeg weryaz nni i ɣa yejj ad injem ijj zeg yeryazen nni ggiɣ deg ifassen nwem, ad \add idweř\add* řeɛmar nnes deg wemcan n řeɛmar nni.”   
\m
\v 25 \add Řami\add* iqfeř usewjed n tɣarṣṭ n wecmaḍ, imsar belli netta inna i ireqqasem n tazřa u i řqebṭanat: “Adfem, wtem ten, war ttejjim uřa d ijj ad injem!” Nitni nɣin ten s řeqḍeɛ n ssif u řqebṭanat nḍaren ten \add barra\add*. Nitni udfen ɣar uř n zzawect n Baɛal.  
\v 26 Nitni kksen imayḍuten \add iqeddsen\add* zi zzawect n Baɛal uca ssarɣen ten.  
\v 27 Nitni arẓin ameyḍa \add iqeddsen\add* n Baɛal. Hedmen \add ɛawed\add* zzawect n Baɛal uca ggin tt d ict n tzubact ař ass-a.  
\v 28 \add Ammu i\add* imḥa Yahu Baɛal zi Israil.  
\v 29 Maca Yahu war ibedd zeg weḍfar n ddnub n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, wenni yarrin Israil ad ixḍa: iɛejmiyyen n wureɣ nni \add iǧan\add* di Bayt-Il. \f ◼ \fr 10:29 \ft \+fk iɛejmiyyen\ft  - niɣ ‘iyenduzen’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 10:29 \xt 1 Ij. 12:28\x*   
\m
\v 30 SIDI inna i Yahu: “Minzi teggid nican umi teggid min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin inu, uca teggid ak-d taddart n Axab marra min ɣari deg wuř, ad qqimen iḥenjiren nwem x řɛarc n Israil ař jjiř wiss arebɛa.” \x ◘ \xo 10:30 \xt 2 Ij. 15:12\x*  
\v 31 \add Maca\add* Yahu war iḥḍi ca maḥend ad yuyur ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa n SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, s marra uř nnes. Netta war iḥeyyed x ddnub n Yarubɛam wenni yarrin Israil ad ixḍa.   
\m
\v 32 Deg wussan nni ibda SIDI ad issemẓi Israil. Ḥazayil iwta i-ten di marra tammurt n Israil,  
\v 33 zi L’Urdun manis dd-tneqqar tfuct, marra \add tammurt n\add* Jilɛad, \add tammurt\add* n Ijadiyyen d Irubiniyyen d Imanassiyyen, zi Aruɛir wenni \add iǧan\add* ɣar teɣzart n Arnun, uřa d Jilɛad d Bacan.   
\m
\v 34 Imezruyen iqqimen n Yahu, d marra min igga d marra timegga nnes imeḥḍen, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil?  
\v 35 Yahu igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Neḍřen t di Samarya. Mmis Yahuyaḥaz idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.  
\v 36 Ussan i di tuɣa Yahu iḥekkem di Samarya aqa aten di tmenya u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\s1 Akehhan Yahuyadaɛ yumur ḥima ad nɣen Atalya  
\m
\v 1 Umi Ɛatalya, yemmas n Axazya, teẓra, aqa mmis immut, tegga ad teqḍa x marra tarrawt \add n řaǧ\add* n ujeǧid. \x ◘ \xo 11:1 \xt [2 Im. 22:10-12; 23:1-21] — 2 Im. 22:10\x*  
\v 2 Maca Yahuciba, yeǧis n ujeǧid Yahuram, učmas n Axazya, teksi Yuwac, mmis n Axazya, s tnuffra zi jar iḥenjiren n ujeǧid nni ittwanɣen uca \add tiwyi\add* t ak-d temɣart i t issuṭṭuḍen deg wexxam n tassut uca tessnuffar i-t \add dinni\add* zi Ɛatalya, \add ḥima\add* war ittwaneqq.  
\v 3 Netta iqqim inuffar akides setta n iseggʷusa di Taddart n SIDI, \add umi\add* teḥkem Ɛatalya x temmurt.   
\m
\v 4 Deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa issekk Yahuyadaɛ uca ijja ad dd-asen imeqqranen x mya n iɛessasen n arrimet u n ireqqasen n tazřa uca issmun i-ten ɣares di Taddart n SIDI. Netta igga akidsen ijj n řɛahd, ijja i-ten ad jjaǧen di Taddart n SIDI. \add Xas uca\add* isscen asen mmis n ujeǧid. \x ◘ \xo 11:4 \xt 2 Im. 23:1\x*  
\v 5 Netta yumur i-ten, inna: “D man aya i ɣa teggem: ict n ttuřut nwem, inni i ɣa yadfen deg \add wass n\add* ssebt, ad ɛessen ɣar taddart n ujeǧid.  
\v 6 Ict n ttuřut \add ad tbedd\add* ɣar tewwart n Ṣur u ict n ttuřut ɣar tewwart awarni i ireqqasen n tazřa. \add Ammu\add* i ɣa tɛessem x taddart di tnubbat.  
\v 7 Tnayen n izeynat nwem, zi marra inni i ɣa iffɣen di ssebt, ad ḥḍan ɣar Taddart n SIDI, ɣar ujeǧid.  
\v 8 Kenniw ad tennḍem i ujeǧid, \add kuř\add* aryaz s řesnaḥ nnes deg ufus nnes, u wenni i ɣa yarzun ad yadef jar řeṣfuf ad ittwaneɣ. Ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad teqqimen ak-d ujeǧid mařa netta iffeɣ niɣ mařa yudef.   
\m
\v 9 Imeqqranen x mya ggin am mammec iweṣṣa ukehhan Yahuyadaɛ uca kuř ijj zzaysen yiwi akides iryazen nnes inni yudfen deg wass n ssebt, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d yinni iffɣen deg wass n ssebt uca usin-dd ɣar ukehhan Yahuyadaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 11:9 \xt 2 Im. 23:8\x*  
\v 10 I imeqqranen n mya iwca ukehhan lansat d tseddariyin iqesḥen n řɛeskar i tuɣa iǧan n ujeǧid Dawud, tinni \add tuɣa iǧan\add* di Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 11 Ireqqasen n tazřa bedden s řesnaḥ deg ufus zeg uɣezdis afusi n wudem n Taddart ař aɣezdis azeřmaḍ n wudem n Taddart, ɣar uɛalṭar u ɣar Taddart, \add ammu\add* quwwaren-dd i ujeǧid.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* issuffeɣ-dd mmis n ujeǧid ɣar barra uca igga as ttaj \add n weɛzař\add* \add x uzeǧif\add* uca iwca as Cchadet. \add Ammu\add* i t ggin d ajeǧid, dehnen t. Nitni wtin deg ifassen, nnan: “Tudart i ujeǧid!”   
\m
\v 13 \add Umi\add* tesřa Ɛatalya řḥess n ireqqasen n tazřa d wenni n řgens, tusa-dd nettat ɣar řgens ɣar Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 14 Teẓra, u xzar, ajeǧid ibedd ɣar upilar am mammec teǧa di lqaɛida, uca ikumandaren \add n řɛeskar\add* d inni iṣuden di řebwaq \add bedden\add* ɣar ujeǧid. Marra řgens n temmurt ifraḥ u isuḍ di řebwaq. \add Xenni\add* tcarreg Ɛatalya arruḍ nnes, tesɣuy: “Tamenziwt, tamenziwt!”  
\v 15 \add Maca\add* yumur ukehhan Yahuyadaɛ i imeqqranen x mya, inni tuɣa iǧan x řɛeskar, inna asen: “Awyem tt jar iseddiyyen \add n řɛeskar\add* ɣar barra uca nɣem wi tt ɣa iḍfaren s ssif.” Maɣar akehhan tuɣa inna: “War tt ttejji ad tᵉttwaneɣ di Taddart n SIDI.”  
\v 16 Nitni ssarsen xas ifassen, uca řami truḥ x webrid n wadaf n iysan ɣar taddart n ujeǧid, nɣin tt dinni. \f ◼ \fr 11:16 \ft \+fk ifassen\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘s ifassen nsen’.\f*   
\m
\v 17 Yahuyadaɛ igga ijj n řɛahd jar SIDI d ujeǧid d řgens, ḥima ad iřin d ijj n řgens i SIDI, uca \add netta igga uřa d ijj n řɛahd\add* jar ujeǧid d řgens. \x ◘ \xo 11:17 \xt 2 Im. 23:16\x*  
\v 18 \add Xas uca\add* yudef marra řgens n temmurt ɣar taddart \add n zzawect\add* n Baɛal u hedmen tt. Iɛalṭaren nnes d řexyařat nnes arẓin ten qaɛ. U nitni nɣin Mattan, akehhan n Baɛal, zzat i iɛalṭaren. Akehhan yařeqqem imeḥḍayen x Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 19 Netta yiwi \add akides\add* imeqqranen x mya d iɛessasen n arrimet d ireqqasen n tazřa d marra řgens n temmurt u nitni ssehwan ajeǧid zi Taddart n SIDI uca kkin x webrid n Tewwart n Ireqqasen n Tazřa tenni ɣar taddart n ujeǧid, u dinni iqqim x řɛarc n ijeǧiden.  
\v 20 Marra řgens n temmurt ifarḥ uca tarsa tendint. Aqa nɣin Ɛatalya s ssif ɣar taddart n ujeǧid.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 12
\s1 Yuwac, ajeǧid n Yahuda  
\m
\v 1 Tuɣa ɣar Yuwac sebɛa n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid.\x ◘ \xo 12:1 \xt [2 Im. 24:1-27]\x*  
\v 2 Deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa n Yahu idweř Yuwac d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem arebɛin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Ḍibya zi Bi’r-Sebɛa. \x ◘ \xo 12:2 \xt 2 Im. 24:1\x*  
\v 3 Yuwac igga min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, marra ussan min ikka ukehhan Yahuyadaɛ isseřmed i-t.  
\v 4 War ttwakksent mɣir řegɛudi. Uca řgens tuɣa ittqeddem ɛad tiɣarṣa d tewhibin n řebxur x řegɛudi \add nni\add*.  
\v 5 Yuwac inna i ikehhanen: “Marra nnuqart n tewhibin iqeddsen nni i ɣa yiwyen di Taddart n SIDI, řa nnuqart i kuř řeɛmar i iɛeddun \add ɣar inni ittwaḥesben\add*, \add řa\add* nnuqart n kuř řeɛmar ɛlaḥsab aqeddar nnes uca uřa marra nnuqart i x dd-yusa deg wuř n ijj n weryaz ḥima ad tt yawi ɣar Taddart n SIDI, \x ◘ \xo 12:5 \xt 2 Ij. 22:3-21\x*  
\v 6 ad tt ksin ikehhanen i yixef nsen, \add kuř\add* aryaz zeg inni issen. Uca nitni ad \add zzayes\add* areqqɛen \add řeḥyuḍ\add* ihruran n Taddart, marra min din ittwafen \add n řeḥyuḍ\add* ihruran.”  
\v 7 Deg useggʷas wiss třata u-ɛicrin n ujeǧid Yuwac war ɛeddřen ikehhanen \add ɛad\add* řeḥyuḍ ihruran n Taddart.  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa ujeǧid Yuwac i ukehhan Yahuyadaɛ u i ikehhanen \add inneɣni\add*, inna asen: “Mayemmi war tɛeddřem řeḥyuḍ icarrgen n Taddart? \add Xenni\add* řexxu, war tkessim \add ɛad\add* nnuqart i dd-ittasen zeg inni tessnem, mɣir ḥima ad tt tessiwḍem i weɛdař n min icarrgen \add di řeḥyuḍ\add* di Taddart.”   
\m
\v 9 Qebřen ikehhanen, maḥend war kessin ɛad nnuqart zi řgens u maḥend war \add ḥdijen ca ɛad\add* ad ɛedřen řeḥyuḍ iqeṭṭsen n Taddart.  
\v 10 Akehhan Yahuyadaɛ iksi ict n tsenduqt, igga ijj n unuqqib di tqebbart nnes uca issars i-tt zzat i uɛalṭar ɣar yefus n kuř ijj n wenni ittadfen Taddart n SIDI, uca ikehhanen, inni iḥḍan x wadaf \add ɣar Taddart\add*, ggin dayes marra nnuqart i dd-ittwawyen di Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 11 Umi ẓrin aqa din aṭṭas n nnuqart di tsenduqt, imsar aqa igeɛɛed umarir n ujeǧid ak-d arrays n ikehhanen. Nitni ssmunen tt di txuncay uca weznen nnuqart nni ittwafen di Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 12 Nitni wcin \add řqedd\add* iweznen n nnuqart deg ufus n yinni iggin řxedmet, i imeḥḍayen n Taddart n SIDI. U nitni wcin tt \add ɛawed\add* i ineqqacen \add n ukeccuḍ\add* u i ibennayen nni tuɣa ixeddmen di Taddart n SIDI,  
\v 13 u i imaṣṣuten d isuydayen, u i tmesɣiwt n ukeccuḍ d tṣuḍar yuydan itteḥwajan i wareqqeɛ n min iqeṭṭsen \add zi řeḥyuḍ\add* di Taddart n SIDI, u i marra min seyyaren i wareqqeɛ n taddart.  
\v 14 Mɣir war ttwaggen ṭṭbaṣi n nnuqart řa tjeqqaḍin, řa ṭṭawyat i urucci d řebwaq, uřa d řeqcuɛ n wureɣ d nnuqart, zi nnuqart i dd-iwyen \add iwdan\add* di Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 15 maɣar nitni wcin tt marra i yinni iggin řxedmet uca nitni areqqɛen zzayes Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 16 War mmseḥsiben ca ak-d yeryazen nni umi wcin nnuqart deg ufus nsen, ḥima ad tt wcen i yinni iggin řxedmet, minzi nitni tuɣa tteggen s utiqqi.  
\v 17 Nnuqart n tɣarṣt n umarwas d nnuqart n tɣarṣa n ddenb war tt ssidfen ɣar Taddart n SIDI. Tuɣa-tt i ikehhanen.   
\b  
\m
\v 18 Xenni igeɛɛed Ḥazayil, ajeǧid n Aram, immneɣ ak-d Jat, iṭṭef i-t. \add Awarni man aya\add* iɛewweř Ḥazayil tamuɣři nnes ɣar Urcalim, ḥima ad igeɛɛed ḍidd nnes. \x ◘ \xo 12:18 \xt 2 Ij. 8:12; 13:25; 2 Im. 24:23\x*  
\v 19 \add Maca\add* Yuwac iksi marra řeqcuɛ iqeddsen nni tuɣa issqeddes i-tent Yahucafaṭ, Yahuram d Axazya, řejdud nnes, ijeǧiden n Yahuda, uřa d řeqcuɛ iqeddsen nnes d marra wureɣ nni tuɣa iǧan deg ixxamen n txubay n Taddart n SIDI u n taddart n ujeǧid, uca issekk \add aya\add* ɣar Ḥazayil, ajeǧid n Aram. \add Xas uca\add* iggʷej netta x Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 12:19 \xt 2 Ij. 18:15\x*   
\m
\v 20 Imezruyen iqqimen n Yuwac d marra min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda?   
\m
\v 21 Imsexxaren nnes ɣewwɣen xas, ggin \add xas\add* ict n tmeɛmuč uca nɣin Yuwac di taddart n lqelɛa manis hekkwan ɣar Silla. \x ◘ \xo 12:21 \xt 2 Ij. 14:5\x*  
\v 22 Aqa Yuzakar, mmis n Cimɛat, d Yahuzabad, mmis n Cumir, imsexxaren nnes, wtin t ařami immut. Nitni neḍřen t jar řejdud nnes di tendint n Dawud. Amaṣya, mmis, idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 13
\s1 Yahuyaḥaz, ajeǧid n Israil  
\m
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss třata u-ɛicrin n Yuwac, mmis n Axazya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, idweř Yahuyaḥaz, mmis n Yahu, d ajeǧid x Israil, di Samarya. \add Netta iḥkem\add* sbeɛṭac n iseggʷusa.  
\v 2 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. Netta iḍfar ddnub n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, wenni yarran Israil ad ixḍa. Netta war iḥeyyed x man aya.  
\v 3 \add X uyenni\add* yarɣa weɣḍab n SIDI x Israil. Marra ussan \add nni\add* iwca i-ten deg ifassen n Ḥazayil, ajeǧid n Aram, u deg ifassen n Binhadad, mmis n Ḥazayil.   
\m
\v 4 \add Maca\add* Yahuyaḥaz iḥeccem zzat i wudem n SIDI u SIDI isřa as, maɣar Netta iẓra řeḥṣaret n Israil, mammec i ten iḥṣař ujeǧid n Aram.  
\v 5 SIDI iwca ijj n umsenjem i Israil, ařami zemmaren ad nfekken zeg ufus n ayt n Aram, uca \add xenni\add* tuɣa ayt n Israil zeddɣen \add ɛawed\add* am qbeř deg iqiḍan nsen.  
\v 6 Maca nitni war ḥeyyden ca x ddnub n taddart n Yarubɛam wenni yarrin Israil ad ixḍa. Israil iqqim iggur ammu u teqqim tarebbit n cwarti tbedd di Samarya.   
\m
\v 7 Maɣar netta war ijji zi řɛeskar n Yahuyaḥaz, mɣir xemsin n imnayen d ɛecra n ikarruten d ɛecra ařef n \add yeryazen\add* x iḍaren, maɣar ajeǧid n Aram tuɣa iqḍa i-ten, igga i-ten am tɛejjajt ɣar usarwet.   
\m
\v 8 Imezruyen iqqimen n Yahuyaḥaz, d marra min igga d marra timegga nnes imeḥḍen, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil?  
\v 9 Yahuyaḥaz igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Neḍřen t di Samarya. Mmis Yuwac idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yuwac, ajeǧid n Israil  
\m
\v 10 Deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa u-třatin n Yuwac, ajeǧid n Yahuda, idweř Yuwac, mmis n Yahuyaḥaz, d ajeǧid x Israil. \add Netta iḥkem\add* seṭṭac n iseggʷusa di Samarya.  
\v 11 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. Netta war iḥeyyed x ddnub n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, wenni yarrin Israil ad ixḍa, \add maca\add* netta yarni yuyur \add amenni\add*.   
\m
\v 12 Imezruyen iqqimen n Yuwac d marra min igga d marra timegga nnes imeḥḍen i zi immneɣ ak-d Amaṣya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil?  
\v 13 Yuwac igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. \add Xas uca\add* inya Yarubɛam x řɛarc nnes. Yuwac ittwanḍeř di Samarya jar ijeǧiden n Israil.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řmewt n Ilicaɛ d lmuɛjiza ɣar wenḍeř nnes  
\m
\v 14 Ilicaɛ ittwařqef s řehřac i zi ɣa immet. Yuwac, ajeǧid n Israil, ihwa-dd ɣares uca iru zzates, inna: “\add A\add* baba, \add a\add* baba! Akarru n Israil d imnayen nnes!” \f ◼ \fr 13:14 \ft \+fk imnayen\ft  - inni inyin x iysan u nedhen xasen.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 13:14 \xt 2 Ij. 2:12\x*  
\v 15 Ilicaɛ inna: “Ksi řqews d fřitcat!” Netta iṭṭef i yixef nnes ijj n řqews d fřitcat.  
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* inna netta i ujeǧid n Israil: “Sars afus nnec x řqews!” Uca issars netta afus nnes \add x řqews\add* uca issars Ilicaɛ ifassen nnes x ifassen n ujeǧid,  
\v 17 inna: “Arzem řkazi \add i iǧan\add* ɣar manis dd-tneqqar tfuct!”, uca netta yarzem i-t. \add Xenni\add* inna Ilicaɛ: “Wwet!” U netta iwta \add s řqews nnes\add*. Uca inna \add Ilicaɛ\add*: “Aqa-tt d ict n fřitca n usenjem s \add ufus n\add* SIDI uřa d ict n fřitca n usenjem \add zeg ifassen\add* n Aram, minzi ad tɣeřbed Aram di Ɛafik ař ɣa ittwareddeǧ.” \x ◘ \xo 13:17 \xt 1 Ij. 20:30\x*  
\v 18 \add Xas uca\add* inna netta: “Ksi fřitcat!” Uca netta iṭṭef i-tent. \add Xenni\add* inna i ujeǧid n Israil: “Wwet x temmurt!” Uca wanita iwta třata n twařawin x temmurt uca \add řexdenni\add* ibedd.  
\v 19 Aryaz n AREBBI iffugem xas aṭṭas, inna: “Tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad tewted xemsa niɣ setta n twařawin, iři ad teɣřeb x Aram ařami t i ɣa teqḍid \add qaɛ\add*. Řexxu \add maca\add* ad tɣeřbed x Aram \add mɣir\add* třata n twařawin.   
\m
\v 20 Ilicaɛ immut uca neḍřen t. Bandiyyat n ayt n Mu’ab tuɣa ttnumant ad adfent ɣar temmurt ɣar umezwaru n useggʷas.  
\v 21 Xzar, \add umi\add* tuɣa neṭṭřen \add ict n twařa\add* ijj n weryaz, imsar aqa ẓrin ict n bandiyya. Nitni nḍaren aryaz deg wenḍeř n Ilicaɛ. \add Umi dayes\add* iwḍa weryaz, iḥada iysan n Ilicaɛ, idweř iddar ɛawed uca ikkar ibedd x iḍaren nnes.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Iɣellaben n Yuwac x Aram  
\m
\v 22 Ḥazayil, ajeǧid n Aram, iḥṣar x Israil, marra ussan n Yahuyaḥaz.  
\v 23 \add Maca\add* SIDI iḥinn x řgens nnes uca yarḥem xasen uca inneqřeb ɣarsen di ṭṭweɛ n Řɛahd nnes ak-d Ibrahim, Isḥaq d Yaɛqub. Netta tuɣa war ixs ad ten yareddeǧ u war ixs ad ten issekk zi zzat n wudem nnes, ař řexxu.  
\v 24 Ḥazayil, ajeǧid n Aram, immut u mmis Binhadad idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.  
\v 25 Yuwac, mmis n Yahuyaḥaz, ikkes-dd zeg ifassen n Binhadad, mmis n Ḥazayil, tineddam nni tuɣa iṭṭef wanita zeg ifassen n babas Yahuyaḥaz. Yuwac iɣřeb xas třata n twařawin uca yarra-dd tineddam ɛawed ɣar Israil.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 14
\s1 Amaṣya, ajeǧid n Yahuda  
\m
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss tnayen n Yuwac, mmis n Yahuyaḥaz, ajeǧid n Israil, idweř Amaṣya, mmis n Yuwac, d ajeǧid n Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 14:1 \xt [2 Im. 25:1-28]\x*  
\v 2 Netta \add tuɣa\add* ɣares xemsa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa, umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Yahuɛadan, zi Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 14:2 \xt 2 Im. 25:1\x*  
\v 3 Netta igga min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, maca war iǧi am babas Dawud. Igga nican am mammec igga babas Yuwac.  
\v 4 Mɣir war ttwakksent řegɛudi. Řgens yiwi ɛad tiɣarṣa d tewhibin n řebxur x řegɛudi.  
\v 5 Umi tuɣa tagelda temten deg ifassen nnes, imsar belli netta inɣa imsexxaren nni inɣin ajeǧid, babas.  
\v 6 \add Maca\add* iḥenjiren n iqettařen war ten inɣi ca, am mammec \add t\add* yura deg wedlis ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa n Musa, i di iweṣṣa SIDI, inna: “Ibabaten war ttwaneqqen di ssibbet n iḥenjiren \add nsen\add* uřa iḥenjiren war ttwaneqqen di ssibbet n ibabaten \add nsen\add*, maɣar kuř ijj ad ittwaneɣ x ddnub \add n yixef\add* nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 14:6 \xt Aɛwd. 24:16; Ḥiz. 18:20\x*   
\m
\v 7 Netta iɣřeb x ayt n Idum di Teɣzurt n Tmeǧaḥt, ɛecra ařef \add n yeryazen\add*, u iṭṭef Salaɛ deg umenɣi u igga as Yaqtayil, ař ass-a. \f ◼ \fr 14:7 \ft \+fk Salaḥ\ft  - isem n yijj n wemcan niɣ n ict n tendint.\f*   
\m
\v 8 Xenni issekk Amaṣya ireqqasen ɣar Yuwas, mmis n Yahuyaḥaz, mmis n Yahu, ajeǧid n Israil, inna: “As-dd, ejj aneɣ ad nemmeřqa \add i umenɣi\add*.”  
\v 9 \add Maca\add* Yuwac, ajeǧid n Israil, issekk \add ijj n ureqqas\add* ɣar Amaṣya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, inna: “Cbarq ak-d isennanen \add i iɣemmyen\add* x \add idurar n\add* Lubnan, issekk \add ict n tebrat\add* ɣar \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt x \add idurar n\add* Lubnan, inna: ‘Ewc yeǧis d tamɣart i mmi!’ \add Maca\add* ijj n řweḥc n řexřa i \add din yuyuren\add* x \add idurar n\add* Lubnan, ikka u iɛfes x cbarq ak-d isennanen.  
\v 10 Iwa cek tɣeřbed x Idum u řexxu tdewřed dayek nnfaxet deg wuř nnec. Ṭṭef deg uweqqar i ɣarek u qqim di taddart nnec, \add minzi\add* mayemmi ɣa temmenḍared ixef nnec di řɣar u ad tewḍid, cek d Yahuda akidek?”   
\m
\v 11 \add Maca\add* Amaṣya war ixs ad iseř, uca Yuwac, ajeǧid n Israil, igeɛɛed ařami netta d Amaṣya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, mmqabařen ɣar Bayt-Cams \add i iǧan\add* di Yahuda.  
\v 12 Yahuda ittwaɣřeb s ufus n Israil, uca nitni arewřen, kuř ijj ɣar uqiḍun nnes.  
\v 13 Yuwac, ajeǧid n Israil, iṭṭef Amaṣya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, mmis n Yuwac, mmis n Axazya, di Bayt-Cams uca yiweḍ t-i-dd ɣar Urcalim. \add Dinni\add* igga ict n tazzit di řḥiḍ n Urcalim, zi Tewwart n Ifrayim ař Tewwart n Teɣmart, x ijj n webrid n arebɛa-mya n iɣaǧen.  
\v 14 Yiwi marra ureɣ d nnuqart d marra řeqcuɛ i ittwafen di Taddart n SIDI u deg ixxamen n txubay n taddart n ujeǧid, \add uřa d\add* irehhanen, uca iɛqeb ɣar Samarya.   
\m
\v 15 Imezruyen iqqimen n Yuwac d min igga d tmegga nnes imeḥḍen d mammec immneɣ ak-d Amaṣya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil?  
\v 16 Yuwac igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Netta ittwanḍeř di Samarya jar ijeǧiden n Israil. Mmis Yarubɛam idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.  
\v 17 Amaṣya, mmis n Yuwac, ajeǧid n Yahuda, iddar \add ɛad\add* xemmesṭac n iseggʷusa awarni i řmewt n Yuwac, mmis n Yahuyaḥaz, ajeǧid n Israil.   
\m
\v 18 Imezruyen iqqimen n Amaṣya, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda?   
\m
\v 19 Nitni ggin ict n tmeɛmuč xas di Urcalim, ařami netta yarweř ɣar Laxic, \add maca\add* nitni ssekken awarni as inni t iḍfaren ɣar Laxic uca nɣin t dinni. \x ◘ \xo 14:19 \xt 2 Im. 25:27\x*  
\v 20 Nitni iwyen t-i-dd x yeysan u netta ittwanḍeř di Urcalim jar řejdud nnes di tendint n Dawud.   
\m
\v 21 Marra řgens n Yahuda yiwi Ɛazarya, wenni umi ɣar iǧa seṭṭac n iseggʷusa, u ggin t d ajeǧid deg wemcan n babas Amaṣya. \x ◘ \xo 14:21 \xt 2 Im. 26:1\x*  
\v 22 Netta ibna Ilat u yarra i-t \add deg ufus\add* n Yahuda, awarni řami igga ad yareyyeḥ ujeǧid jar řejdud nnes.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yarubɛam, ajeǧid n Israil  
\m
\v 23 Deg useggʷas wiss xemmesṭac n Amaṣya, mmis n Yuwac, ajeǧid n Yahuda, idweř Yarubɛam, mmis n Yuwac, ajeǧid n Israil di Samarya. \add Netta iḥkem\add* waḥit u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa di Samarya.  
\v 24 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. Netta war iḥeyyed x marra ddnub n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, wenni yarrin Israil ad ixḍa.  
\v 25 Netta yarra-dd marra tammurt n Israil \add sadu ufus nnes\add* zi mani ɣa tiwḍed ɣar Ḥamat ař Řebḥar n Řewḍa ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, i tuɣa issiweř s uqemmum n umsexxar nnes Yunus, mmis n Amittay zi Jat-Ḥafir. \x ◘ \xo 14:25 \xt Yun. 1:1; Mt. 12:39, 40\x*  
\v 26 Maɣar SIDI iẓra aqa řeɣben n Israil d amerzag aṭṭas u war din iqqim \add ɛad\add* wenni ittwaṭṭfen d wenni umi jjin u war tuɣi wenni iɛawnen i Israil.  
\v 27 SIDI tuɣa war yenni ad imḥa isem n Israil zi sadu ijenwan, uca issenjem i-ten s ufus n Yarubɛam, mmis n Yuwac.   
\m
\v 28 Imezruyen iqqimen n Yarubɛam d marra min igga d marra timegga nnes imeḥḍen d mammec immneɣ u mammec ikesseb twařa nneɣnit Dimacq d Ḥamat inni \add tuɣa iǧan\add* ɣar Yahuda, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil?  
\v 29 Yarubɛam igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes, jar ijeǧiden n Israil. Mmis Zakariyya idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 15
\s1 Ɛazarya, ajeǧid n Yahuda  
\m
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa u ɛicrin n Yarubɛam, ajeǧid n Israil, idweř Ɛazarya, mmis n Amaṣya, ajeǧid n Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 15:1 \xt [2 Im. 26:1-23] — 2 Ij. 14:21; 2 Im. 26:1\x*  
\v 2 Netta \add tuɣa\add* ɣares seṭṭac n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem tnayen u-xemsin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Yakulya zi Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 15:2 \xt 2 Im. 26:1, 3; 2 Im. 27:3\x*  
\v 3 Netta igga min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, am mammec marra i tuɣa igga babas Amaṣya.  
\v 4 Mɣir war ttwakksent řegɛudi. Yiwi řgens ɛad tiɣarṣa d tewhibin n řebxur x řegɛudi.  
\v 5 \add Maca\add* SIDI iwta ajeǧid ařami ihřec s řbarṣ ař ass n řmewt nnes. Netta iqqim izeddeɣ deg ict n taddart tᵉttwaɛzeř, \add umi\add* Yutam, mmis n ujeǧid, tuɣa d řemqeddem n tzeddiɣt \add n ujeǧid\add* u iḥekkem x řgens n temmurt.   
\m
\v 6 Imezruyen iqqimen n Ɛazarya d marra min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda?  
\v 7 Ɛazarya igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Neḍřen t jar řejdud nnes di tendint n Dawud. Mmis Yutam idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Zakarya, ajeǧid n Israil  
\m
\v 8 Deg useggʷas wiss tmenya u-třatin n Ɛazarya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, iḥkem Zakariyya, mmis n Yarubɛam, x Israil di Samarya, \add řqedd n\add* setta n iyuren.  
\v 9 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, \add nican\add* am mammec t ggin řejdud nnes. Netta war iḥeyyed x ddnub n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, wenni yarrin Israil ad ixḍa.  
\v 10 Callum, mmis n Yabic, igga xas ict n tmeɛmuč uca iwta i-t zzat i řgens uca inɣa i-t. Netta idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes. \f ◼ \fr 15:10 \ft \+fk Callum\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘nneqmet’ niɣ ‘axřaf’.\f*   
\m
\v 11 Imezruyen iqqimen n Zakariyya, xzar, aqa ttwazemmemen deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil.  
\v 12 Wa d awař i tuɣa issiweř SIDI ɣar Yahu, inna: “Iḥenjiren nnec ad qqimen x řɛarc n Israil ař jjiř wiss arebɛa!” Uca ammu i temsar. \x ◘ \xo 15:12 \xt 2 Ij. 10:30\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Callum, ajeǧid n Israil  
\m
\v 13 Deg useggʷas wiss tesɛa u-třatin n Ɛuzziya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, idweř Callum, mmis n Yabic, d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem ijj n uyur ikmeř di Samarya. \f ◼ \fr 15:13 \ft \+fk Ɛuziya\ft  - niɣ ‘Ɛuzi-Yahu’. Isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘SIDI d jjhed inu’.\f*  
\v 14 Manaḥim, mmis n Jadi, iffeɣ-dd ɣares zi Tirṣa uca yusa-dd ɣar Samarya, iwta Callum, mmis n Yabic, di Samarya, uca inɣa i-t. Netta idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\m
\v 15 Imezruyen iqqimen n Callum d tmeɛmuč i igga, xzar, man aya \add marra\add* ittwazemmem deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil.  
\v 16 Xenni iɣřeb Manaḥim x Tafsaḥ, d marra imezdaɣ nni dayes, uca iwta uřa d tammurt nnes zi Tirṣa, minzi nitni tuɣa war d as arzimen \add tiwwura\add*. Aqa inɣa \add i-ten\add*. Marra timɣarin s ddeyset ifetteq asent \add aɛeddis\add*.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Manaḥim, ajeǧid n Israil  
\m
\v 17 Deg useggʷas wiss tesɛa u-třatin n Ɛazarya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, idweř Manaḥim, mmis n Jadi, d ajeǧid x Israil. \add Netta iḥkem\add* ɛecra n iseggʷusa di Samarya.  
\v 18 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. Marra ussan \add n tudart nnes\add* war iḥeyyed ca x ddnub n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, wenni yarrin Israil ad ixḍa.  
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd Ful, ajeǧid n Accur, \add ihjem\add* x temmurt. Iwca Manaḥim ařef talint n nnuqart i Ful, ḥima ad iqqim ad iḥkem u ḥima ad issemten tageldit deg ufus nnes. \x ◘ \xo 15:19 \xt 1 Im. 5:26\x*  
\v 20 Manaḥim igga Israil ad \add ɣares\add* dd-yiwi nnuqart, marra ayt n bu-wagřa, ḥima ad issiweḍ nnuqart nni i ujeǧid n Accur. Zi kuř aryaz \add iksi\add* xemsin ciqlu. \add Xas uca\add* iɛqeb ujeǧid n Accur, war iqqim \add ɛad\add* di temmurt.   
\m
\v 21 Imezruyen iqqimen n Manaḥim d marra min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil?  
\v 22 Manaḥim igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Mmis Faqaḥya idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Faqaḥya, ajeǧid n Israil  
\m
\v 23 Deg useggʷas wiss xemsin n Ɛazarya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, idweř Faqaḥya, mmis n Manaḥim, d ajeǧid x Israil. \add Netta iḥkem\add* tnayen n iseggʷusa di Samarya.  
\v 24 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. Netta war iḥeyyed x ddnub n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, wenni yarrin Israil ad ixḍa.  
\v 25 Faqaḥ, mmis n Ramalyahu, aneɣraf \add n řɛeskar\add*, igga xas ict n tmeɛmuč, iwwet i-t di Samarya, di lburj n taddart n ujeǧid. Arjub d Aryah wcin as afus u tuɣa akides \add ɛawed\add* xemsin n yeryazen zi Jilɛad. Netta inɣa Faqaḥya u idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\m
\v 26 Imezruyen iqqimen n Faqaḥya d marra min igga, xzar, man aya \add marra\add* ittwazemmem deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Faqaḥ, ajeǧid n Israil  
\m
\v 27 Deg useggʷas wiss tnayen u-xemsin n Ɛazarya, idweř Faqaḥ, mmis n Ramalyahu, d ajeǧid x Israil. \add Netta iḥkem\add* ɛicrin n iseggʷusa di Samarya.  
\v 28 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. Netta war iḥeyyed ca x ddnub n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ nni yarrin Israil ad ixḍa.  
\v 29 Deg wussan n Faqaḥ, ajeǧid n Israil, yusa-dd Tiɣlat-Filasir, ajeǧid n Accur. Netta iḥewwes Ɛayun d Abil-Bayt-Maɛka d Yanuḥ d Qadac d Ḥaṣur d Jilɛad d Ljalil d marra tammurt n Naftali. Netta indeh i-ten ɣar lmenfa ɣar Accur. \x ◘ \xo 15:29 \xt Ica. 8:23\x*  
\v 30 Huciɛa, mmis n Ila, igga ict n tmeɛmuč x Faqaḥ, mmis n Ramalyahu. Netta iwta i-t uca inɣa i-t. Netta idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes deg useggʷas wiss ɛicrin n Yutam, mmis n Ɛuzziya.   
\m
\v 31 Imezruyen iqqimen n Faqaḥ d marra min igga, xzar, man aya \add marra\add* ittwazemmem deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yutam, ajeǧid n Yahuda  
\m
\v 32 Deg useggʷas wiss tnayen n Faqaḥ, mmis n Ramalyahu, ajeǧid n Israil, idweř Yutam d ajeǧid. \add Tuɣa netta\add* d mmis n Ɛuzziya, ajeǧid n Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 15:32 \xt [2 Im. 27:1-9]\x*  
\v 33 Netta \add tuɣa\add* ɣares xemsa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. \add Netta iḥkem\add* seṭṭac n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Yaruca, yeǧis n Ṣaduq. \x ◘ \xo 15:33 \xt 2 Im. 27:1-9\x*  
\v 34 Netta igga min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, nican am mammec t igga babas Ɛuzziya.  
\v 35 Mɣir war ttwakksent řegɛudi. Řgens yiwyi-dd \add ɛad\add* tiɣarṣa d tewhibin n řebxur x řegɛudi. Netta ibna Tewwart Yuɛřan di Taddart n SIDI.   
\m
\v 36 Imezruyen iqqimen n Yutam, d marra min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda?  
\v 37 Deg wussan nni ibda SIDI ad issekk Raṣin, ajeǧid n Aram, d Faqaḥ, mmis n Ramalyahu, ɣar Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 15:37 \xt 2 Ij. 16:5; Ica. 7:1\x*  
\v 38 Yutam igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Netta ittwanḍeř jar řejdud nnes di tendint n babas Dawud. Mmis Aḥaz idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes. \f ◼ \fr 15:38 \ft \+fk Aḥaz\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘netta iṭṭef’.\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 16
\s1 Aḥaz, ajeǧid n Yahuda  
\m
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss sbeɛṭac n Faqaḥ, mmis n Ramalyahu, idweř Aḥaz, mmis n Yutam, d ajeǧid n Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 16:1 \xt [2 Im. 28:1-27] — 2 Im. 28:1\x*  
\v 2 Aḥaz \add tuɣa\add* ɣares ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem seṭṭac n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Netta war iggi min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, AREBBI nnes, am mammec \add igga\add* babas Dawud.  
\v 3 Netta yuyur deg ibriden n ijeǧiden n Israil. Netta ijja ɛad mmis ad yuyur di tmessi am mammec marra jjɛayef n řegnus inni tuɣa iɛarren SIDI zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 16:3 \xt Lawi 18:21; 20:2, 3; 2 Ij. 17:31\x*  
\v 4 Netta yiwyi-dd tiɣarṣa d tewhibin n řebxur x řegɛudi u x tewririn u sadu marra azɣar aziza.  
\v 5 Xas uca iffeɣ Raṣin, ajeǧid n Aram, d Faqaḥ, mmis n Ramalyahu, ajeǧid n Israil, immneɣ ak-d Urcalim. Nitni nnḍen i Aḥaz, \add maca\add* war zemmaren ad xas ɣeřben. \x ◘ \xo 16:5 \xt Ica. 7:1\x*   
\m
\v 6 Di řweqt nni yarra-dd Raṣin, ajeǧid n Aram, Ilat i Aram. Issuffeɣ ayt n Yahuda zi Ilat uca usin-dd ayt n Aram ɣar Ilat, \add qqimen\add* zeddɣen din ař ass-a. \f ◼ \fr 16:6 \ft \+fk Iramiyyen\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘ayt n temmurt n Aram’.\f*  
\v 7 Aḥaz issekk ireqqasen i Tiɣlat-Filasir, ajeǧid n Accur, inna: “Necc d amsexxar nnec d mmic. Geɛɛed d tfekked ayi zeg ufus n ujeǧid n Aram d ujeǧid n Israil, inni xafi innqeřben.”  
\v 8 Aḥaz yiwi nnuqart d wureɣ i ittwafen di Taddart n SIDI u deg ixxamen n txubay n taddart n ujeǧid uca issekk \add aya am\add* ict n terzeft i ujeǧid n Accur. \x ◘ \xo 16:8 \xt 2 Im. 28:21\x*  
\v 9 Ajeǧid n Accur isřa ɣares uca igeɛɛed ujeǧid n Accur ɣar Dimacq, iṭṭef i-tt. Netta indeh i-tt ɣar lmenfa ɣar Qir u inɣa Raṣin.   
\m
\v 10 Ajeǧid Aḥaz iffeɣ ɣar Dimacq i umsagar ak-d Tiɣlat-Filasir, ajeǧid n Accur, uca iẓra ijj n uɛalṭar di Dimacq. Ajeǧid Aḥaz issekk ijj n umedya n uɛalṭar d tweṣṣaf nnes n řebni, qaɛ am mammec tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad t ggen, ɣar ukehhan Uriya.  
\v 11 \add Xas uca\add* ibna ukehhan Uriya aɛalṭar. Ɣar \add řweqt i di\add* dd-iɛqeb ujeǧid Aḥaz zi Dimacq, aqa ibna t ukehhan Uriya am mammec marra min \add ɣares\add* dd-issekk ujeǧid Aḥaz zi Dimacq.  
\v 12 \add Umi\add* dd-yusa ujeǧid zi Dimacq, iẓra ujeǧid aɛalṭar uca iqarreb-dd ujeǧid ɣar uɛalṭar uca issbexxar xas \add tiɣarṣa\add*.  
\v 13 Netta issbexxar taɣarṣt nnes d tewhibt nnes \add n řɣiǧet\add* u iseyyeb xas tawhibt n useyyeb nnes. Issfarrɣeɣ uřa d idammen n tɣarṣa nnes n řehna x uɛalṭar.  
\v 14 Aɛalṭar n nnḥas nni ibedden zzat i wudem n SIDI, issmuṭṭiy t zeg uɣezdis n zzat n Taddart, zi jar uɛalṭar \add n jdid\add* d Taddart n SIDI, ɣar uɣezdis n ccamal n uɛalṭar \add n jdid\add* uca issars i-t \add dinni\add*.  
\v 15 Řexdenni ajeǧid Aḥaz iweṣṣa akehhan Uriya, inna: “Sbexxar taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ n ṣṣbeḥ d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* n tmeddit řa taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ n ujeǧid d tewhibt nnes \add n řɣiǧet\add* d tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ di ṭṭweɛ n marra řgens n temmurt d tewhibin nsen \add n řɣiǧet\add* d tewhibin nsen n useyyeb, u zeǧeɛ xas marra idammen n marra tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ u n tɣarṣa \add nneɣni\add*. Aɛalṭar n nnḥas ad yiři i nnec, ḥima ad \add dayes\add* arzuɣ ɛad.  
\v 16 Akehhan Uriya igga am mammec marra s minzi iweṣṣa ujeǧid Aḥaz.  
\v 17 Ajeǧid Aḥaz iqess teřwiḥin \add i yeǧan\add* x tkarrutin uca ikkes \add zzaysent\add* tabanyut i xas iǧan. Ikkes uřa d tarimant n waman zeg ifunasen n nnḥas inni sadu nnes uca issars i-tt x ict n zzellij n weẓru. \f ◼ \fr 16:17 \ft \+fk tarimant\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řebḥar’ niɣ ‘il’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 16:17 \xt 1 Ij. 7:23-51\x*  
\v 18 Pasu n ssebt i tuɣa ibnan di Taddart, uřa d adaf n ujeǧid ɣar uɣezdis n barra ikkes i-ten zi Taddart n SIDI di ssibbet n ujeǧid n Accur. \x ◘ \xo 16:18 \xt 1 Ij. 10:5; 1 Im. 9:18\x*  
\v 19 Imezruyen iqqimen n Aḥaz d min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda?  
\v 20 Aḥaz igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes di tendint n Dawud. Mmis Ḥizqiya idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 17
\s1 Ḥucaɛ, ajeǧid n Israil ař lmenfa ɣar Accur  
\m
\v 1 Deg useggʷwas wiss tenɛac n Aḥaz, ajeǧid n Yahuda, idweř Huciɛa, mmis n Ila, d ajeǧid x Israil di Samarya. \add Netta iḥkem\add* tesɛa n iseggʷusa.  
\v 2 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, maca war iǧi anect n ijeǧiden n Israil, inni tuɣa qbeř nnes.  
\v 3 Calmanassar, ajeǧid n Accur, ihjem xas uca Huciɛa idweř d amsexxar nnes uca ittwagg xas maḥend ad as iwc ljizya.  
\v 4 Ajeǧid n Accur yufa aqa Huciɛa igga ict n tmeɛmuč. Wanita tuɣa issekk ireqqasen nnes ɣar Su, ajeǧid n Miṣra, uca war dd-yiwi ɛad ljizya am qbeř i ujeǧid n Accur, zeg useggʷas ař aseggʷas. Ajeǧid n Accur iṭṭef i-t uca icedd i-t s iceddiyyen di řeḥbes.  
\v 5 Ajeǧid n Accur iwḍa x marra tammurt, igeɛɛed ɣar Samarya u inneḍ as-dd třata n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 17:5 \xt 2 Ij. 18:9\x*  
\v 6 Deg useggʷas wiss tesɛa n Huciɛa, iḥewwes ajeǧid n Accur Samarya uca indeh \add ayt n\add* Israil di lmenfa ɣar Accur u issezdeɣ i-ten di Ḥalaḥ u ɣar Xabur wenni d iɣzar n Juzan, u \add di\add* tneddam n Imadayen. \x ◘ \xo 17:6 \xt 2 Ij. 18:10; Ica. 8:4\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 7 Aya imsar minzi ayt n Israil xḍan x SIDI, AREBBI nsen, wenni ten dd-issgeɛɛden zi Miṣra, zi sadu i ufus n firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, u umi ggʷeden nitni irebbiten nneɣni,  
\v 8 ggin ad ddaren ɛlaḥsab tiweṣṣa n řegnus nni iɛarren i-ten SIDI zi zzat i wudem nsen, u \add ɛlaḥsab tiweṣṣa\add* n ijeǧiden n Israil inni \add ten\add* iggin. \x ◘ \xo 17:8 \xt Lawi 18:3\x*  
\v 9 Ayt n Israil tuɣa dřin timesřayin i war ittřiqin zzat i SIDI. Nitni ssbedden i ixef nsen řegɛudi di marra tineddam nsen, \add wah,\add* zi lburj n tɛessast ař tandint ifaryen \add s iɣebřawen\add*.  
\v 10 Nitni ssbedden imayḍuten \add iqeddsen\add* d trebbin n cwarti x kuř tawrirt yuɛřan u sadu kuř azɣar d aziza.  
\v 11 Nitni qeddmen tiwhibin n řebxur x marra řegɛudi, am mammec ggin řegnus nni tuɣa issuffeɣ SIDI zi zzat n wudem nsen. Nitni ggin timesřayin d tiɛeffanin ařami sɛaren SIDI.  
\v 12 Nitni sexxaren i imeyḍa \add n l’aṣnam\add* i x tuɣa d asen inna SIDI: “War iɛeddeř ad teggem aya!” \x ◘ \xo 17:12 \xt Uf. 20:3, 4, 5; Aɛwd. 5:7, 8, 9\x*  
\v 13 SIDI iɛřem i Israil d Yahuda s uqemmum n marra inabiyyen, u s kuř ijj n umwařaw, inna: “Tubem zi tbridin nwem tiɛeffanin u ḥḍam x lfarayiḍ inu d tweṣṣa inu ɛlaḥsab marra Ccariɛa i zi umureɣ řejdud nwem u wenni d awem dd-ssekkeɣ s ufus n imsexxaren inu, inabiyyen. \x ◘ \xo 17:13 \xt Irm. 18:11; 25:5; 35:15\x*  
\v 14 Nitni war sřin ca u tuɣa qesḥen aṭṭas am mammec tuɣa qesḥen aṭṭas řejdud nsen, inni war iggin ttiqet di SIDI, AREBBI nsen. \x ◘ \xo 17:14 \xt Aɛwd. 31:27; Mal. 3:7\x*  
\v 15 Nitni nḍaren tiweṣṣa nnes d Řɛahd nnes, wenni igga Netta ak-d řejdud nsen, uřa d cchadat nnes nni tuɣa xasen iched. Nitni ḍfaren min iǧan di řbaṭeř uca uřa d nitni \add s yixef nsen\add* dewřen beṭṭřen. \add Nitni ḍfaren ɛawed\add* řegnus nni d asen dd-innḍen i x tuɣa d asen inna SIDI aqa ad tteggen am mammec \add ggin\add* nitni.  
\v 16 Nitni aggʷejen x marra tiweṣṣa n SIDI, AREBBI nsen, u ggin i yixef nsen řexyařat ifesyen: tnayen n iɛejmiyyen. Nitni ggin \add ɛawed\add* ict n trebbit n cwarti uca bendqen i marra řɛeskar n ujenna u ɛebden i Baɛal. \f ◼ \fr 17:16 \ft \+fk iɛejmiyyen\ft  - niɣ ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 17:16 \xt Uf. 32:8; 1 Ij. 12:28\x*  
\v 17 Nitni arrin iḥenjiren nsen d tḥenjirin nsen ad cuqen di tmessi uca ssxedmen aɛezzem d tgezzant. Nitni zzenzen ixef nsen, maḥend ad ggen min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, ḥima ad t sɛaren. \x ◘ \xo 17:17 \xt Lawi 20:3, 4; Aɛwd. 18:10; 2 Ij. 16:3\x*  
\v 18 \add X uyenni\add* isɛar SIDI aṭṭas x Israil, \add ařami\add* inḍar i-ten x wudem nnes. War \add zzaysen\add* iqqim walu mɣir taqbič n Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 17:18 \xt Ḥuc. 1:6\x*   
\m
\v 19 \add Maca\add* uřa d Yahuda war iḥḍa lfarayiḍ n SIDI, AREBBI nsen. Nitni uyuren di tweṣṣa n Israil nni ggin s yixef nsen.   
\m
\v 20 SIDI inḍar marra zzariɛet n Israil. Netta issbehdeř i-ten uca iwca i-ten deg ufus n imkeccaḍen ařami inḍar i-ten x wudem nnes.  
\v 21 Maɣar Netta tuɣa iqřeɛ Israil zi taddart n Dawud uca ggin Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ d ajeǧid. Yarubɛam \add maca\add* ibḍa Israil x SIDI uca yarra i-ten ad ggen ijj n ddenb d ameqqran. \x ◘ \xo 17:21 \xt 1 Ij. 12:16, 17, 26\x*  
\v 22 Ayt n Israil kkin di marra ddnub i igga Yarubɛam. Nitni war xasen ḥeyyden ca,  
\v 23 ařami inḍar SIDI Israil zi zzat i wudem nnes am mammec tuɣa issiweř s uqemmum n marra imsexxaren nnes, inabiyyen. Ssuffɣen Israil zeg wudem n temmurt nnes di lmenfa ɣar Accur, ař ass-a.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řegnus nneɣni di Samarya  
\m
\v 24 Ajeǧid n Accur yiwi-dd \add iwdan\add* zi Babil d Kuta d Ɛawa d Ḥamat d Sfarwayim, uca issezdeɣ i-ten di tneddam n Samarya, deg wemcan n ayt n Israil. Nitni ṭṭfen Samarya d řwart \add i yixef nsen\add* u ggin ad zedɣen di tneddam nnes.  
\v 25 Umi dinni zedɣen ɛad cwayt, imsar aqa nitni war ggʷiden ca SIDI. \add Xenni\add* issekk SIDI iyraden jar asen inni inɣin ca zzaysen.  
\v 26 Nitni ssiwřen \add x man aya\add* ak-d u ujeǧid n Accur, nnan: “Řegnus nni tessuffɣed u tesszedɣed di tneddam n Samarya, war ssinen mammec \add teǧa\add* tubbart n AREBBI n temmurt. \add X uya\add* Netta issekk iyraden jar asen, u xzar, nitni nɣin ten, maɣar war ssinen ca tubbart n AREBBI n temmurt.   
\m
\v 27 Ajeǧid n Accur yumur, inna: “Jjem ad din iraḥ ijjen zeg ikehhanen nni tnedhem ssenni. Nitni ad \add din\add* raḥen u ad \add din\add* zedɣen u netta ad asen isseřmed tubbart n AREBBI n temmurt.”  
\v 28 Yusa-dd ijjen zeg ikehhanen nni tuɣa nedhen zi Samarya uca netta izdeɣ di Bayt-Il. Isseřmed i-ten mammec ɣa weqqaren SIDI.  
\v 29 \add Maca\add* kuř řgens yarni ad igg irebbiten n yixef nnes uca ssbedden ten di tudrin x řegɛudi nni tuɣa bnan Isamariyyen, kuř řgens di tneddam nsen mani tuɣa zeddɣen.  
\v 30 Iryazen n Babil ggin \add i yixef nsen\add* Sukkut-Bnut, u iryazen zi Kuta ggin Narjal, u iryazen zi Ḥamat ggin Acima,  
\v 31 u Iɛawiyyen ggin iwrafen n Nibḥaz d Tartaq, uca Isafarwayyin sscemḍen iḥenjiren nsen i Adrammilik d Ɛanammilix, irebbiten n Sfarwayim.  
\v 32 \add S marra man aya\add* ggʷeden nitni \add ɛawed\add* SIDI, \add maca di řweqt d ijj\add* ggin nitni i yixef nsen zi \add marra\add* řeṣfuf nsen \add ɛawed\add* ikehhanen i řegɛudi, inni d asen isexxaren di tudrin x řegɛudi. \x ◘ \xo 17:32 \xt 1 Ij. 12:31\x*  
\v 33 Nitni ggʷeden SIDI uca sexxaren uřa i irebbiten \add n ixef nsen\add* am mammec \add tuɣa teǧa\add* tubbart n řegnus i zi tuɣa ttwanedhen nitni. \x ◘ \xo 17:33 \xt Ṣaf. 1:5\x*   
\m
\v 34 Ař ass-a tteggen nitni ɛlaḥsab ṭṭbayeɛ nsen n zic. Nitni war tteggʷden ca SIDI u war tteggen ca ɛlaḥsab tiweṣṣa d lfariḍa, \add ixs ad yini\add* Ccariɛa d řumur i igga SIDI x ayt n Yaɛqub wenni umi tuɣa iwca isem ‘Israil’. \x ◘ \xo 17:34 \xt Amz. 32:27; 35:10; 1 Ij. 18:31\x*  
\v 35 SIDI igga ijj n Řɛahd akidsen, uca yumur i-ten, inna: “Kenniw war tzemmarem ad tweqqarem irebbiten nneɣni, war d asen ttaḍarem, war d asen ɛebbdem u war d asen ttawyem taɣarṣt. \x ◘ \xo 17:35 \xt Řqḍ. 6:10\x*  
\v 36 Maca ittxeṣṣa ad teggʷdem SIDI, wenni kenniw dd-issuffɣen zi Miṣra s jjhed ameqqran u s uɣiř isswiẓẓḍen, u ad as tsejdem u ad as tawyem taɣarṣt.  
\v 37 Ad teḥḍam tiweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ d Ccariɛa d řumur nni d awem yura, maḥend ad ten teggem kuř ass. War iḥeǧeř ad teggʷdem irebbiten nneɣni.  
\v 38 War tᵉttᵉttum Řɛahd i ggiɣ akidwem u war tᵉttweqqarem i irebbiten nneɣni,  
\v 39 maɣar ad teggʷedem SIDI, AREBBI nwem. Netta ad kenniw issenjem zeg ufus n marra řɛedyan nwem.”   
\m
\v 40 \add Maca\add* nitni war xsen ad sřen, maca ggin ɛlaḥsab tubbart nsen n zic.  
\v 41 Řegnus ggʷeden SIDI u sexxaren uřa i řexyařat nsen ineqcen deg umur d ijjen. Uřa d iḥenjiren nsen d iḥenjiren n iḥenjiren nsen tteggen \add ɛad\add* am mammec ggin řejdud nsen, ař ass-a.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 18
\s1 Ḥizqiya d ajeǧid x Yahuda  
\m
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss třata n Huciɛa, mmis n Ila, ajeǧid n Israil, imsar belli Ḥizqiya idweř d ajeǧid. \add Netta tuɣa\add* d mmis n Aḥaz, ajeǧid n Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 18:1 \xt [2 Im. 29:1-2; 31:1] — 2 Im. 28:27; 29:1\x*  
\v 2 Netta tuɣa ɣares xemsa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem tesɛa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Abi, yeǧis n Zakariyya.  
\v 3 Netta igga min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, nican am mammec t igga babas Dawud.  
\v 4 Netta ikkes řegɛudi, yarẓa imayḍuten \add iqeddsen\add*, ihdem tarebbit n cwarti uca iřbez afiɣar n nnḥas i tuɣa igga Musa, minzi ayt n Israil tuɣa i d as dd-yiwyen tiwhibin n řebxur ař ussan nni. Netta iřaɣa as Naḥuctan. \x ◘ \xo 18:4 \xt 2 Im. 31:1\x*  
\v 5 Netta ittceř x SIDI, AREBBI n Israil. Jar marra ijeǧiden n Yahuda inni dd-yusin awarni as niɣ \add ddaren\add* qbeř nnes, war tuɣi iǧi uřa d ijj am netta.  
\v 6 Netta tuɣa iḍfar abrid n SIDI, war xas iḥeyyed ca zi ḍeffar nnes. Netta tuɣa iḥeṭṭa řumurat nnes nni tuɣa yumur SIDI i Musa.  
\v 7 SIDI tuɣa akides. Mani ma tuɣa ittraḥ, tuɣa ifřeḥ. Netta iɣewweɣ x ujeǧid n Accur u war xas isexxar \add ɛad\add*.  
\v 8 Netta iɣřeb x Ifilisṭiniyyen ař Ɣazza ak-d jjwayeh nnes, zi lburj n iɛessasen ař tandint ifaryen. \x ◘ \xo 18:8 \xt Ica. 14:30\x*   
\m
\v 9 Deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa n ujeǧid Ḥizqiya, d aseggʷas wiss sebɛa n Huciɛa, mmis n Ila, ajeǧid n Israil, imsar belli Calmanassar, ajeǧid n Accur, igeɛɛed ḍidd i Samarya uca iṭṭef i-tt. \x ◘ \xo 18:9 \xt 2 Ij. 17:3\x*  
\v 10 Nitni ṭṭfen tt awarni i třata n iseggʷusa. Deg useggʷas wiss setta n Ḥizqiya, aqa-t d aseggʷas wiss tesɛa n Ḥuciɛa, ajeǧid n Israil, ṭṭfen nitni Samarya. \x ◘ \xo 18:10 \xt 2 Ij. 17:6\x*  
\v 11 Ajeǧid n Accur indeh \add ayt n\add* Israil di lmenfa ɣar Accur uca yiwyi ten di Ḥalaḥ u ɣar Xabur, wenni d iɣzar n Juzan, u \add di\add* tneddam n Imadayen, \x ◘ \xo 18:11 \xt 1 Im. 5:26\x*  
\v 12 maɣar nitni tuɣa war sřin ɣar min d asen inna SIDI, AREBBI nsen, uca arẓin Řɛahd nnes. Marra min yumur Musa, amsexxar n SIDI, war d as sřin u war t ggin. \f ◼ \fr 18:12 \ft \+fk ɣar min d asen inna SIDI\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ɣar tmijja n SIDI’.\f*  *   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Adaf n Sanḥarib di temmurt n Yahuda  
\m
\v 13 Deg useggʷas wiss arbeɛṭac n ujeǧid Ḥizqiya iffeɣ Sanḥarib, ajeǧid n Assur, ɣar marra tineddam ifaryen \add s iɣebrawen\add* n Yahuda uca iḥewwes i-tent. \x ◘ \xo 18:13 \xt [2 Im. 32:1-9; Ica. 36:1-22] — 2 Im. 32:1; Ica. 36:1\x*  
\v 14 Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, issekk \add ireqqasen\add* ɣar ujeǧid n Accur, ɣar Laxic, inna: “Necc xḍiɣ! Beɛɛed xafi! Marra min xafi ɣa tegged, ad t xeǧṣeɣ.” \add Xenni\add* igga ujeǧid n Accur ict n ljizya x Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda: teřt mya talint n nnuqart d třatin talint n wureɣ.  
\v 15 Ḥizqiya iwca marra nnuqart nni ittwafen di Taddart n SIDI u deg ixxamen n txubay n taddart n ujeǧid.  
\v 16 Di řweqt nni iqess Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, \add marra wureɣ n\add* tewwura n Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI u n řeḍruf ɣar uɣezdis n tewwart inni tuɣa iɣeǧef Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, \add s wureɣ\add* uca iwca i-t i ujeǧid n Accur.   
\m
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* issekk ajeǧid n Accur ljiniral ak-d uzeǧif n imsexxaren icennɛen d ukumandar n řɛeskar ak-d ijj n řɛeskar d ameqqran aṭṭas zi Laxic ɣar ujeǧid Ḥizqiya di Urcalim. Nitni geɛɛden, iwḍen ɣar Urcalim. Uca \add awarni řami\add* geɛɛden uca iwḍen nitni, bedden ɣar uqadus n waman n uyeřman n sennej, wenni \add iǧan\add* ɣar webrid yuɛřan ɣar Weḥwic n Uṣebban.  
\v 18 Nitni řaɣan, \add ḥima ad dd-yas\add* ujeǧid. \add Xenni\add* uyuren ɣarsen Alyaqim, mmis n Ḥilqiya, wenni iǧan x taddart \add n ujeǧid\add*, ak-d umarir Cibna d Yuwax, mmis n Asaf, amarir n umezruy.  
\v 19 Akumandar n řɛeskar inna asen: “Inim i Ḥizqiya: ‘Ammu i iqqar ujeǧid ameqqran, ajeǧid n Accur: Man atecři-ya i x tᵉttecřed?  
\v 20 Aqa-t d řhard n iyencicen \add waha\add*, umi tennid: Aqa \add ɣarneɣ\add* ccwar d jjehd i umenɣi! Man wen i x tᵉttecřed, aqa cek tɣewwɣed xafi?  
\v 21 Xzar, řexxu tᵉttecřed x Miṣra, x uɣanim nni innḍefsen, wenni, umi ḥed xas i ɣa iɛemmed, ittejjun deg ufus nnes uca issnuqqeb i-t. Ammu \add i yeǧa\add* firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, i marra inni xas ittecřen. \x ◘ \xo 18:21 \xt Ica. 36:6; Ḥiz. 29:6, 7\x*  
\v 22 Mařa kenniw ad d ayi tinim: ‘Neccin nettceř x SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ!’, \add xenni necc ad iniɣ:\add* ‘Ma Netta war iǧi d wenni i zi iḥeyyed Ḥizqiya řegɛudi d iɛalṭaren, u \add xenni\add* inna i Yahuda d Urcalim: Ittxeṣṣa ad tbendqem zzat i uɛalṭar-a di Urcalim?’  
\v 23 Xenni řexxu, egg ijj n umḥarrem ak-d sidi inu, ajeǧid n Accur, necc ad ac wceɣ ařfayen n iysan mařa cek zeg uɣezdis nnec ad asen dd-tawyed ayt n bu-uyis.  
\v 24 Mammec texsed ad tennqeřbed x wudem n lwali, wenni qaɛ d ameẓyan n imsexxaren n sidi inu, uca ad tᵉttecřed x Miṣra di ssibbet n ikarruten d imnayen?  
\v 25 Ɛawed, maɣar ma necc geɛɛdeɣ-dd ḍidd n wemcan-a, ḥima ad t areddǧeɣ břa SIDI? SIDI ini ayi: ‘Geɛɛed ḍidd i temmurt-a, areddeǧ i-tt!’”   
\m
\v 26 Uca nnan Alyaqim, mmis n Ḥilqiya d Cibna d Yuwax i ukumandar n řɛeskar: “Siweř ɛafek s \add iřes n\add* Tramit ak-d imsexxaren nnec, minzi nefhem as mliḥ. War kidneɣ ssiwiř s Tyahudect deg imezzuɣen n řgens \add i iǧan\add* x řḥiḍ.”  
\v 27 \add Maca\add* akumandar n řɛeskar inna asen: “Ma issekk ayi-dd sidi inu ḥima ad ssiwřeɣ awařen-a ɣar sidi nnec u ɣarek \add waha\add*, war iǧi i yeryazen nni iqqimen x řḥiḍ, \add maḥend ad iniɣ\add* aqa aten \add jmiɛ\add* akidwem ad ccen asuffeɣ nsen u ad swen ibeccicen nsen?”  
\v 28 Xenni ikkar ukumandar, iřaɣa s jjhed s Tyahudect uca issiweř, inna: “Sřem i wawař n ujeǧid ameqqran, ajeǧid n Accur!  
\v 29 Ammu i iqqar ujeǧid: ‘Ḥḍam war kenniw ittɣecci Ḥizqiya, minzi netta war izemmar ad kenniw ifekk zeg ufus nnes.  
\v 30 War ttejjim Ḥizqiya ad kenniw yarr ad tᵉttecřem x SIDI, ad tinim: SIDI ad aneɣ ifekk nican u tandint-a war tᵉttmewci ca deg ifassen n ujeǧid n Accur.’  
\v 31 War tesřim ca ɣar Ḥizqiya, maɣar ammu i iqqar ujeǧid n Accur: ‘Ggem ayi array uca ffɣem-dd \add zi tendint\add* ɣari, \add xenni\add* izemmar kuř ijjen zzaywem ad icc zi tzayart nnes u zeg wartu n tazart nnes u ad isu aman zeg wanu nnes,  
\v 32 ař dd ɣa yaseɣ u ad kenniw awyeɣ ɣar ict n temmurt am temmurt nwem: ɣar ict n temmurt teccur s imendi d binu n jdid, ɣar ict n temmurt teccur s weɣrum d imarjaɛen n uḍiř, ict n temmurt n zzitun d zzect d tamment. Ammu i ɣa teqqimem teddarem, war tmettim ca. War ttesřim ɣar Ḥizqiya, maɣar netta ittɣarra kenniw xmi iqqar: SIDI ad aneɣ ifekk!  
\v 33 Ma zemmaren \add xenni\add* irebbiten n řegnus, kuř ijj \add zzaysen\add*, ad fekken tammurt nsen zeg ufus n ujeǧid n Accur?  
\v 34 Mani ǧan irebbiten n Ḥamat d Arfad? Mani ǧan irebbiten n Sfarwayim d Haniɛ d Ɛiwa? Ma fekken nitni Samarya zeg ufus inu?  
\v 35 Man wen zi marra irebbiten n temmura \add nneɣni\add* i issnejmen tammurt nsen zeg ufus inu ařami ɣa ifekk SIDI Urcalim zeg ufus inu?’”   
\m
\v 36 \add Maca\add* řgens iseɣd, war xas dd-yarri s uřa d ijj n wawař, maɣar řumur n ujeǧid inna: “Kenniw war xas dd-tarrim ca!”  
\v 37 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd Alyaqim, mmis n Ḥilqiya, řemqeddem n tzeddiɣt \add n ujeǧid\add*, ak-d Cibna amarir, d Yuwax, mmis n Asaf, amarir n umezruy s warruḍ icarrgen ɣar Ḥizqiya. Nitni ḥajan as marra awařen n ukumandar n řɛeskar.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 19
\s1 Awař amezwaru x ufekki n Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 Umi ten isřa ujeǧid Ḥizqiya, icarreg arruḍ nnes, idřa ixef nnes s ict n txancet \add n wecḍan\add* uca yudef ɣar Taddart n SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 19:1 \ft \+fk Umi ten isřa\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Imsar umi isřa ...’\f*  \x ◘ \xo 19:1 \xt [2 Im. 32:20-21; Ica. 37:1-38]\x*  
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* issekk netta Alyaqim, řemqeddem n tzeddiɣt \add n ujeǧid\add*, d Cabna, amarir, d imɣaren n ikehhanen deg warruḍ n txuncay \add n wecḍan\add* ɣar unabi Icaɛya, mmis n Amuṣ. \x ◘ \xo 19:2 \xt Ica. 1:1\x*  
\v 3 Nitni nnan as: “Ammu i iqqar Ḥizqiya: ‘Ass-a d ijj n wass n řeḥṣaret u n weɛqab u n ubehdeř, maɣar iḥenjiren iwḍen-dd ař arzam n uɛeddis \add n yemmatsen\add*, \add maca\add* war din jjehd i twarut. \x ◘ \xo 19:3 \xt Ica. 37:3\x*  
\v 4 Ad taɣ SIDI, AREBBI nnec, isřa marra awařen n ukumandar n řɛeskar wenni ittwassekken zi sidis nnes, ajeǧid n Accur, ḥima ad istehza zi AREBBI iddaren, u \add ad taɣ\add* SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad iɛaqeb awařen i isřa. Sgeɛɛed \add xenni\add* ict n tẓaǧit di ṭṭweɛ n řbaqi nni i ɣa ittwafen \add ɛad\add*.’”   
\m
\v 5 \add Ammu\add* iwḍen imsexxaren n ujeǧid Ḥizqiya ɣar Icaɛya.  
\v 6 Inna asen Icaɛya: “Ammu i ittxeṣṣa ad tinim i siditwem: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: War teggʷed ca zeg wawařen i tesřid cek, i zi i d ayi ceqqfen imsexxaren n ujeǧid n Accur.  
\v 7 Xzar, Necc ad dayes ggeɣ ijj n buḥbeř u netta ad iseř i yijj n řexbar u ad iɛqeb ɣar temmurt nnes u Necc ad t nɣeɣ \add din\add* di temmurt nnes s ssif.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* iɛqeb-dd ukumandar n řɛeskar uca yufa ajeǧid n Accur ittmenɣa ak-d \add tendint n\add* Libna, maɣar isřa aqa iqřeɛ iqiḍan nnes \add iffeɣ\add* zi Laxic.  
\v 9 \add Umi\add* isřa aqa nnan x Tirhaqa, ajeǧid n Kuc: “Xzar, iffeɣ-dd, ḥima akidek immneɣ!”, issekk \add ɛawed\add* ireqqasen ɣar Ḥizqiya, inna:  
\v 10 “Ammu i ɣa tessiwřem ak-d Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ad tinim: ‘War ttejji ad cek iɣwa AREBBI nnec wenni x tᵉttecřed am iqqar: Urcalim war tᵉttweṭṭi i ujeǧid n Accur deg ifassen!  
\v 11 Xzar, tesřid min ggin ijeǧiden n Accur ak-d marra timmura nneɣnit, tinni tuɣa ad ttwareddǧent. Ma ittɣiř ac ad tᵉttwafekked?  
\v 12 Ma fekken ten irebbiten n řegnus inni yareddǧen řejdud inu? Juzan d Ḥaran d Rṣif d ayt n Ɛadan, inni \add tuɣa izeddɣen\add* di Talassar?  
\v 13 Mani iǧa ujeǧid n Ḥamat d ujeǧid n Arfad d ujeǧid n tendint n Sfarwayim uřa d \add ajeǧid n\add* Hanaɛ d Ɛiwwa?’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Taẓaǧit n Ḥizqiya d ufekki n Urcalim  
\m
\v 14 Ḥizqiya iksi tibratin zeg ufus n imsexxaren uca iɣra i-tent. \add Xenni\add* igeɛɛed ɣar Taddart n SIDI uca ibezzeɛ i-tent Ḥizqiya zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 15 Uca iẓẓuǧ Ḥizqiya zzat i wudem n SIDI, inna: “\add A\add* SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, wenni ittɣiman \add jar\add* ikiruben! Cek, \add wah\add* Cek weḥḥdek d AREBBI n marra tigeldiwin n ddunect. Cek teggid ijenwan d temmurt. \f ◼ \fr 19:15 \ft \+fk ikiruben\ft  - ict n marka n lmalakat.\f*  
\v 16 \add A\add* SIDI, ewc amezzuɣ nnec, seř! \add A\add* SIDI, arzem tiṭṭawin nnec, xzar! Seř i wawařen n Sanḥarib nni dd-issekk, ḥima ad istehza zi AREBBI iddaren.  
\v 17 D tidett, \add a\add* SIDI, ijeǧiden n Accur qḍan řegnus nni, xarrben temmurt nsen,  
\v 18 u nḍaren irebbiten nsen di tmessi, maɣar tuɣa war ǧin d irebbiten, maca d timegga n ufus n yewdan waha, zeg ukeccuḍ d weẓru, uca nitni mḥan ten.  
\v 19 \add Maca\add* řexxu, \add a\add* SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, senjem aneɣ zeg ufus nnes, maḥend marra tigeldiwin n ddunect ad ssnen, \add a\add* SIDI, aqa Cek weḥḥdek d AREBBI.”   
\b  
\m
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* isekk Icaɛya, mmis n Amuṣ, \add ijj n ureqqas\add* ɣar Ḥizqiya, inna: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Necc sřiɣ s minzi ɣari teẓẓuǧed x Sanḥarib, ajeǧid n Accur.  
\v 21 Wa d awař i xas issiweř SIDI: ‘Taɛzarect, yeǧis n Ṣihyun, tesseḥqar i cek, testehza zzayek, yeǧis n Urcalim thezza azeǧif awarni ac!  
\v 22 Wi zi testehzid u wi di tceqqfed? Wi xef tessgeɛɛded tmijja \add nnec\add*, u mixef tessgeɛɛded s nnfaxet tiṭṭawin nnec? \add Cek tᵉttɣennaned\add* x Umqeddas n Israil!  
\v 23 S uqemmum n imsexxaren nnec testehzid Sidi inu, tennid: S ubarru n ikarruten inu geɛɛdeɣ idurar yuɛřan, iɣezdisen n Lubnan. Necc ad zedmeɣ ticejjura nnes n tengelt yuɛřan uřa d řemxeyyer n ssibri nnes u necc ad dd-adfeɣ ɣar wemcan nnes n wareyyeḥ i iggʷejen aṭṭas, ɣar wezɣar n umarjeɛ nnes n uḍiř iṣebḥen. \f ◼ \fr 19:23 \ft \+fk S uqemmum\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘s ufus’. \fk amerzi\ft  - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*  
\v 24 Necc ɣziɣ \add anuten\add*, swiɣ aman. S tařeqqa n iḍaren inu ssiẓɣeɣ marra iɣezran n Miṣra.  
\v 25 Ma war tesřid aqa \add aṭṭas\add* zeg wami ggiɣ man aya, uca wciɣ as udem deg wussan n mecḥař uya? Řexxu jjiɣ t ad dd-iffeɣ, aqa cek d wenni i ɣa yarren tineddam ifaryen d řxirbat.  
\v 26 Imezdaɣ nsen tuɣa aten arxun, arẓin u seḍḥan. Nitni tuɣa aten am wefsu deg iyyar, \add am\add* uɣemmuy aziza, \add am\add* uřum x tzeɣwin, u \add am\add* \add imendi\add* icemḍen \add s usemmiḍ\add* qbeř ma ad iffeɣ.  
\v 27 \add Maca\add* necc ssneɣ aɣimi nnec d uffuɣ nnec d weɛqab nnec d uɣewweɣ nnec xafi.  
\v 28 Minzi cek tɣewwɣed xafi u tuffet nnec tiweḍ ɣar imezzuɣen inu, ad ac ssekkeɣ tasennart deg wenzaren nnec u \add ad ggeɣ\add* sřimet jar iyencicen nnec, u Necc ad cek arreɣ x webrid i di dd-tusid da.’   
\m
\v 29 D ta ad ac tiři d řeɛřamet: Deg useggʷas-a ad teccem min ɣa iɣemmyen s yixef nnes u deg useggʷas wiss tnayen min zzayes ɣa iɣemmyen ɛawed, maca deg useggʷas wiss třata ad tzarɛem u ad temjarem, ad teggem imarjaɛen n uḍiř, ad daysen teẓẓum tzayarin uca ad teccem řɣiǧet nnes.  
\v 30 Maɣar min innejmen, min iqqimen zi taddart n Yahuda, ad iwwet ɛawed iẓewran ɣar swadday u sennej ad yawi řɣiǧet.  
\v 31 Maɣar zi Urcalim ad dd-iffeɣ min iqqimen u zeg wedrar n Ṣihyun ad iffeɣ min innejmen, asam n SIDI \add n řɛeskarat ijehden\add* ad igg aya.   
\m
\v 32 S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI x ujeǧid n Accur: Netta war dd-ittidef ca di tendint-a u war dayes iccit ca uřa d ict n fřitca, war ɣares-dd iqarreb ca s ict n tseddart \add n uɛeskari\add* u war xas ttbeqqiḍen ijj n lbaraj i řeḥṣaret.  
\v 33 X webrid i x dd ɣa yas, ad dd-iɛqeb. War ittidif ca ɣar tendint-a, iqqar SIDI.  
\v 34 Necc ad sseřqiɣ x tendint-a, ḥima ad tt ssnejmeɣ di ṭṭweɛ inu u di ṭṭweɛ n umsexxar inu Dawud.’” \x ◘ \xo 19:34 \xt 2 Ij. 20:6\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 35 Di ǧiřet nni, imsar, aqa iffeɣ lmalak n SIDI, inɣa mya u-xemsa u-tmenyin-ařef \add n yeryazen\add* di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Accur. Umi i dd kkaren nitni tiwecca nnes, xzar, aqa aten marra idsen d řxecbat. \x ◘ \xo 19:35 \xt Ica. 37:36\x*  
\v 36 Uca Sanḥarib, ajeǧid n Accur, yarẓa iqiḍan nnes, iruḥ uca iɛqeb \add ɣar temmurt nnes\add*. Netta iqqim izeddeɣ di Ninwa.  
\v 37 Umi isjed \add ijj n wass\add* di taddart n arebbi nnes Nisrux, imsar, aqa \add iḥenjiren nnes\add* Adrammilik d Caraṣar nɣin t s ssif. Nitni arewřen ɣar temmurt n Ararat. Mmis Asarḥaddun idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes. \x ◘ \xo 19:37 \xt 2 Im. 32:21; Ica. 37:38\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 20
\s1 Řeḥřac n Hazaqiya d usgenfi nnes  
\m
\v 1 Deg wussan nni iḥřec Ḥizqiya s ijj n řeḥřac ineqqen. Yusa-dd ɣares unabi Icaɛya, mmis n Amuṣ, inna as: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ewc řumurat i taddart nnec, maɣar ad temmted, war tᵉttɣimid teddared \add ɛad ktar\add*.’” \x ◘ \xo 20:1 \xt [2 Im. 32:24; Ica. 38:1-22] — 2 Im. 32:24; Ica. 38:1\x*  
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* inneqřeb s uɣembub nnes ɣar řḥiḍ uca iẓuǧ i SIDI, inna:  
\v 3 “A, SIDI, ɛqeř aqa necc uyureɣ zzat i wudem nnec s řaman u s yijj n wuř ikemmřen u ggiɣ min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin nnec.” Uca ibda Ḥizqiya ittru s jjhed.  
\v 4 Tuɣa ɛad war iffiɣ Icaɛya zi řwesṭ n tendint, řami ɣares dd-yusa wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 5 “Ɛqeb, ini i Ḥizqiya, řḥakem n řgens inu: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n babac Dawud: Necc sřiɣ i tẓaǧit nnec u ẓriɣ i imeṭṭawen nnec. Xzar, ad cek ssgenfiɣ. Deg wass wiss třata ad tgeɛɛded \add ɛawed\add* ɣar Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 6 Necc ad arniɣ xemmesṭac n iseggʷusa i wussan \add n tudart\add* nnec u ad cek fekkeɣ zeg ufus n ujeǧid n Accur, uřa d tandint. Necc ad sseřqiɣ x tendint-a di ṭṭweɛ inu u di ṭṭweɛ n umsexxar inu Dawud.’”  
\v 7 \add Xas uca\add* inna Icaɛya: “Ksi ijj n weɣrum n tazart!” Nitni iwyen t-i-dd, ssarsen x ubuɛrus uca idweř iggenfa.  
\v 8 Ḥizqiya \add maca\add* inna i Icaɛya: “Man řeɛřamet aqa SIDI ad ayi issgenfa u necc ad geɛɛdeɣ ɣar Taddart n SIDI deg wass wiss třata?”  
\v 9 Inna Icaɛya: “Aya ad ac tiři d řeɛřamet n SIDI, aqa SIDI ad isseqfeř awař nni issiweř: ‘Ma ad tuyur tiři ɛecra n treffidin ɣar zzat niɣ ad dd-teɛqeb ɛecra n treffidin ɣar ḍeffar?’”  
\v 10 Ḥizqiya inna: “Ihwen i tiři, maḥend ad tezzuggar ɛecra n treffidin, lla, ejj tiři ad teɛqeb ɛecra n treffidin ɣar ḍeffar.” \f ◼ \fr 20:10 \ft \+fk Ḥazaqiya\ft  - nican s Tɛibranit ‘Yeḥazqi-Yahu’. Isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘SIDI iwca ayi jjehd’.\f*  
\v 11 Uca iřaɣa unabi Icaɛya ɣar SIDI u Wanita ijja tiři ad teɛqeb x treffidin i x tehwa x ddruj n Aḥaz: ɛecra n treffidin ɣar ḍeffar.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ireqqasen zi Babil  
\m
\v 12 Di řweqt nni issekk Baradux-Baladan, mmis n Baladan, ajeǧid n Babil, tibratin d ict n tarzeft ɣar Ḥizqiya, maɣar netta tuɣa isřa aqa Ḥizqiya ihřec. \x ◘ \xo 20:12 \xt [2 Im. 32:31-33; Ica. 39:1-8] \x*  
\v 13 Ḥizqiya isřa asen uca isscen asen marra taddart n txubay nnes: nnuqart d wureɣ d řeɛṭur d zzect d řehri n řesnaḥ nnes d marra min ittwafen deg ixxamen nnes n txubay. War iqqim walu di taddart nnes u di marra řeḥkamet nnes nni war tuɣi d asen t isscen.   
\m
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd unabi Icaɛya ɣar ujeǧid Ḥizqiya, inna as: “Min nnan iryazen nni u manis dd-usin ɣarek?” Ḥizqiya inna: “Nitni usin-dd zeg ict n temmurt tiggʷej, zi Babil.”  
\v 15 Netta inna: “Min ẓrin nitni di taddart nnec?” Ḥizqiya inna: “Nitni ẓrin marra min iǧan di taddart inu. War iqqim ca zi min iǧan deg ixxamen n txubay inu, war d asen t ssecneɣ.”  
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* inna Icaɛya i Ḥizqiya: “Seř i wawař n SIDI!  
\v 17 ‘Ad dd-asen wussan meřmi marra min iǧan di taddart nnec uřa d min yarwen řejdud nnec ař ass-a, ad t awyen ɣar Babil. War ittɣimi walu, iqqar SIDI.  
\v 18 Ad awyen uřa zeg iḥenjiren nnec inni dd ɣa iffɣen zzayek, inni dd ɣa tejjed, ḥima ad iřin d imsexxaren imcennɛen di řeqṣar n ujeǧid n Babil.’”  
\v 19 Ḥizqiya inna i Icaɛya: “Awař n SIDI i d ayi tennid iṣbeḥ.” Netta inna ɛawed: “Niɣ lla, mařa \add xenni\add* deg wussan inu ad \add din\add* yiři řehna d řaman!”   
\m
\v 20 Imezruyen iqqimen n Ḥizqiya d marra timegga nnes imeḥḍen d mammec igga ayeřmam d uqadus n waman u \add mammec\add* indeh aman di tendint, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda? \x ◘ \xo 20:20 \xt 2 Im. 32:30\x*  
\v 21 Ḥizqiya igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Mmis Manassa idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 21
\s1 Manassi, ajeǧid n Yahuda  
\m
\v 1 Tuɣa ɣar Manassa tenɛac n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem xemsa u-xemsin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Hafṣi-Bah. \x ◘ \xo 21:1 \xt [2 Im. 33:1-9, 20] — 2 Im. 33:1\x*  
\v 2 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, am mammec jjɛayef n řegnus nni tuɣa issuffeɣ SIDI zi zzat n wudem n ayt n Israil zi řwart nsen.  
\v 3 Netta ibda ad iɛdeř řegɛudi nni tuɣa ihdem babas Ḥizqiya. Netta issbedd iɛalṭaren i Baɛal uca igga ict n trebbit n cwarti am mammec tuɣa \add tt\add* igga Axab, ajeǧid n Israil, uca ibendeq i marra řɛeskar n ujenna uca iɛbed asen. \x ◘ \xo 21:3 \xt 2 Ij. 18:4\x*  
\v 4 Issbedd ɛawed iɛalṭaren di Taddart n SIDI i x inna SIDI: “Di Urcalim ad ssmetneɣ Isem inu.” \x ◘ \xo 21:4 \xt Aɛwd. 12:5, 11; 2 Ṣm. 7:13; 1 Ij. 8:29; 9:3; 2 Im. 7:12; Izhd. 132:13, 14; Irm. 32:34\x*  
\v 5 Netta ibna iɛalṭaren i marra řɛeskar n ujenna di tnayen n řemraḥat n Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 6 Netta ijja mmis ad yekk x tmessi u issxeddam tabezgiwt u tuɣa ittgezzen. Netta yiwi-dd inni issawařen ak-d imettan, d igezzanen. Netta igga aṭṭas min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, maḥend ad t isɛar.  
\v 7 Netta issbedd ijj n řexyař ineqcen n trebbit n cwarti nni tuɣa igga, di Taddart nni x tuɣa inna SIDI i Dawud, mmis n Suliman: “Di Taddart-a u di Urcalim i farzeɣ zi marra tiqebbař n Israil, ad ssmetneɣ Isem inu i řebda. \x ◘ \xo 21:7 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:10; 1 Ij. 8:16, 29; 9:3; 2 Ij. 23:27\x*  
\v 8 Necc war ttejjiɣ ɛad aḍar n Israil ad iweddar barra i temmurt i wciɣ i řejdud nsen. Mɣir ittxeṣṣa asen ad ḥḍan ad ggen am mammec marra min d asen umureɣ u am mammec marra Ccariɛa i d asen yumur umsexxar inu Musa.”  
\v 9 \add Maca\add* nitni war sřin ca, maɣar Manassa yarra i-ten ad weddaren, ařami arenyen di tuɛɛefna mahu řegnus nni imḥa SIDI zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil.  
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* issiweř SIDI s uqemmum n imsexxaren nnes, inabiyyen, inna: \f ◼ \fr 21:10 \ft \+fk s uqemmum\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘s ufus’.\f*  
\v 11 “Minzi Manassa, ajeǧid n Yahuda, igga jjɛayef-a, igga netta tuɛɛefna mahu x \add ayt n\add* Amur inni \add i din iǧan\add* qbeř nnes. Netta yarra uřa d Yahuda ad ixḍa s imeyḍa nnes \add n l’aṣnam\add*. \x ◘ \xo 21:11 \xt Irm. 15:4\x*  
\v 12 S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Xzar, Necc ad ggeɣ tuɛeffna x Urcalim d Yahuda, maḥend marra wi xas i ɣa isřen, aqa tnayen n imezzuɣen nnes ad ṭneṭnen.  
\v 13 Necc ad qqneɣ i Urcalim fiřu n řeɛbar n Samarya d řmizan n taddart n Axab. Necc ad mesḥeɣ Urcalim am mammec mesḥeɣ ijj n ṭṭebṣi. Mesḥen t u \add xenni\add* qeřben t x uzeǧif nnes.  
\v 14 Ad jjeɣ min iqqimen zi tesɣart n řwart inu, ad ten ssiwḍeɣ ɣar ifassen n řɛedyan nsen u nitni ad dewřen d taḥeggʷast d takeccaḍt i marra řɛedyan nsen,  
\v 15 maɣar nitni ggin min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI u \add maɣar\add* nitni sɛaren ayi zeg wass i di ffɣen řejdud nsen zi Miṣra ař ass-a.   
\m
\v 16 Ɛawed tuɣa Manassa issizzeř aṭṭas n idammen imezdagen ařami zzaysen iccur marra Urcalim zeg ijj n ṭṭarf ɣar wenneɣni, břa ma nidar \add ɛad\add* ddenb nnes i zi yarra Yahuda ad ixḍa, umi igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI.   
\m
\v 17 Imezruyen iqqimen n Manassa d marra min igga uřa d ddenb nnes i igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda?  
\v 18 Manassa igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Netta ittwanḍeř deg weḥwic n taddart nnes, di řemraḥ n Ɛuṣa. Mmis Amun idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes. \x ◘ \xo 21:18 \xt 2 Im. 33:20\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Amun, ajeǧid n Yahuda  
\m
\v 19 Amun \add tuɣa\add* ɣares tnayen u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem tnayen n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Mcullamit, yeǧis n Ḥaruz zi Yutba. \x ◘ \xo 21:19 \xt [2 Im. 33:21-25]\x*  
\v 20 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, \add ammu nican\add* am mammec t igga babas Manassa.  
\v 21 Netta yuyur kuř abrid i di yuyur babas. Netta isexxar i imeyḍa \add n l’aṣnam\add* i tuɣa isexxar \add uřa d\add* babas uca isjed asen.  
\v 22 Netta ismeḥ di SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nnes, u netta war yuyur ca deg webrid n SIDI.  
\v 23 Imsexxaren n Amun ggin xas ict n tmeɛmuč uca nɣin ajeǧid di taddart nnes.  
\v 24 \add Maca\add* řgens n temmurt nɣin marra inni tuɣa iggin ict n tmeɛmuč i ujeǧid Amun, uca řgens n temmurt ggin mmis Yuciya d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\m
\v 25 Imezruyen iqqimen n Amun d min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda?  
\v 26 Netta ittwanḍeř deg wenḍeř nnes deg weḥwic n Ɛuzza. Mmis Yuciya idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes. \x ◘ \xo 21:26 \xt Mt. 1:10\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 22
\s1 Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda - Adlis ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa  
\m
\v 1 Yuciya \add tuɣa\add* ɣares tmenya n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem waḥit u-třatin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Yadidya, yeǧis n Ɛadaya zi Buṣqat. \x ◘ \xo 22:1 \xt [2 Im. 34:1-28] — 2 Im. 34:1\x*  
\v 2 Netta igga min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. Netta yuyur di kuř abrid n babas Dawud, war iḥeyyed \add x webrid\add* \add ɣar\add* yefus uřa \add ɣar\add* uzeřmaḍ.   
\m
\v 3 Deg useggʷas wiss tmenṭac n ujeǧid Yuciya, imsar belli ajeǧid Yuciya issekk amarir Cafan, mmis n Aṣalya, mmis n Macullam, ɣar Taddart n SIDI, inna:  
\v 4 “Geɛɛed ɣar Ḥilqiya, arrays n ikehhanen, ḥima ad yegg ad sswejden tmenyat n nnuqart i dd yiwyen di Taddart n SIDI, d tinni i dd-yarwen iɛessasen n tewwura zi řgens.  
\v 5 Ejj i-ten ad tent ggen deg ifassen n yinni itteggen řxedmet, \add deg ifassen n\add* imeḥḍayen n Taddart n SIDI, \add ḥima\add* nitni ad tent wcen i yinni itteggen řxedmet i \add din\add* iǧan di Taddart n SIDI, ḥima ad areqqɛen řeḥyuḍ ihruran n Taddart,  
\v 6 i ineqqacen \add n ukeccuḍ d weẓru\add*, i ibennayen d imaṣṣuten, u i tmesɣiwt n ukeccuḍ d tṣuḍar ittwassuydan i weɛdař n Taddart.”  
\v 7 Maca war ittxeṣṣi maḥend ad kidsen ggen řeḥsab zi jjihet n \add ttmenyat n\add* nnuqart i d asen immewcen, maɣar nitni tteggen s utiqqi.   
\b  
\m
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* inna arrays n ikehhanen Ḥilqiya i umarir Cafan: “Necc ufiɣ adlis ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa di Taddart n SIDI.” Uca iwca Ḥilqiya i Cafan adlis ittwannḍen u wanita iɣra i-t.  
\v 9 \add Awarni as\add* yuyur umarir Cafan ɣar ujeǧid uca issiweḍ řexbar i ujeǧid, inna: “Imsexxaren nnec ssmunen \add ttmenyat n\add* nnuqart nni ittwafen di Taddart, farrɣen tent uca wcin tent deg ifassen n yinni iggin řxedmet, i imeḥḍayen n Taddart n SIDI.”  
\v 10 \add Ɛawed\add* iḥaja umarir Cafan i ujeǧid, inna: “Akehhan Ḥilqiya iwca ayi ijj n wedlis.” Cafan iɣra i-t zzat i wudem n ujeǧid.   
\m
\v 11 Umi isřa ujeǧid awařen n wedlis ittwannḍen n Ccariɛa, icarreg arruḍ nnes. \f ◼ \fr 22:11 \ft \+fk Umi isřa\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Imsar umi isřa ...’.\f*  
\v 12 Ajeǧid yumur i ukehhan Ḥilqiya u i Axiqam, mmis n Cafan, u i Ɛakbur, mmis n Mixa-Yah, u i Cafan, amarir, u i Ɛasaya, amsexxar n ujeǧid, inna:  
\v 13 “Uyurem, arzum SIDI di ṭṭweɛ inu u di ṭṭweɛ n řgens u di ṭṭweɛ n marra Yahuda zi jjihet n wawařen-a n wedlis-a ittwannḍen i ittwafen, maɣar asɛar n SIDI i yarɣin ḍidd nneɣ d ameqqran, minzi řejdud nneɣ war sřin ca ɣar wawařen n wedlis-a ittwannḍen, ḥima ad ggen am mammec marra \add min dayes\add* yuran i neccin.”   
\m
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* yuyur ukehhan Ḥilqiya ak-d Axiqam, Ɛakbur, Cafan d Ɛasaya ɣar tnabit Xulda, tamɣart n Callum, mmis n Tiqwa, mmis n Ḥarḥas, wenni iḥeṭṭan x warruḍen. Nettat tezdeɣ di Urcalim, deg wezyen nneɣni. Nitni ssiwřen akides.  
\v 15 Nettat tenna asen: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Ini i weryaz nni kenniw i ɣari dd-issekken:  
\v 16 Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Xzar, Necc ad awyeɣ tuɛeffna x wemcan-a u x imezdaɣ nnes, aqa marra awařen n wedlis-a ittwannḍen i iɣra ujeǧid n Yahuda,  
\v 17 maɣar nitni semḥen dayi, iwyen tiwhibin n řebxur i irebbiten nneɣni ařami dayi sɛaren s marra řxedmet n ifassen nsen. Asɛar inu ad ittwassarɣ ḍidd i wemcan-a u war ixessi ca ɛad.  
\v 18 \add Maca\add* inim i ujeǧid n Yahuda, wenni kenniw dd-issekken da ḥima ad tᵉttarem i SIDI: Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, x wawařen i tesřid cek:  
\v 19 Minzi uř nnec idweř yarḍeb u tesswaḍɛed ixef nnec zzat i wudem n SIDI umi tesřid x min ssiwřeɣ x wemcan-a u x imezdaɣ nnes - aqa nitni ad dewřen d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ d nneɛřet - u umi tcarrged arruḍ nnec uca trud zzat i wudem inu, x uya ad ac sřiɣ, iqqar SIDI.  
\v 20 S uya, aqa Necc ad cek ssmuneɣ ɣar řejdud nnec uca ad ttwassarsed deg wenḍeř di řehna u tiṭṭawin nnec war ẓarrent tuɛeffna i d ɣa awyeɣ x wemcan-a.’” \add Xenni\add* ssiwḍen nitni awař-a ɣar ujeǧid.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 23
\s1 Ařeqqeḥ s ufus n Yuciya  
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* issekk ujeǧid \add ireqqasen\add* uca marra imɣaren n Yahuda d Urcalim munen ɣares. \x ◘ \xo 23:1 \xt [2 Im. 34:29-30; 35:1-27] — 2 Im. 34:29\x*  
\v 2 Ajeǧid igeɛɛed ɣar Taddart n SIDI ak-d marra iryazen n Yahuda d marra imezdaɣ n Urcalim, uřa d ikehhanen d inabiyyen d marra řgens, zeg umeẓyan ař umeqqran, u netta iɣra xasen deg imezzuɣen nsen marra awařen n wedlis n Řɛahd nni tuɣa ufin di Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 3 Ajeǧid tuɣa ibedd ɣar ijj n upilar uca netta iqqen Řɛahd zzat i SIDI, ḥima ad iḍfar SIDI, ad iḥḍa řumurat nnes d cchadat nnes d tweṣṣa nnes s marra uř \add nnes\add* u s marra řeɛmar \add nnes\add*, maḥend ad issemten awařen n Řɛahd-a nni yurin deg wedlis-a. Uca yudef řgens marra di Řɛahd.   
\m
\v 4 Ajeǧid yumur i Ḥilqiya, arrays n ikehhanen, u i ikehhanen n usettef wiss tnayen u i iɛessasen n tewwart, aqa nitni ad ssuffɣen marra řeqcuɛ nni tuɣa ittwaggen i Baɛal u i trebbit n cwarti uřa i marra řɛeskar n ujenna zi Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI ɣar barra, u issecmeḍ man aya \add marra\add* barra i Urcalim deg iyyaren n Qidrun u ijja ad arbun iɣɣeḍ nnes ɣar Bayt-Il.  
\v 5 Netta ikkes \add ɛawed\add* ikehhanen n l’aṣnam nni tuɣa řeqqmen ijeǧiden n Yahuda, ḥima ad qeddmen tiwhibin n řebxur di řegɛudi, di tneddam n Yahuda u di jjwayeh i dd innḍen i Urcalim, uřa d yinni i iqeddmen tiwhibin n řebxur i Baɛal, d tfuct, d tziri, d temmura n ujenna u i marra řɛeskar n ujenna. \f ◼ \fr 23:5 \ft \+fk timmura n ujenna\ft  - ixs ad yini كواكب سيارونِ.\f*  
\v 6 Issuffeɣ uřa d tarebbit n cwarti zi Taddart n SIDI, \add igga i-tt\add* barra i Urcalim ɣar teɣzart n Qidrun. Netta issecmeḍ i-tt ɣar teɣzart n Qidrun u iddez i-tt d taɛejjajt u yareyyec i-tt x imeḍřan n ayt n řgens.  
\v 7 Netta ihdem ixxamen n imetleyyin nni tuɣa ɣar Taddart n SIDI, mani ttxeyyaḍent temɣarin iqiḍan nni ggint am tizzayiwin i trebbit n cwarti.  
\v 8 Netta ijja ad ssuffɣen marra ikehhanen zi tneddam n Yahuda uca issexmej řegɛudi mani qeddmen ikehhanen tiwhibin n řebxur, zi Jabɛa ař Bi’r-Sebɛa. Netta ihdem řegɛudi ɣar tewwura \add n tendint\add*, uřa d tinni \add iǧan\add* ɣar wadaf n Tewwart n Yacuwa, azeǧif ameqqran n tendint, ɣar uzeřmaḍ n wenni \add i tuɣa ittadef\add* Tawwart n Tendint.  
\v 9 Maca ikehhanen n řegɛudi war zemmaren ad geɛɛden ɣar uɛalṭar n SIDI di Urcalim, maca nitni ccin aɣrum břa antun di řwest n aytmatsen.  
\v 10 Netta issexmej uřa d Tufat nni \add iǧan\add* di teɣzurt n ayt n Hinnum, ḥima uřa d ijj war issɛeddu mmis niɣ yeǧis x tmessi i Mulak.  
\v 11 Netta ikkes iysan i tuɣa ggin ijeǧiden n Yahuda i řewqar n tfuct ɣar wadaf n Taddart n SIDI, ɣar texxamt n Natan-Malak, amsexxar acenneɛ, wenni \add iǧan\add* di řebniyyat barra \add i Zzawect Tameqqrant\add*. Netta iqedd i ikarruten n tfuct s tmessi.  
\v 12 \add Uřa d\add* iɛalṭaren nni tuɣa ibedden x tzeqqa n tɣurfet n Aḥaz nni ggin ijeǧiden n Yahuda, uřa d iɛalṭaren i igga Manassa di tnayen n řemraḥat n Taddart n SIDI, ihdem i-ten ujeǧid. Netta iřbez i-ten, \add issiggʷej i-ten\add* ssenni uca inḍar taɛejjajt nsen di teɣzart n Qidrun.  
\v 13 Uca issexmej ujeǧid řegɛudi nni \add din iǧan\add* zzat i Urcalim, ɣar yefus n wedrar n Uḍeyyeɛ, \add řegɛudi\add* i ibna Suliman, ajeǧid n Israil, i Acturit, nnɛi n l’aṣnam n ayt n Ṣidun, u i Kamuc, nnɛi n l’aṣnam n ayt n Mu’ab, u i Milkum, jjɛifect n l’aṣnam n ayt n Ɛammun.  
\v 14 Netta yarẓa imayḍuten \add iqeddsen\add* d iwetwiten uca ihdem tirebbin n cwarti uca iccur amcan nsen s yeɣsan n yewdan. \x ◘ \xo 23:14 \xt Uf. 23:24; 34:13; Řxř. 33:52; Aɛwd. 7:5, 25; 12:3\x*   
\m
\v 15 Uřa d aɛalṭar nni \add iǧan\add* di Bayt-Il, řgeɛɛdet i iggin Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, d wenni yarrin Israil ad ixḍa, aqa aɛalṭar nni d řgeɛɛdet nni, ihdem i-ten s tnayen idsen. Netta issecmeḍ řgeɛɛdet, iddez i-tt ařami tedweř d taɛejjajt uca issecmeḍ tarebbit n cwarti. \x ◘ \xo 23:15 \xt 1 Ij. 12:32, 33\x*  
\v 16 \add Umi\add* dd-inneqřeb Yuciya, iẓra imeḍřan i \add tuɣa\add* dinni x wedrar, uca issekk \add din ca n yeryazen\add*, iksi-dd iɣsan zeg imeḍřan uca issecmeḍ i-ten x uɛalṭar. \add Ammu\add* i issexmej i-t ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI i zi ibarreḥ weryaz n AREBBI wenni ibarrḥen awařen-a. \x ◘ \xo 23:16 \xt 1 Ij. 13:2\x*  
\v 17 \add Yarni\add* inna: “Mana weẓru nni i war ẓriɣ ɛemmars i din twařiɣ?” Nnan as yeryazen n tendint: “Wa d anḍeř n weryaz n AREBBI wenni tuɣa dd-yusin zi Yahuda, d wenni ibarrḥen s tmesřayin-a nni teggid ak-d uɛalṭar-a n Bayt-Il.”  
\v 18 Netta inna: “Jjem t din! Uřa d ijjen war ittḥidi iɣsan nnes!” Ammu i jjin nitni iɣsan nnes \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d yeɣsan n unabi wenni dd-yusin zi Samarya.   
\m
\v 19 Ikkes Yuciya marra tudrin n tzawiyyin n řegɛudi nni \add iǧan\add* di tneddam n Samarya i tuɣa ssbedden ijeǧiden n Israil, maḥend ad sɛaren \add SIDI\add*. Netta igga zzaysen am mammec igga di Bayt-Il. \x ◘ \xo 23:19 \xt 2 Im. 34:6\x*  
\v 20 Marra ikehhanen n řegɛudi inni \add tuɣa iǧan\add* din, iɣarṣ asen x iɛalṭaren uca issecmeḍ iɣsan n iwdan. Awarni as iɛqeb ɣar Urcalim.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n Useɛdu  
\m
\v 21 Ajeǧid yumur i marra řgens: “Swejdem \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu i SIDI, AREBBI nwem, am mammec ittwari deg wedlis-a n Řɛahd.” \x ◘ \xo 23:21 \xt [2 Im. 35] — Uf. 12:3; Aɛwd. 16:2; 2 Im. 35:1\x*  
\v 22 Ict n \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt n\add* Useɛdu am wa war ittwagg \add ɛemmarṣ\add* zeg wussan n řquḍat nni tuɣa iḥekkmen Israil, uřa di marra ussan n ijeǧiden n Israil d ijeǧiden n Yahuda.  
\v 23 Maca deg useggʷas wiss tmenṭac n ujeǧid Yuciya sswejden nitni \add Řɛid n Tɣarṣt\add* n Useɛdu wanita i SIDI di Urcalim.   
\m
\v 24 Yuciya ikkes uřa d yinni issawařen ak-d imettan, d igezzanen, d řexyařat timeẓyanin n l’aṣnam, d imeyḍa n \add l’aṣnam\add*, d marra nnɛawat n l’aṣnam i ittwařan di temmurt n Yahuda u di Urcalim, ḥima ad igg awařen n Ccariɛa i ittwarin deg wedlis ittwannḍen i tuɣa yufa ukehhan Ḥilqiya di Taddart n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 23:24 \xt Lawi 19:31; 20:27; Aɛwd. 18:11; Ica. 8:19\x*  
\v 25 Qbeř nnes war din tuɣi uřa d ijj n ujeǧid am netta, idweř-dd ɣar SIDI s marra uř nnes u s marra řeɛmar nnes d s marra jjehd nnes, ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa n Musa, u awarni as war din tuɣi uřa d ijjen am netta. \x ◘ \xo 23:25 \xt Aɛwd. 6:5; 10:12; Mt. 22:37; Mk. 12:20, 33; Lk. 10:27\x*   
\m
\v 26 Maca SIDI war ijji zi řḥaduq n weɣḍab nnes ameqqran i zi tuɣa yarɣa weɣḍab nnes x Yahuda zi ssibbet n marra asɛar i d as igga Manassa.  
\v 27 SIDI inna: “Ad ssiggʷjeɣ uřa d Yahuda x wudem inu, am mammec ssiggʷejeɣ Necc Israil, u Necc ad nḍareɣ tandint-a Urcalim i farzeɣ, uřa d Taddart i xef nniɣ: ‘Ad yiři Isem inu diha!’” \x ◘ \xo 23:27 \xt 2 Ij. 17:18, 20; 24:3\x*   
\m
\v 28 Imezruyen iqqimen n Yuciya d marra min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda?   
\b  
\m
\v 29 Deg wussan nnes igeɛɛed firɛun Nixu, ajeǧid n Miṣra, ḍidd i ujeǧid n Accur ɣar yeɣzar n Lfuraṭ. Ajeǧid Yuciya iffeɣ, maḥend ad t iřqa, maca \add firɛun Nixu\add* inɣa i-t ɣar Majiddu řami t yeẓra.  
\v 30 Imsexxaren nnes iwyen t d amettin x ijj n ukarru zi Majiddu ɣar Urcalim, ssiwḍen t ɣar Urcalim uca neḍřen t deg wenḍeř nnes. Řgens n temmurt iksi Yahuyaḥaz, mmis n Yuciya, uca dehnen t, ggin t d ajeǧid deg wemcan n babas. \x ◘ \xo 23:30 \xt 2 Im. 36:1\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yahuyaḥaz, ajeǧid n Yahuda  
\m
\v 31 Yahuyaḥaz \add tuɣa\add* ɣares třata u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem třata n iyuren di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Ḥamutal, yeǧis n Irmiya zi Libna. \x ◘ \xo 23:31 \xt [2 Im. 36:1-4]\x*  
\v 32 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, nican am mammec t ggin řejdud nnes.  
\v 33 Firɛun Nixu ijja ad t ibelleɛ di Ribla di temmurt n Ḥamat, ḥima war iḥekkem \add ɛad\add* di Urcalim. Netta igga i temmurt ijj n multa n mya talint n nnuqart d ict n talint n wureɣ.  
\v 34 \add Xenni\add* igga firɛun Alyaqim, mmis n Yuciya d ajeǧid deg wemcan n babas uca ibeddeř isem nnes ɣar Yahuyaqim. \add Maca\add* Yahuyaḥaz yiwyi i-t uca yusa-dd ɣar Miṣra uca immut dinni. \x ◘ \xo 23:34 \xt Mt. 1:11\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yahuyaqim, ajeǧid n Yahuda  
\m
\v 35 Yahuyaqim iwca nnuqart d wureɣ i firɛun, maca netta tuɣa iqeddar tammurt, ḥima \add izemmar\add* ad isellem nnuqart nni ɛlaḥsab řumur n firɛun. \add Iqeddar kuř ijj n\add* weryaz ɛlaḥsab řeqdar nnes, \add ammu i\add* ittar nnuqart d wureɣ n řgens n temmurt, ḥima ad t iwc i firɛun Nixu. \x ◘ \xo 23:35 \xt [2 Im. 36:5-8]\x*  
\v 36 Yahuyaqim \add tuɣa\add* ɣares xemsa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem ḥiṭac n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Zabida, yeǧis n Fidaya zi Rumat.  
\v 37 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, nican am mammec t ggin řejdud nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 24
\s1 Yahuda sadu ufus n ujeǧid n Babil řmijař n třata n iseggʷusa  
\m
\v 1 Deg wussan nnes igeɛɛed Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, u Yahuyaqim idweř iṭaɛ as třata n iseggʷusa. \add Xenni\add* inneqřeb uca iɣewweɣ xas. \x ◘ \xo 24:1 \xt 2 Im. 36:6\x*  
\v 2 Issekk-dd ɣares SIDI bandiyyat n Ikaldaniyyen d bandiyyat n Aram d bandiyyat n Mu’ab d bandiyyat n ayt n Ɛammun. Netta issekk i-ten ɣar Yahuda, ḥima ad tt xarrben ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI i tuɣa issiweř s uqemmum n imsexxaren nnes, inabiyyen. \f ◼ \fr 24:2 \ft \+fk s uqemmum\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘s ufus’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 24:2 \xt 2 Ij. 20:17; 23:27\x*  
\v 3 Wah, man aya \add imsar\add* ak-d Yahuda ɛlaḥsab řumur n SIDI, ḥima ad t issiggʷej x wudem nnes di ssibbet n ddnub n Manassa, di ssibbet n marra min igga wanita. \f ◼ \fr 24:3 \ft \+fk ɛlaḥsab řumur n SIDI\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘x uqemmum n SIDI’.\f*  
\v 4 Uřa di ssibbet n idammen imezdagen i issizzeř řami tuɣa zzaysen iccur Urcalim. \add S uya\add* SIDI tuɣa war ixs ad as iɣfar.   
\m
\v 5 Imezruyen iqqimen n Yahuyaqim d marra min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda?  
\v 6 Yahuyaqim igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Mmis Yahuyakin idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.   
\m
\v 7 Ajeǧid n Miṣra war iffiɣ ɛad \add ɣar umenɣi\add* zi temmurt nnes, maɣar ajeǧid n Babil tuɣa iksi marra min tuɣa \add iǧan\add* n ujeǧid n Miṣra zi Teɣzart n Miṣra ař iɣzar n Lfuraṭ.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yahuyakin, ajeǧid n Yahuda - amezwar n lmenfa ɣar Babil  
\m
\v 8 Yahuyakin \add tuɣa\add* ɣares tmenṭac n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem třata n iyuren di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Neḥucṭa, yeǧis n Il-Natan zi Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 24:8 \xt [2 Im. 36:9-10]\x*  
\v 9 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, nican am mammec t igga babas.  
\v 10 Di řweqt nni ffɣen imsexxaren n Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, ɣar Urcalim uca tᵉttwaḥsar tendint. \x ◘ \xo 24:10 \xt Dan. 1:1\x*  
\v 11 Uřa Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, \add netta simant nnes\add* yusa-dd ɣar tendint am tt ḥṣaren imsexxaren nnes.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ Yahuyakin, ajeǧid n Yahuda, \add zi tendint, yuyur\add* ɣar ujeǧid n Babil, netta ak-d yemmas d imsexxaren nnes d řḥukkam nnes d imsexxaren nnes icennɛen. Ajeǧid n Babil iḥebbes i-t deg useggʷas wiss tmenya n tgelda nnes.  
\v 13 Netta iḥewwes ssenni marra tixubay zi Taddart n SIDI d txubay zi taddart n ujeǧid uca ikkes \add ureɣ\add* x marra řeqcuɛ n wureɣ nni tuɣa igga Suliman, ajeǧid n Israil, di Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI, am mammec tuɣa issiweř SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 24:13 \xt 2 Im. 20:17; Ica. 39:6\x*  
\v 14 Netta yiwi-dd marra Urcalim ak-d marra řḥukkam d marra ayt n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen, ɛecra-ařaf n imeḥbas, uřa d kuř aneqqac \add n ukeccuḍ d weẓru\add* d imziřen. War ijji uřa d ijj mɣir imezřaḍ n řgens n temmurt.  
\v 15 Netta indeh Yahuyakin ɣar Babil. Yemmas n ujeǧid d temɣarin n ujeǧid d imsexxaren nnes icennɛen d marra ayt n jjehd di temmurt yiwyi ten di lmenfa zi Urcalim ɣar Babil. \x ◘ \xo 24:15 \xt 2 Im. 36:10; Ist. 2:6\x*  
\v 16 Marra iryazen imeḥḍen, sebɛa-ařaf \add n yeryazen\add*, uřa d ineqqacen \add n ukeccuḍ d weẓru\add* d imziřen, ařef \add n yeryazen\add*, d marra \add abarru\add* n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt inni ittqeddan x umenɣi, aqa ajeǧid n Babil indeh i-ten \add marra\add* di lmenfa ɣar Babil. \x ◘ \xo 24:16 \xt Irm. 52:28\x*  
\v 17 Ajeǧid n Babil igga Mattanya, ɛemmis, d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes uca ibeddeř isem nnes ɣar Ṣidqiya.\x ◘ \xo 24:17 \xt Irm. 37:1; 52:1\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda  
\m
\v 18 Ṣidqiya \add tuɣa\add* ɣares waḥit u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem ḥiṭac n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Ḥamuṭal, yeǧis n Irmiya, zi Libna. \x ◘ \xo 24:18 \xt [2 Im. 36:11-21, Irm. 52:1-30]\x*  
\v 19 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, nican am mammec t igga Yahuyaqim.  
\v 20 Zi ssibbet n weɣḍab n SIDI, aqa imsar i Urcalim d Yahuda ařami ten-i-dd issekk zi zzat i wudem nnes. \add Awarni as\add* iɣewweɣ Ṣidqiya x ujeǧid n Babil.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 25
\s1 Yahuda di lmenfa ɣar Babil  
\m
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss tesɛa n řeḥkamet nnes, deg uyur wiss ɛecra, deg \add wass\add* wiss ɛecra n uyur, imsar aqa yusa-dd Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, ɣar Urcalim, netta ak-d marra řɛeskar nnes. Iḥṣar i-tt uca nitni quwwaren as s ict n řgeɛɛdet i tɛessast. \x ◘ \xo 25:1 \xt 2 Im. 36:17 Irm. 32:2; 39:1; 52:4\x*  
\v 2 Ḥṣaren tandint ař aseggʷas wiss ḥiṭac n ujeǧid Ṣidqiya.  
\v 3 Deg \add wass\add* wiss tesɛa n uyur \add wiss arebɛa\add* idweř řaẓ imɣar di tendint ařami war tuɣi \add ɛad\add* macca ɣar řgens n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 25:3 \xt Irm. 52:6\x*  
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* tᵉttwarẓ tendint u marra iɛeskariyyen arewřen di ǧiřet x webrid n tewwart \add i iǧan\add* jar tnayen n řeḥyuḍ nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar weḥwic n ujeǧid, waxxa Ikaldaniyyen tuɣa quwwaren i tendint, uca ajeǧid yuyur deg webrid n Řewḍa.  
\v 5 \add Maca\add* řɛeskar n Ikaldaniyyen ḍfaren ajeǧid u nitni ḥarten xas di řewḍat n Ariḥa u marra řɛeskar nnes bezzɛen t xas.  
\v 6 Ṭṭfen ajeǧid uca iwyen t ɣar ujeǧid n Babil, ɣar Ribla, uca ḥekmen xas.  
\v 7 Nitni ɣarṣen i iḥenjiren n Ṣidqiya zzat i tiṭṭawin nnes, ssdarɣřen tiṭṭawin n Ṣidqiya uca carfen t s tnayen n ssnaseř n nnḥas, iwyen t ɣar Babil.   
\m
\v 8 \add Awarni as\add* deg uyur wiss xemsa, deg \add wass\add* wiss xemsa n uyur - tuɣa-t deg useggʷas wiss tseɛṭac n Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil - yusa-dd Nabuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, amsexxar n ujeǧid n Babil, di Urcalim.  
\v 9 Issecmeḍ Taddart n SIDI d taddart n ujeǧid d marra tudrin n Urcalim uřa kuř taddart d tameqqrant issarɣ as timessi.  
\v 10 Řeḥyuḍ i dd-innḍen i Urcalim ɣeḍřen ten marra řɛeskar n Ikaldaniyyen nni \add dd-yusin ak-d\add* řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet.  
\v 11 Min iceṭṭen zi řgens nni ittwajjen di tendint, \add ixs ad yini\add* \add marra\add* inni tuɣa iɛdun ɣar ujeǧid n Babil d min iceṭṭen zi řɣaci, indeh i-ten Nabuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, ɣar lmenfa.  
\v 12 Řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet ijja mɣir ca n imezřaḍ n temmurt am ayt n bu-tzayart d ifeǧaḥen.   
\m
\v 13 Ipilaren n nnḥas di Taddart n SIDI d tkarrutin d trimant n nnḥas nni tuɣa \add din\add* ɣar Taddart n SIDI, arẓin ten Ikaldaniyyen uca arbun marra nnḥas ɣar Babil.\f ◼ \fr 25:13 \ft \+fk tarimant\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řebḥar’ niɣ ‘il’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 25:13 \xt 2 Ij. 20:17; Irm. 20:5; 27:19\x*  
\v 14 Uřa d tiydurin, d iɣenjayen, d tjeqqaḍin, d tɣenjayin uřa d marra řeqcuɛ n nnḥas i zi tuɣa ttsexxaren, iwyen ten.  
\v 15 Řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet yiwi-dd timejmarin d ṭṭawyat i urucci, \add marra\add* min \add tuɣa iǧan\add* qaɛ n wureɣ niɣ n nnuqart.  
\v 16 \add Uřa d\add* tnayen n ipilaren d trimant d tkarrutin nni tuɣa igga Suliman i Taddart n SIDI. Tuɣa war izemmar ad weznen nnḥas n marra řeqcuɛ-a.  
\v 17 Řuɛřa n ijj n upilar tuɣa dayes tmenṭac n iɣaǧen, u ttaj i xas, tuɣa n nnḥas. Řuɛřa n ttaj tuɣa-t třata n iɣaǧen. , u tiracciwin d iremmamen i d as dd-innḍen i ttaj tuɣa aten marra n nnḥas. Ammu i tuɣa uřa ɣar upilar wiss tnayen, x tracca i xas \add iǧan\add*.\x ◘ \xo 25:17 \xt 1 Ij. 7:15; 2 Im. 3:15; Irm. 52:21\x*   
\m
\v 18 Yiwi-dd řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet \add ɛawed\add* Saraya, akehhan ameqqran, d Ṣafanya, akehhan wiss tnayen, uřa d třata n iɛessasen n tewwart. \f ◼ \fr 25:18 \ft \+fk Ṣafanya\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni t issnuffaren SIDI’.\f*  
\v 19 Netta yiwi-dd ijj n umsexxar amcenneɛ wenni ittwařeqqmen x iɛeskariyyen d xemsa n yeryazen imeḥḍen zeg imtiqqan n ujeǧid, inni ittwafen di tendint, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d umarir n ukumandar n řɛeskar nni izemmemen řgens n temmurt i umenɣi, uřa d settin n yeryazen zi řgens n temmurt nni ittwafen di tendint.  
\v 20 Yiwi ten Nabuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet uca yuyur akidsen ɣar ujeǧid n Babil, ɣar Ribla.  
\v 21 Ajeǧid n Babil iwwet i-ten, inɣa i-ten di Ribla di temmurt n Ḥamat. \add Ammu i\add* ittwandeh Yahuda zi temmurt nnes ɣar lmenfa.  
\v 22 \add X\add* řgens i tuɣa iqqimen di temmurt n Yahuda, i tuɣa ijja \add din\add* Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, aqa igga xasen Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam, mmis n Cafan. \x ◘ \xo 25:22 \xt Irm. 40:5, 9\x*  
\v 23 \add Umi\add* sřin ikumandaren n řɛeskarat, nitni d yeryazen nsen, belli ajeǧid n Babil igga Jadalya \add d awkiř\add*, usin-dd nitni ɣar Jadalya di Miṣfa: Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya, Yuḥanan, mmis n Qariḥa, Saraya, mmis n Tanḥumat, Anaṭufati, d Yazanyahu, mmis n Umaɛki, nitni ak-d yeryazen nsen. \x ◘ \xo 25:23 \xt Irm. 40:7\x*  
\v 24 Jadalya ijjuǧ asen u i yeryazen nsen, inna asen: “War tteggʷdem zeg imsexxaren n Ikaldaniyyen. Qqimem di temmurt uca sexxarem i ujeǧid n Babil, xenni ad tiřim mliḥ.”   
\m
\v 25 \add Maca\add* deg uyur wiss sebɛa yusa-dd Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya, mmis n Ilicamaɛ, \add wenni\add* dd-iqqarṣen zeg ujeǧid, ak-d ɛecra n yeryazen. Nitni wtin Jadalya \add ařami\add* immut uřa d Iyahudiyyen d Ikaldaniyyen inni ɣares iǧan di Miṣfa.  
\v 26 \add Xenni\add* ikkar marra řgens, am umeẓyan am umeqqran, uřa d ikumandaren n řɛeskar, ffɣen ɣar Miṣra, minzi ggʷeden zeg Ikaldaniyyen.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Yahuyakin iṭṭef arḍa di Babil  
\m
\v 27 Deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa u-třatin n lmenfa n Yahuyakin, ajeǧid n Yahuda, deg uyur wiss tenɛac, deg \add wass\add* wiss sebɛa u-ɛicrin n uyur, imsar, aqa Iwil-Marudax, ajeǧid n Babil, deg useggʷas i di idweř d ajeǧid, iḍřeq-dd i Yahuyakin, ajeǧid n Yahuda, zi řeḥbes. \x ◘ \xo 25:27 \xt [Irm. 52:31-34]\x*  
\v 28 Netta issiweř akides s řeḍrafet u igga řkursi nnes tiwa i řkarasi n ijeǧiden nneɣni i tuɣa ɣares iǧan di Babil.  
\v 29 Ibeddeř \add Yahuyakin\add* arruḍ nnes n řeḥbes uca idweř ittett řebda ɣares marra ussan n tudart nnes.  
\v 30 X řɛuč nnes, aqa immewc as zeg ujeǧid řebda ijj n řɛuč aqedda n wass x wass nnes, marra ussan n tudart nnes.   